The Second Sales Division!","native":"営業二課っ!","romaji":"Eigyou Ni-ka!","userPreferred":"Eigyou Ni-ka!"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":2},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#5d5de4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx87091-o5v78QIIHnds.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx87091-o5v78QIIHnds.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx87091-o5v78QIIHnds.png"},"description":"An expressionless club doorman meets a flashy boy at one of the many parties the place gathers. As someone who’s always been considered quite boring or an emotionless person, Saya-chan with his clumsy personality will make this man a more vivid one.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":14,"month":12,"year":2015},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":87091,"idMal":93610,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/87091","startDate":{"day":12,"month":8,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Neon Sign Umber","When Amber shines in Neon Light","琥珀色 霓虹灯"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"ネオンサイン・アンバー","romaji":"Neon Sign Amber","userPreferred":"Neon Sign Amber"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/180960-3lZ5RcTRIZTh.jpg","chapters":30,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#fea150","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx180960-nFB4aEHNmWbs.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx180960-nFB4aEHNmWbs.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx180960-nFB4aEHNmWbs.png"},"description":"A one-night stand turns into a messy love story.\u003cbr\u003e\nJosh, a brilliant lawyer and obsessive neat freak, is coping with a broken engagement. The only upside? His firm changed cleaning services. But when the new cleaner is Angel—his one-night stand from last night—chaos ensues. Is this love or just a messy disaster waiting to unfold?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Manta)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes six side story chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":16,"month":8,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":180960,"idMal":184924,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/180960","startDate":{"day":24,"month":2,"year":2024},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["สะอาดแล้วครับคุณทนาย"],"title":{"english":"The Dirtiest High","native":"더티 하이","romaji":"Dirty High","userPreferred":"Dirty High"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":1,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx147162-oQerPb5iBBfO.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx147162-oQerPb5iBBfO.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx147162-oQerPb5iBBfO.jpg"},"description":null,"endDate":{"day":17,"month":3,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai","Horror","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":147162,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/147162","startDate":{"day":17,"month":3,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Lady K \u0026 The Sick Man - Paradise -","Kko to Yamioji Raku"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"K子と病みおじ・楽","romaji":"K-ko to Yamioji Raku","userPreferred":"K-ko to Yamioji Raku"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/51151-PNvsqKdzzkQr.jpg","chapters":45,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d6a16b","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx51151-qUatDXeS0oqh.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx51151-qUatDXeS0oqh.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx51151-qUatDXeS0oqh.png"},"description":"During their final summer vacation, Nana and Kaoru’s plans coincide when both find themselves staying at the same mansion in the countryside, with Nana being tutored by adult goods shop owner, Tachibana, and Kaoru by his favorite BDSM writer, Sarashina Shutaro. Wanting to use the couple as inspiration for his next book, the two witness Shutaro's mastery of BDSM with Tachibana. So when Nana witnesses the rawness and intensity of true BDSM, will she look away or will something new unlock in her?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: FAKKU!)","endDate":{"day":4,"month":4,"year":2014},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Ecchi","Romance"],"id":51151,"idMal":21151,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/51151","startDate":{"day":2,"month":7,"year":2010},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Nana to Kaoru Arashi","나나와 카오루 블랙라벨"],"title":{"english":"Nana \u0026 Kaoru: Black Label","native":"ナナとカオル Black Label","romaji":"Nana to Kaoru: Black Label","userPreferred":"Nana to Kaoru: Black Label"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":5},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":5,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d65093","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx147158-mtxOezS25NvU.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx147158-mtxOezS25NvU.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx147158-mtxOezS25NvU.jpg"},"description":"In this world, in addition to being male or female, people are divided into two \"dynamics\": those who yearn to control and those who yearn to be controlled. Kippei's a regular office worker who's always hated being the latter. But, suppressing his desire has stressed him out to the point of making him sick. Finally, he goes to the doctor, who tells him the last thing he wants to hear: he needs to find a partner and get some release! Kippei signs up for a matchmaking program, only to get paired with a guy who happens to be his hot coworker Sota Otomo.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Renta!)","endDate":{"day":30,"month":4,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance"],"id":147158,"idMal":144004,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":79,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/147158","startDate":{"day":26,"month":6,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Learning to Love at Your Feet","native":"君の足元で愛を知る","romaji":"Kimi no Ashimoto de Ai wo shiru","userPreferred":"Kimi no Ashimoto de Ai wo shiru"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/188223-3P2RF3qYxzRr.jpg","chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4aebb","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b188223-HwFCW3IR7CEX.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b188223-HwFCW3IR7CEX.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b188223-HwFCW3IR7CEX.png"},"description":"\u003ci\u003e\"Six months... Just six months, and it'll all be over.\"\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAfter a one-night stand Hollywood top star Chase Miller, Joshua finds out he’s pregnant. As a single father, Joshua raises their child in secrecy. But when he is forced to return to work as Chase’s bodyguard, the two are reunited in a cruel twist of fate. Relieved that Chase doesn’t seem to remember him, Josh’s comfort is short lived -  something primal, something desperate, yearns for the touch of his former lover, and every time he sees this beautifully twisted man, Josh’s heart races in spite of his mind. The more time passes, the more boundaries blur as instinct takes over… Will Joshua be able to resist the lips of his former lover? Or are the strings of fate too strong to resist?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Lezhin US)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":188223,"idMal":184890,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":80,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/188223","startDate":{"day":15,"month":1,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Kiss Me If You Can (キス・ミー・イフ・ユー・キャン)"],"title":{"english":"Kiss Me if You Can","native":"키스 미 이프 유 캔","romaji":"Kiss Me If You Can","userPreferred":"Kiss Me If You Can"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4c9ae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx150858-qsoHKQX7TcCE.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx150858-qsoHKQX7TcCE.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx150858-qsoHKQX7TcCE.jpg"},"description":"Sudo ostensibly works as a normal deliveryman but actually acts as a \"courier\" for the underworld, sleeps with his neighbor Uno after they got drunk over dinner. The next day, Uno becomes very distant from him. Worried about Uno's feelings for him, Sudo sees Uno being harassed by some thugs on the street, and he reflexively takes Uno by the hand and try to run away. Attacked by enemies, the wounded Sudo was saved by forming a contract bond with Uno, a descendant of witches, who has been hiding his powers in secret.\n\u003cBR\u003e\u003cBR\u003e\n(Source: \u0026.Emo, translated)","endDate":{"day":24,"month":3,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Drama","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":150858,"idMal":146920,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":78,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/150858","startDate":{"day":24,"month":6,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Witch and Cat"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"魔女と猫","romaji":"Majo to Neko","userPreferred":"Majo to Neko"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/109511-7bwZTtCRdRA7.jpg","chapters":98,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1bbae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx109511-OQgawHqIipmz.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx109511-OQgawHqIipmz.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx109511-OQgawHqIipmz.jpg"},"description":"There’s a late bloomer, and then there’s a \u003ci\u003elate bloomer.\u003c/i\u003e Do-Yun may be half Omega, but he certainly doesn’t look it: he’s tall, chiseled... But the worst of it all is that he’s a full-grown adult male who has yet to go into heat. He doesn’t see the problem, and everyone assumes he’s an Alpha, anyway. But when his body finally decides it’s “time,” it just happens to be at the most inopportune moment. He has no-one to turn to but his work rival, Tae-Han – but thankfully, Tae-Han is more than man enough to help him out. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin US) \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Chapter count includes 14 extras.\u003ci\u003e","endDate":{"day":3,"month":10,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":109511,"idMal":122279,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/109511","startDate":{"day":2,"month":2,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["恋人パシリ〜遺伝子の発現にはご注意を〜"],"title":{"english":"Love Shuttle","native":"애인셔틀","romaji":"Aein Shuttle","userPreferred":"Aein Shuttle"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#933528","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx152905-Z4k0znQ5QMdB.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx152905-Z4k0znQ5QMdB.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx152905-Z4k0znQ5QMdB.jpg"},"description":"As the son of King Yeom-ra of the underworld, Jae-shin has lived a hedonistic life full of ever-changing bed partners and condescension towards humans. One day, however, he crosses a line and is given a rather unusual punishment: by day, he becomes a powerless puppy, and by night, he becomes a human. The only way to escape his punishment is to win over a human’s heart, which won’t be easy…especially when the human he sets his eyes on is sweet-natured prince Lee Nok. Will Jae-shin win over the prince? Or will Jae-shin be the one who is won over?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin US)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Supernatural"],"id":152905,"idMal":152634,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/152905","startDate":{"day":21,"month":7,"year":2022},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":["Night Song","Devil's Night Song","鬼夜曲","鬼夜曲～闇に響く亡霊の唄～"],"title":{"english":"The Ghost's Nocturne","native":"귀야곡","romaji":"Gwiyagok","userPreferred":"Gwiyagok"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/104058-r4KgYXFTH0y6.jpg","chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4781a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx104058-zyFkjImcZsft.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx104058-zyFkjImcZsft.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx104058-zyFkjImcZsft.png"},"description":"Saving the World, One BJ at a Time!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nMasato might be an unemployed, virgin bachelor, but ever since he was a kid, he's wanted to do something that could benefit the world. With it looking like he'll never achieve his dream, Masato's approached by two sisters who might give him that chance. Tomoe and Ayano work with a succubus organization seeking pure human blood and Masato is one of the last remaining pure-blooded humans in existence! With his essence carrying immeasurable value to succubi, they hire him to suck every satisfying ounce of seed straight from the tap. But once he's revealed to the greater succubus public, will he have the will and strength to accomplish his goal?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nSuccubi Ally! by Fue is a soul-sucking experience of one man's goal to quench the thirst of succubi-kind. Pushing him to his near limits, a little bit of succubus saliva down his throat brings him rock-hard and ready to do every job from A to Z. Topping off at over 230 pages of sweet succubi action, Succubi Ally's women are a hand and mouthful that're cute beyond belief!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Fakku)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eChapter names:\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n1. \u003cb\u003eTada yori Takai mono wa nai\u003c/b\u003e (タダより高いモノは無い, There's No Such Thing as a Free Lunch)\u003cbr\u003e\n2. \u003cb\u003eKyuusei-nushi no Oshigoto wa\u003c/b\u003e (吸精主のお仕事は, The Job of a Sperm Provider)\u003cbr\u003e\n3. \u003cb\u003eHatsujou Chinpo to Kamonegi Mother\u003c/b\u003e (発情チ〇ポとカモネギマザー, A Horny Cock \u0026 a Mother Sucker)\u003cbr\u003e\n4. \u003cb\u003eMe ni wa Me wo, Katabutsu ni wa Kenbutsu wo\u003c/b\u003e (目には目を、堅物には堅ブツを, An Eye for an Eye, A Hard Cock for a Hard-Head)\u003cbr\u003e\n5. \u003cb\u003eKyuujitsu wa Yasumu Jikan ga Nai no Desu\u003c/b\u003e (休日は休む時間が無いのです, No Time to Relax on a Holiday)\u003cbr\u003e\n6. \u003cb\u003eShasei wa Tsuzuku yo Doko made mo\u003c/b\u003e (射精は続くよ何処までも！, The Ejaculations Will Continue as Long as They Must!)\u003cbr\u003e","endDate":{"day":22,"month":12,"year":2015},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":104058,"idMal":110632,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/104058","startDate":{"day":22,"month":8,"year":2014},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Succubi Ally!","native":"淫魔のミカタ！","romaji":"Inma no Mikata!","userPreferred":"Inma no Mikata!"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":7,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1d6c9","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/nx100159-Gg1zPDfI59am.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/nx100159-Gg1zPDfI59am.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/nx100159-Gg1zPDfI59am.png"},"description":"Jimmy, a small-time thief, is caught pickpocketing by a middle-aged guy named Reese. Instead of handing him over to the police, Reese makes him slog hard for a day at the book store where he works. Wanting to get back at the other man for humiliating him, Jimmy breaks into Reese's apartment, only to find evidence that he's a retired cop. A bit spooked now, he leaves in a hurry, determined to put it all behind him and carry on as usual... But getting Reese out of his head proves to be tougher than Jimmy could ever have imagined.\n","endDate":{"day":21,"month":2,"year":2017},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":100159,"idMal":109001,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/100159","startDate":{"day":20,"month":9,"year":2016},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"オンドアステップ","romaji":"On Doorstep","userPreferred":"On Doorstep"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/98072-n9svQ8oeHWye.jpg","chapters":80,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4356b","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx98072-NOp0lfCSWNVz.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx98072-NOp0lfCSWNVz.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx98072-NOp0lfCSWNVz.jpg"},"description":"Wooseung, an art student who's only now delving into the dating scene, falls head over heels for Sunjin, the ever-so-charming upperclassman. Imagine Wooseung dreaming up classic romantic scenes, only to find out Sunjin's idea of a relationship is... let's just say… more physical. And it’s not Sunjin's fault! He can't help it when Wooseung is just so freaking cute. From picture-perfect romantic dreams to Sunjin's hands-on approach, Wooseung's in for a wild ride!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tapas)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003ci\u003eNote: includes 20 extra chapters. This work was first serialised in Lezhin before it got discontinued and moved to Series Naver. There is an adult version and a non-adult version.\u003c/I\u003e\n","endDate":{"day":16,"month":1,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":98072,"idMal":128470,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/98072","startDate":{"day":17,"month":8,"year":2016},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Энциклопедия страсти","欲望相关两三事","About Lust","Yogmang Ilaneun Geos-e Daehayeo","關於慾望的那些事"],"title":{"english":"All About Lust: Where We Started","native":"욕망이라는 것에 대하여","romaji":"Yongmangiraneun Geose Daehayeo","userPreferred":"Yongmangiraneun Geose Daehayeo"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":6},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/165659-t8cX3gvyz5n0.jpg","chapters":16,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4aea1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx165659-YFNy8C3H1Yyr.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx165659-YFNy8C3H1Yyr.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx165659-YFNy8C3H1Yyr.jpg"},"description":"At odds with each other since their high school days, corporate salesmen Ryo and Zen have finally become lovers. The transition has not been a smooth one however, with each man still baiting the other into petty competitions as they struggle to navigate their new dynamic. And with their hectic work schedules cutting into their time together, it isn’t long before anxiety and jealousy begin to creep into their hearts. Yet just when it seems that positive progress is being made, their coworker, Futami, returns to the main office from Osaka and tries to insert himself into Ryo and Zen’s rivalry! But is some friendly competition \u003ci\u003eall\u003c/i\u003e he’s after?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes five extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":24,"month":9,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":165659,"idMal":164828,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":79,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/165659","startDate":{"day":24,"month":1,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Fake Fact Lips: BREAK","native":"フェイクファクトリップス break","romaji":"Fake Fact Lips break","userPreferred":"Fake Fact Lips break"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":2},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/126902-vE2Ddh32k2OK.jpg","chapters":112,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bba1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx126902-M4ZXSfBI1O73.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx126902-M4ZXSfBI1O73.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx126902-M4ZXSfBI1O73.jpg"},"description":"Du-Sik is in a bind. After making off with the takings from the gay bar where he worked, he seeks refuge in a small, coastal town. As his funds dwindle, he desperately needs a way to make ends meet. Still, a boy’s gotta eat! So he dives into a clam house to satisfy his cravings. But with no money to pay, he dashes off leaving Ju-Ha, the server, to foot the bill. Later on, when Du-Sik returns to pay his debt, he’s greeted by a sordid scene that offers a tantalizing glimpse of the solution to his money problems. For within Ju-Ha's beautiful shell lies a secret treasure waiting to be drawn out. And Du-Sik is just the man to do it.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin, edited)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Chapter count includes 2 epilogue chapters and 20 side story chapters.\u003ci/\u003e","endDate":{"day":17,"month":11,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":126902,"idMal":136294,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/126902","startDate":{"day":9,"month":10,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Shell Boy","Seashell Boy","El chico de las perlas","Le Garçon aux perles","真珠を産む少年","Perlenjunge"],"title":{"english":"Pearl Boy","native":"조개소년","romaji":"Jogaesonyeon","userPreferred":"Jogaesonyeon"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/118776-SJE564Dv5zL8.jpg","chapters":74,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1ae43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx118776-mMSzcto7qQ0K.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx118776-mMSzcto7qQ0K.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx118776-mMSzcto7qQ0K.jpg"},"description":"This is a new story that follows the end of \u003ci\u003eA Pervert's Daily Life\u003c/i\u003e with new characters.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: The series starts with \"A Pervert's Daily Life\" prologue chapter before chapter 72 on Lezhin Korea.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":20,"month":10,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Hentai","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":118776,"idMal":119735,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/118776","startDate":{"day":20,"month":4,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["新卒妄想ちゃんの日常性活！ アナザーストーリー"],"title":{"english":"Perverts' Daily Lives","native":"일상생활들 가능하세요?","romaji":"Ilsangsaenghwaldeul Ganeunghaseyo?","userPreferred":"Ilsangsaenghwaldeul Ganeunghaseyo?"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":9,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45da1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx112485-aNTeflamFKFd.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx112485-aNTeflamFKFd.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx112485-aNTeflamFKFd.png"},"description":"Impatient 29-year old omega Shishikura has watched all his friends get married while his own romances keep fizzling out. Determined to find someone compatible, he turns to a matchmaking service. But while waiting for his perfect soulmate to be found, he goes into heat at the worst possible moment—alone with Kotani, a new coworker who is nursing a longtime grudge against Shishikura! After spending a desperate steamy night together, there’s no doubt that the two are physically compatible, but do they even like each other?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: SuBLime)","endDate":{"day":14,"month":5,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":112485,"idMal":133353,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/112485","startDate":{"day":12,"month":10,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["I Can't Believe You're My Fated Partner!","운명의 짝이 너라니"],"title":{"english":"Worst Soulmate Ever","native":"運命の番がお前だなんて","romaji":"Unmei no Tsugai ga Omae da Nante","userPreferred":"Unmei no Tsugai ga Omae da Nante"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/n107095-8BiyXv0PD33c.jpg","chapters":1,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/nx107095-dWCJN2l7z78d.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/nx107095-dWCJN2l7z78d.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/nx107095-dWCJN2l7z78d.jpg"},"description":"A young couple having their first time together after coming back from the summer festival.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Published in Comic Hotmilk 2019-01\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":1,"month":12,"year":2018},"format":"ONE_SHOT","genres":["Hentai","Romance"],"id":107095,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":79,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/107095","startDate":{"day":1,"month":12,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Summer and Innocence"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"夏と純","romaji":"Natsu to Jun","userPreferred":"Natsu to Jun"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/86342-Cqep9cZ11ava.png","chapters":132,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d6b","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx86342-d9DErFMbqZCV.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx86342-d9DErFMbqZCV.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx86342-d9DErFMbqZCV.jpg"},"description":"As the newest hire of a game dev studio, beautiful Seong-Ji draws all the attention of her coworkers — but it's her bossy and blunt team leader Su-Min that intrigues her. Love is a whole new game for Seong-Ji, and with company president Se-Ju breaking (or was it laying?) down the rules, this new girl’s got her work cut out for her if she wants to win. Will she be able to give Su-Min what she wants?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tappytoon, edited)","endDate":{"day":15,"month":12,"year":2019},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":86342,"idMal":108021,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/86342","startDate":{"day":29,"month":4,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["WDTFS","왓 더즈 더 폭스 세이?","狐狸說了什麼?"],"title":{"english":"What Does the Fox Say?","native":"What Does the Fox Say?","romaji":"What Does the Fox Say?","userPreferred":"What Does the Fox Say?"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":6}],"pageInfo":{"currentPage":4,"hasNextPage":true,"lastPage":104,"perPage":48,"total":5000}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-15T06:40:40.748747+03:00"},"{\"query\":\"query ListManga ($page: Int, $search: String, $perPage: Int, $sort: [MediaSort], $status: [MediaStatus], $genres: [String], $averageScore_greater: Int, $startDate_greater: FuzzyDateInt, $startDate_lesser: FuzzyDateInt, $format: MediaFormat, $countryOfOrigin: CountryCode, $isAdult: Boolean) {\\n\\tPage(page: $page, perPage: $perPage) {\\n\\t\\tpageInfo {\\n\\t\\t\\thasNextPage\\n\\t\\t\\ttotal\\n\\t\\t\\tperPage\\n\\t\\t\\tcurrentPage\\n\\t\\t\\tlastPage\\n\\t\\t}\\n\\t\\tmedia(type: MANGA, isAdult: $isAdult, countryOfOrigin: $countryOfOrigin, search: $search, sort: $sort, status_in: $status, format: $format, genre_in: $genres, averageScore_greater: $averageScore_greater, startDate_greater: $startDate_greater, startDate_lesser: $startDate_lesser, format_not: NOVEL) {\\n\\t\\t\\t... baseManga\\n\\t\\t}\\n\\t}\\n}\\nfragment baseManga on Media {\\n\\tid\\n\\tidMal\\n\\tsiteUrl\\n\\tstatus(version: 2)\\n\\tseason\\n\\ttype\\n\\tformat\\n\\tbannerImage\\n\\tchapters\\n\\tvolumes\\n\\tsynonyms\\n\\tisAdult\\n\\tcountryOfOrigin\\n\\tmeanScore\\n\\tdescription\\n\\tgenres\\n\\ttitle {\\n\\t\\tuserPreferred\\n\\t\\tromaji\\n\\t\\tenglish\\n\\t\\tnative\\n\\t}\\n\\tcoverImage {\\n\\t\\textraLarge\\n\\t\\tlarge\\n\\t\\tmedium\\n\\t\\tcolor\\n\\t}\\n\\tstartDate {\\n\\t\\tyear\\n\\t\\tmonth\\n\\t\\tday\\n\\t}\\n\\tendDate {\\n\\t\\tyear\\n\\t\\tmonth\\n\\t\\tday\\n\\t}\\n}\\n\",\"variables\":{\"isAdult\":true,\"page\":5,\"perPage\":48,\"sort\":[\"SCORE_DESC\"]}}":{"value":{"Page":{"media":[{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":20,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#50bbe4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx85899-BJnIIxTbo3Cp.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx85899-BJnIIxTbo3Cp.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx85899-BJnIIxTbo3Cp.png"},"description":"Good-for-nothing Momo lacks the ability to look after himself, and is the ultimate slut. Yata is the mothering type, a reliable but simple guy. The two get off to the worst possible start when Yata comes across Momo during a post-sex clean-up in a public restroom. Taking advantage of Yata's kindness, Momo ends up staying at his apartment. As he spends more with Yata, the once-slovenly Momo starts to change... But in the midst of this, Momo's previous \"owner\" shows up. An erotic comedy with a sad twist that'll pull at your heartstrings.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Renta!)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eIncluded one-shot:\u003c/b\u003e \u003cbr\u003e\nVolume 2: Sumomo","endDate":{"day":24,"month":2,"year":2017},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":85899,"idMal":88717,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/85899","startDate":{"day":24,"month":10,"year":2013},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["八田百田","Sumomo"],"title":{"english":"Yata \u0026 Momo","native":"やたもも","romaji":"YataMomo","userPreferred":"YataMomo"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":3},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":24,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b116762-xf8cSaQ2VN4Q.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b116762-xf8cSaQ2VN4Q.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b116762-xf8cSaQ2VN4Q.jpg"},"description":"Cavo is a hideous monster with a pure heart. Liam, on the other hand, might look like the perfect gentleman, but he's a beast on the inside, and he has an eccentric personality to boot. When Cavo rescues Liam from an unfortunate situation in the forest, the paths of the monster and the beast cross for the first time. Will their meeting be a fleeting encounter or a timeless entanglement? And will Liam succeed in leading the innocent Cavo astray?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Yen Press)","endDate":{"day":30,"month":9,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Fantasy","Romance"],"id":116762,"idMal":116653,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/116762","startDate":{"day":31,"month":3,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["สุภาพบุรุษปีศาจกับทาสรักอสูร"],"title":{"english":"Monster and the Beast","native":"バケモノとケダモノ","romaji":"Bakemono to Kedamono","userPreferred":"Bakemono to Kedamono"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":4},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/107393-i1ZfQbao1Gjy.jpg","chapters":61,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4aea1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b107393-NDWJt6465sUr.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b107393-NDWJt6465sUr.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b107393-NDWJt6465sUr.png"},"description":"Mr. Do-Yun Kim’s a pretty quiet, unassuming guy at the office with a big secret. He’s actually half vampire! But without full vamp status, he can’t drink blood and has to seek out some human essence to live. Drained and desperate, he finds a “special” companion, but everything goes wrong. Now he’s caught up in a one-sided office relationship, and most importantly, it’s not working!!! Will Do-Yun survive and keep his secret intact?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tapas, edited)","endDate":{"day":20,"month":3,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":107393,"idMal":185319,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/107393","startDate":{"day":1,"month":8,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["K's Secret","El deseo secreto de Kim"],"title":{"english":"The Unquenchable Mr. Kim","native":"회사원 K의 비밀","romaji":"Hoesawon Kui Bimil","userPreferred":"Hoesawon Kui Bimil"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":12,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae0d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/nx101950-uztg46sruhW0.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/nx101950-uztg46sruhW0.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/nx101950-uztg46sruhW0.jpg"},"description":"Kami, who is gay, has given up on love. Despite not having anyone to share his cooking with, he always makes a ton of food. And along comes Waki, a good-looking TV announcer who hosts \"Waki Travels! Waki's Happy Food Corner!\" Although he's got no taste buds, he eats a ton and comments on the food he finds in people's homes. But he takes an interest in Kami's food and even goes to visit him at his workplace. While he's able to slowly open up to the big-hearted Waki, he's still unable to be true to his feelings when he's afraid of getting hurt again...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes 3 extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e\n","endDate":{"day":7,"month":9,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":101950,"idMal":115789,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/101950","startDate":{"day":6,"month":5,"year":2017},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Ren-chin!"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"恋チン!","romaji":"Renchin!","userPreferred":"Renchin!"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":2},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/55555-1rG6G5iAzAym.jpg","chapters":48,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx85555-b7hCT4nEh93W.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx85555-b7hCT4nEh93W.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx85555-b7hCT4nEh93W.png"},"description":"Corporate secretary Shirotani suffers from obsessive-compulsive disorder. One day he meets Kurose, a therapist who offers to take him through a ten-step program to cure him of his compulsion. As the two go through each of the ten steps, Shirotani 's attraction to his counselor grows.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: SuBLime)","endDate":{"day":14,"month":11,"year":2017},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Psychological","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":85555,"idMal":56857,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/85555","startDate":{"day":13,"month":7,"year":2013},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["10 Count","До десяти","텐카운트"],"title":{"english":"Ten Count","native":"テンカウント","romaji":"Ten Count","userPreferred":"Ten Count"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":6},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e44343","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx166619-KfSkSpBTwz9J.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx166619-KfSkSpBTwz9J.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx166619-KfSkSpBTwz9J.jpg"},"description":"Lee Taegun is the nation’s top esper, unmatched and untouchable with how powerful he is. A veritable immovable object. But the truth is, he’s not as untouchable as he seems. Like every esper out there, he experiences negative side effects of using his powers. However, unlike every esper out there, he’s dead set against partnering with a guide who could help him recover. Now here comes Seo Eunsung, one of the greatest guides alive, and he’s determined to guide Taegun whether he likes it or not. So: irresistible force meets immovable object. Who will fall first in this battle? Or will they both fall…for each other?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin US)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Comedy","Fantasy","Romance","Sci-Fi"],"id":166619,"idMal":185020,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":78,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/166619","startDate":{"day":30,"month":6,"year":2023},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["疏導危機","GUIDING HAZARD〜俺たちのマッチング率は90%〜","ไกด์ดิ้งแสนอันตราย"],"title":{"english":"Guiding Hazard","native":"가이딩 해저드","romaji":"Guiding Hazard","userPreferred":"Guiding Hazard"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":21,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#6bf143","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx134346-pbkqwIkv19t2.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx134346-pbkqwIkv19t2.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx134346-pbkqwIkv19t2.jpg"},"description":"Dazed and confused, Chihiro awakes on a pile of garbage with memories of wedding still fresh in his mind. When out of the blue a young man named Keito appears before him. Instantly,  he then recalls the night he spent with this person. The booze! The hotel! The punch to his face!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nChihiro may not have a place to call home currently and Keito may not be a good person by any means, but maybe the two of them could be happy together.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: KUMA)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes four extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":24,"month":8,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":134346,"idMal":134649,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":81,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/134346","startDate":{"day":24,"month":1,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Happy of the End","native":"ハッピー・オブ・ジ・エンド","romaji":"Happy of the End","userPreferred":"Happy of the End"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":3},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/92798-weBJg9FjKcJ3.jpg","chapters":9,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f15093","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx92798-Fm0EvZlfcf49.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx92798-Fm0EvZlfcf49.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx92798-Fm0EvZlfcf49.jpg"},"description":"Oh, to be on a nude beach with a harem of all your classmates! Another legendary story from Shiwasu no Okina, this title tells you exactly what you’re going to get!","endDate":{"day":27,"month":6,"year":2015},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":92798,"idMal":79253,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/92798","startDate":{"day":28,"month":4,"year":2014},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Class Trip to the Nudist Beach!!","Nudist Beach ni Shuugakuryokou de!!","Yarimoku Beach ni Shuugaku Ryokou de!!","In school trip to the nudist beach!!","The Nude Beach Field Trip!!"],"title":{"english":"The Nude Beach Field Trip!!","native":"ヌーディストビーチに修学旅行で!!","romaji":"Nudist Beach ni Shuugaku Ryokou de!!","userPreferred":"Nudist Beach ni Shuugaku Ryokou de!!"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/177070-KifbVuD7uGRe.jpg","chapters":50,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#ffd6ae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx177070-XB0dderaCHKk.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx177070-XB0dderaCHKk.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx177070-XB0dderaCHKk.jpg"},"description":"Jin-Ha, an overworked developer, gets the worst news of his life—he’s a recessive Omega! He’s now extra sensitive to alphas, and the only thing that calms him is his boss Hyun-Joon’s pheromones. This is a nightmare, especially since Jin-Ha’s been stashing money in a “murder for hire” account to cope with how annoying Hyun-Joon is. As if that’s not enough, a creepy stalker starts showering him with pheromones. Now, Jin-Ha’s stuck under the protection of his infuriatingly handsome boss!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tapas)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes 12 extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":9,"month":5,"year":2025},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":177070,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/177070","startDate":{"day":13,"month":1,"year":2024},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Eine unromantische Romanze","Une romance pas très romantique","Eine unromantische Romanze"],"title":{"english":"Romance Not Romantic","native":"로맨스 낫 로맨틱","romaji":"Romance Not Romantic","userPreferred":"Romance Not Romantic"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/n107392-U2yXwoXGhGvg.jpg","chapters":135,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#ffc993","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx107392-Zac5Gx9C05Dm.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx107392-Zac5Gx9C05Dm.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx107392-Zac5Gx9C05Dm.jpg"},"description":"A human, lycan, or a vampire - what am I?! Completely unaware of the existence of these predators, Hwa-Gok goes about his everyday life... That is, until Lee-Bin turns his life upside down by biting him on the neck, setting off a whirlwind of events neither of them could foresee.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin US)","endDate":{"day":27,"month":1,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance","Supernatural"],"id":107392,"idMal":185124,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/107392","startDate":{"day":2,"month":5,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Blood Link","native":"블러드 링크","romaji":"Blood Link","userPreferred":"Blood Link"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":7,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4435d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx73465-VJzl3cBLcAYo.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx73465-VJzl3cBLcAYo.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx73465-VJzl3cBLcAYo.jpg"},"description":"Ashitaka's an out and proud gay man, trawling for booty calls at his favorite gay bar - but only bottoms need apply, because Ashitaka only tops! His first attempt at gay sex three years ago ended painfully and embarrassingly, and he vowed to never yield his ass to another man again - but fate has decided to throw the very man responsible for his 'bottom trauma' back into his life, and the guy's looking for a fresh start.\n","endDate":{"day":30,"month":6,"year":2012},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":73465,"idMal":43465,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/73465","startDate":{"day":30,"month":11,"year":2011},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Cherry Poppers","Вишнёвые хлопушки","Puchitto Hajiketa"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"ぷちっとはじけた、","romaji":"Puchitto Hajiketa,","userPreferred":"Puchitto Hajiketa,"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx168144-2SZDRncMzqEq.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx168144-2SZDRncMzqEq.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx168144-2SZDRncMzqEq.jpg"},"description":"Wanna play a game? The only catch is, you’re not just playing it, you’ve got to play your way out of it. That’s exactly what is happening to Bada. And he’s been at this for a while, trying to gather clues and items to find a way out of this damn horror RPG. The killer, the NPCs, the setting, Bada’s now familiar with them all. He’ll just have to endure a couple more games, maybe get killed a few more times… But in this session, Nam Doha, someone who Bada thought was just an NPC, is suddenly acting strange. Has he been another player this entire time? Bada has to be tortured to end this storyline and start over and Doha has volunteered to do it, but the look in his eyes suggests he has other, even more sinister intentions in mind… \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eWhat sadistic horrors must Bada endure to break free from this Dreadful Night?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin US)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Horror","Romance"],"id":168144,"idMal":185253,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":78,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/168144","startDate":{"day":9,"month":8,"year":2023},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Mörderiche Nacht","รัตติกาลสยองท่องเกมมรณะ"],"title":{"english":"Dreadful Night","native":"드레드풀 나잇","romaji":"Dreadful Night","userPreferred":"Dreadful Night"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":78,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx149092-XUnaAg4lRMWf.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx149092-XUnaAg4lRMWf.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx149092-XUnaAg4lRMWf.png"},"description":"Perhaps karma does exist. Han Nokyoung, an A-list actor with a foul attitude, winds up getting his just deserts when a video of him sleeping with LK Entertainment’s CEO, Kang Junil, surfaces on the internet. To make matters worse, Nokyoung soon becomes the victim of an acid attack, ending his career entirely. With even his boss and the man he loves, Jang Hyunjae, leaving his side, Nokyoung feels there’s nothing left for him anymore and takes his own life. But instead of waking up in the afterlife, Nokyoung finds himself three years in the past! Now determined to change the future, Nokyoung turns over a new leaf and tries not to get involved with either of the men that led to his downfall. However, when it comes to Kang Junil, Nokyoung’s fate might already be sealed…\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tappytoon)","endDate":{"day":9,"month":11,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":149092,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/149092","startDate":{"day":27,"month":4,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Otra Vez","重置"],"title":{"english":"Again","native":"다시","romaji":"Dasi","userPreferred":"Dasi"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":5,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx145390-s5rYNbeZDQ8h.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx145390-s5rYNbeZDQ8h.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx145390-s5rYNbeZDQ8h.png"},"description":"Shouya, a high school boy whose heart has never known romance, comes across an internet diary filled with wistful whispers of love toward the writer's same-sex crush. A photo posted to the page provides a hint as to the blog's owner: Tsubame, a fellow classmate known for being a lone wolf. Shouya realizes that his friend Ryuu is the object of the diary writer's affections, so he attempts to play matchmaker...but where will his own feelings take him in the process?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)","endDate":{"day":12,"month":8,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":145390,"idMal":143853,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/145390","startDate":{"day":14,"month":1,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["First Love Note"],"title":{"english":"Hatsukoi Note","native":"ハツコイノオト","romaji":"Hatsukoi Note","userPreferred":"Hatsukoi Note"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx134832-GrkjXyxSg1K9.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx134832-GrkjXyxSg1K9.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx134832-GrkjXyxSg1K9.jpg"},"description":"Kurahashi and Matsune had a casual relationship as friends with benefits. One day, Matsune and a woman visited the kimono shop where Kurahashi worked. Seeing Matsune's outgoing manner which was completely different from his usual personality, Kurahashi was delighted and made fun of him. Later, Kurahashi found out that the woman was actually Matsune's matchmaking partner. They continued their relationship after that, but...?","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":134832,"idMal":137323,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":79,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/134832","startDate":{"day":30,"month":9,"year":2017},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"チキンハートセレナーデ","romaji":"Chicken Heart Serenade ","userPreferred":"Chicken Heart Serenade "},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":11,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f15d78","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx132725-onWREHsjgDMs.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx132725-onWREHsjgDMs.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx132725-onWREHsjgDMs.jpg"},"description":"1. Takamine-ke no Nirinka ~Seed~; Comic ExE 9\u003cbr\u003e\n2. Takamine-ke no Nirinka ~Bloom~; Comic ExE 10\u003cbr\u003e\n3. Takamine-ke no Nirinka ~Lily~; Comic ExE 13\u003cbr\u003e\n4. Takamine-ke no Nirinka ~Iris~; Comic ExE 25\u003cbr\u003e\n5. Takamine-ke no Ichirinsou ~Gypsophila~; Comic ExE 27\u003cbr\u003e\n6. Takamine-ke no Sanrinsou ~Fruits~ (高嶺家の三輪草 〜Fruits〜, The Three Flowers of The Takamine House ~Fruits~)\u003cbr\u003e\n7. Shoka no Makuai de; COMIC Anthurium 2017-07\u003cbr\u003e\n8. Kaiten Eigyouchuu ~Afternoon Tea~; COMIC X-EROS #21\u003cbr\u003e\n9. Tousian e Youkoso!; COMIC X-EROS #17\u003cBR\u003e\n10. Last Summer; COMIC ExE 16\u003cBR\u003e\n10.5 Takamine-ke no Sanrinsou ~ampoule \"0\"~ (高嶺家の三輪草 〜ampoule 『0』〜, The Three Flowers of The Takamine House ~ampoule “0”~)","endDate":{"day":27,"month":2,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":132725,"idMal":142890,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":79,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/132725","startDate":{"day":27,"month":2,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Takamine-ke no Nirinka","Takamine-ke no Ichirinsou","Takamine-ke no Sanrinsou","Shoka no Makuai de","Kaiten Eigyouchuu","Tousian e Youkoso!","The Three Flowers of The Takamine House","The Anemone of the Takamine House","Between the Bookshelves ","Welcome to Tousian!"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"Garden","romaji":"Garden","userPreferred":"Garden"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":47,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1a150","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b115044-s2n2KTeN0gjn.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b115044-s2n2KTeN0gjn.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b115044-s2n2KTeN0gjn.jpg"},"description":"Ho-Jun’s recent breakup was pretty rough. His partner told him it wasn’t him, per se… Ho-Jun just wasn’t good in bed. But it turns out Drunk Ho-Jun is surprisingly resourceful; singlehandedly managing to find and set himself up with a sex tutor by the name of Mr. An. An Seung-Hyeon was only half serious when he posted the sex tutor ad, but he quickly finds himself in too deep to call the lessons off. And the more he sees Ho-Jun, the more he can’t help but notice how much attractive he is. Seung-Hyeon is making it up as he goes along, so what will the final exam look like? \u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin, edited)","endDate":{"day":26,"month":6,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":115044,"idMal":126440,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/115044","startDate":{"day":17,"month":7,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["gusticheo","굿티처","グッド・ティーチャー"],"title":{"english":"The Good Teacher","native":"굿 티처","romaji":"Good Teacher","userPreferred":"Good Teacher"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":15,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#c9f1f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx87094-jFDNS8iO7raF.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx87094-jFDNS8iO7raF.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx87094-jFDNS8iO7raF.jpg"},"description":"Up until now it’s always been cute girls laughing by my side. But now, sleeping next to me, full of faults, smelling of tobacco, a lascivious man. But he’s the cutest of them all...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nContinuation of Shuuna and Hayashida Kan's story. First chapter timeline is parallel with Renai-rubi no Tadashii Furikata, but told from Shuuna's POV.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes five extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":30,"month":1,"year":2018},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Psychological","Romance"],"id":87094,"idMal":94696,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/87094","startDate":{"day":30,"month":7,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["The Unraveling Monster","The Monster Exposed","坦露的怪物","解放的怪物","Obsessed with a Naked Monster","Potwór obnażony"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"はだける怪物","romaji":"Hadakeru Kaibutsu","userPreferred":"Hadakeru Kaibutsu"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":2},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/87092-tJ5pROYAIcJa.jpg","chapters":19,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#fea128","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx87092-WGkKidAulWve.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx87092-WGkKidAulWve.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx87092-WGkKidAulWve.jpg"},"description":"It’s Naoto’s first day of college, and the last person he expected to see was his high school ex Taichi, whom he’d dumped after a huge argument. Even though years have passed, Naoto finds he’s still steamed over some of the harsh words that were exchanged, but he also recognizes how much Taichi has matured since then and can’t help getting pulled back in. Will the discovery of his friend’s crush on Taichi fray the fragile threads of this mending relationship?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: SuBLime)","endDate":{"day":10,"month":7,"year":2018},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":87092,"idMal":93609,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/87092","startDate":{"day":6,"month":2,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["It's the Journey not the Destination","เอสเคปเจอร์นีย์","이스케이프 저니"],"title":{"english":"Escape Journey","native":"エスケープジャーニー","romaji":"Escape Journey","userPreferred":"Escape Journey"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":3},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/85610-Z1GP0W5NSNWX.jpg","chapters":14,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4d650","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx85610-ZwyRUMuw6ewD.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx85610-ZwyRUMuw6ewD.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx85610-ZwyRUMuw6ewD.jpg"},"description":"Konya mo Nemurenai spin-off series, focusing more on Gorou and Verde's relationship.\n","endDate":{"day":22,"month":11,"year":2016},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":85610,"idMal":80371,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/85610","startDate":{"day":22,"month":9,"year":2014},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Here on Out with You"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"キミトコレカラ","romaji":"Kimi to Kore kara","userPreferred":"Kimi to Kore kara"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":2},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":7,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#6b351a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx46061-Ixrn29U7X1Dp.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx46061-Ixrn29U7X1Dp.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx46061-Ixrn29U7X1Dp.jpg"},"description":"1. \u003cb\u003eNightS\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nMasato Karashima is a \"transporter\", a man paid to smuggle anything from guns to drugs to people. When he's hired by yakuza gang member Masaki Hozumi, he finds himself attracted to the older man, and what starts out as a business transaction quickly spirals into a cat-and-mouse game of lust and deception.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n2. \u003cb\u003eKanjou Spectrum\u003c/b\u003e (感情スペクトル, Emotion Spectrum)\u003cbr\u003e\nA high-school student tries to be a good wingman for a classmate, with an unexpected result.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n3-4. \u003cb\u003eReply\u003c/b\u003e (リプライ)\u003cbr\u003e\nTold from the alternating perspectives of an emotionally reserved salesman and the shy mechanic who's in love with him.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n5. \u003cb\u003eReply no Reply\u003c/b\u003e (リプライのリプライ, Reply of Reply)\u003cbr\u003e\n6. \u003cb\u003eSankagetsugo no Reply\u003c/b\u003e (三ヶ月後のリプライ, Three Months After Reply)\u003cbr\u003e\n7. \u003cb\u003eNight one month after\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nA short story that takes place one month before \u003ci\u003eAru Yoru: NightS\u003c/i\u003e, when Karashima visits Masaki for the first time after he discovers his whereabouts.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: SuBLime, edited)","endDate":{"day":11,"month":8,"year":2016},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Drama","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":46061,"idMal":16061,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/46061","startDate":{"day":1,"month":7,"year":2008},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Kanjou Spectrum","Reply","Emotion Spectrum","Reply of Reply","Sankagetsu Go no Reply","Three Months After Reply","Night One Month After"],"title":{"english":"NightS","native":"ナイツ","romaji":"NightS","userPreferred":"NightS"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx159928-eF05qiVM3TR5.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx159928-eF05qiVM3TR5.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx159928-eF05qiVM3TR5.jpg"},"description":"A series of hentai stories following the two protagonists of \u003ci\u003e1-nichi Goto ni Tsun ga Hetteku Tsuntsuntsuntsuntsuntsuntsuntsuntsuntsuntsundere Joshi\u003c/i\u003e.","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":159928,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":78,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/159928","startDate":{"day":31,"month":7,"year":2022},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"成人向けツンデレちゃん進捗報告","romaji":"Seijin Muke Tsundere-chan Shinchoku Houkoku","userPreferred":"Seijin Muke Tsundere-chan Shinchoku Houkoku"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/112687-DIXxMiz8Djvc.jpg","chapters":10,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4d60d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx112687-1jV9nIQ6X0GB.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx112687-1jV9nIQ6X0GB.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx112687-1jV9nIQ6X0GB.png"},"description":"1. \u003cb\u003eGoukaku H!\u003c/b\u003e (ごーかくえっち！); Comic Hotmilk 2017-03\u003cbr\u003e\n2. \u003cb\u003eNatsu to Jun\u003c/b\u003e (夏と純, Summer and Innocence); Comic Hotmilk 2019-01\u003cbr\u003e\n3. \u003cb\u003eKoiseyo Otome\u003c/b\u003e (恋せよ処女, 恋せよオトメ); Comic Hotmilk 2019-08\u003cbr\u003e\n4. \u003cb\u003eKago no Chuu, Kumo o shitau.\u003c/b\u003e (籠の蟲、蜘蛛を慕う。); Comic Hotmilk 2018-06\u003cbr\u003e\n5. \u003cb\u003eDaisuki.\u003c/b\u003e (大好き。, I love you); Comic Hotmilk 2019-05\u003cbr\u003e\n6. \u003cb\u003eKitto Onee-chan Yori...\u003c/b\u003e (きっとお姉ちゃんより…, No Doubt, Even Better Than Sis...); Comic Hotmilk 2017-10\u003cbr\u003e\n7. \u003cb\u003eSakyutto!\u003c/b\u003e (さきゅっと！); Comic Hotmilk 2018-10\u003cbr\u003e\n8. \u003cb\u003eNanka Ii Koto Atta?\u003c/b\u003e (なんかイイことあった？, Did something good happened?); Comic Hotmilk 2018-03\u003cbr\u003e\n9. \u003cb\u003eDanchou Onegaishimasu!\u003c/b\u003e (団長お願いします！); Comic Hotmilk 2017-08\u003cbr\u003e\n10. \u003cb\u003eWill you marry me?\u003c/b\u003e (Will you marry me？); kakioroshi","endDate":{"day":25,"month":9,"year":2019},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":112687,"idMal":124834,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/112687","startDate":{"day":25,"month":9,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Goukaku H!","Natsu to Jun","Koiseyo Otome","Kago no Chuu, Kumo o shitau.","Daisuki.","Kitto Onee-chan Yori...","Sakyutto!","Nanka Ii Koto Atta?","Danchou Onegaishimasu!","Will you marry me?","Summer and Innocence","I love you","No Doubt, Even Better Than Sis...","Did something good happened?"],"title":{"english":"I Love You","native":"君が好き。","romaji":"Kimi ga Suki.","userPreferred":"Kimi ga Suki."},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/109380-Cct04UUMMeRW.jpg","chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx109380-HU9SrzsEnao5.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx109380-HU9SrzsEnao5.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx109380-HU9SrzsEnao5.jpg"},"description":"Nine powerful gods of ancient Egypt are known as the Ennead. When the god of war, Seth, kills his brother Osiris to take over Egypt, he ushers in an era of chaos and cruelty under his rule. The other gods are unable to fight Seth’s power until centuries later, when a new challenger appears: Horus, the child of Isis. Horus is not yet even a full god, but he’s backed by other deities to dethrone Seth and bring an end to the many years of bloodshed. The conflict between Seth and Horus that begins as a series of trials warps into a complex web of deceit, obsession...and even desire.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Fantasy","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":109380,"idMal":131827,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/109380","startDate":{"day":20,"month":9,"year":2018},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["エネアド","ENNEAD九柱神"],"title":{"english":"ENNEAD","native":"엔네아드","romaji":"ENNEAD","userPreferred":"ENNEAD"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/39700-FbjQj4kRyW32.jpg","chapters":15,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#93280d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx39700-Rj86PPXYLF5y.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx39700-Rj86PPXYLF5y.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx39700-Rj86PPXYLF5y.jpg"},"description":"The story happens in a circus in Paris in the 1970's. (...) Much is made of the romance of the circus atmosphere, of flying through the air on a trapeze, etc etc. Think cirque here, not circus. We're doing Old World riffs on the romance and tawdriness of the ring. There are no elephants in tutus walking on their hind legs; it's slit-eyed jugglers and daring death-loving trapeze artists and sad Pierrot clowns, even if the Pierrot clown - our hero, Torinosu, 'Bird's Nest' - has a false red nose. The tawdriness comes from the circus master pimping out his performers to anyone willing to pay. (...) And there's tanbi decadence - ghosts who wander into the action looking like teenaged girls even if they're the hero's brother, and abandoned neurotic women with a thing for inflicting pain, and buracon and possible murder and unspoken pining and a hero who looks about to perish at any moment from terminal angst.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003ci\u003eNote: chapter count includes one prologue and one epilogue.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":2,"month":5,"year":2003},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Psychological","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":39700,"idMal":9700,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/39700","startDate":{"day":1,"month":8,"year":2001},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Copernicus' Breath","La Respiration de Copernic","The Respiration of Copernicus","La Respiración de Copérnico"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"コペルニクスの呼吸","romaji":"Copernicus no Kokyuu","userPreferred":"Copernicus no Kokyuu"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":2},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e46b0d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx31199-Blh83jPCM3MX.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx31199-Blh83jPCM3MX.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx31199-Blh83jPCM3MX.png"},"description":"Graduate student Souichi Tatsumi is demanding, violent, tyrannical... and a homophobe. So, it's unfortunate that his best assets are a beacon to the homosexual eye: his ass and crotch. Unfortunate, indeed--for both him and his underclassman -slash- lab assistant, Tetsuhiro Morinaga, who is hopelessly in love with those assets despite the threat to his own personal safety.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nMorinaga longs to tell Tatsumi how he feels, not to mention other longings... but, given Tatsumi's personality, Morinaga has a better chance of winning the lottery.","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":31199,"idMal":1199,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/31199","startDate":{"day":1,"month":1,"year":2004},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Koi Suru Boukun","Zakochany Tyran","사랑하는 폭군","Verliebter Tyrann"],"title":{"english":"The Tyrant Falls In Love","native":"恋する暴君","romaji":"Koisuru Boukun","userPreferred":"Koisuru Boukun"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#28aee4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx153899-eV2V2fNq1RBG.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx153899-eV2V2fNq1RBG.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx153899-eV2V2fNq1RBG.jpg"},"description":"Writer Mitsuru Hasegawa and Annaka Yuusei (a.k.a. Anna), who runs a real estate business, are childhood friends and lovers. They have a secret: Anna is a \"biter\" who feeds on human blood, and Mitsuru is a \"nectar\" whose blood the \"biter\" likes. The two signed a \"symbiotic contract\" in which they could not live without each other's blood. \nAnna, who had a crush on Mitsuru since he was young, was as happy as having his dream come true. However, at the same time, Anna also felt guilty for what he did to Mitsuru...\n  \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Taiyoh Tosho, translated)\n\u003cBR\u003e\u003cBR\u003e\n\u003cI\u003eNote: Includes one extra chapter.\u003c/I\u003e","endDate":{"day":18,"month":2,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":153899,"idMal":149968,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":78,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/153899","startDate":{"day":31,"month":5,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Smoky Nectar Renew","native":"スモーキーネクター Renew","romaji":"Smoky Nectar: Renew","userPreferred":"Smoky Nectar: Renew"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1c9bb","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx127419-bSSYqzFLUhM8.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx127419-bSSYqzFLUhM8.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx127419-bSSYqzFLUhM8.png"},"description":"Mitsuru Hasegawa is a reporter looking into an incident suspected to involve a vampire. Yusei Annaka, or Anna, a friend he's known since they were kids, warns him not to stick his nose in too deep. He should know―he's a vampire himself. Mitsuru agrees to let Anna suck his blood as part of his research, and one thing leads to an incredible experience. Mitsuru's about to learn a secret about himself he had never imagined...!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Renta!)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":18,"month":9,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Mystery","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":127419,"idMal":133899,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/127419","startDate":{"day":17,"month":1,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["蜜と煙","Mitsu to Kemuri"],"title":{"english":"Smoky Nectar","native":"スモーキーネクター","romaji":"Smoky Nectar","userPreferred":"Smoky Nectar"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/154626-4BhXEzE9OVdC.jpg","chapters":103,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4785d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx154626-iouXOmaMfO9h.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx154626-iouXOmaMfO9h.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx154626-iouXOmaMfO9h.jpg"},"description":"COVID has spread all over the world! Gwang-Ho, an intern, is deployed to 'Mermaid Village' by the sea in a time of medical shortage. One day, he sees a diver named Hye-Yeon naked on the beach. Since that day, he couldn’t stop thinking about her, and decides to do something about it.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003e\"I didn't know a diving suit could be so sexy...\"\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: TOPTOON+, edited)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":30,"month":7,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Hentai","Romance"],"id":154626,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/154626","startDate":{"day":13,"month":9,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Intern Girl","海女實習生"],"title":{"english":"Intern Diver","native":"인턴 해녀","romaji":"Intern Haenyeo","userPreferred":"Intern Haenyeo"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/151601-uDGktAuHZ8jT.jpg","chapters":121,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e49350","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx151601-gxVOd84himii.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx151601-gxVOd84himii.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx151601-gxVOd84himii.png"},"description":"He left a really negative review on a hentai game... Only to wake up as the main character! To make things worse, he will be killed by the god of games unless he gets all 6 girls in the game to fall for him! \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003e\"Damn it... Fine, I'll do whatever it takes to get all the girls!\"\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: DAYcomics)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Chapter count includes an epilogue.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":27,"month":10,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Drama","Fantasy","Hentai","Romance"],"id":151601,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/151601","startDate":{"day":23,"month":6,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Trapped in the Academy’s Eroge"],"title":{"english":"Trapped in a Hentai Game Academy","native":"아카데미 야겜에 빙의했다.","romaji":"Academy Yageme Binguihaessda.","userPreferred":"Academy Yageme Binguihaessda."},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":1,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1c9bb","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx150880-QjV6Er18SWQ8.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx150880-QjV6Er18SWQ8.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx150880-QjV6Er18SWQ8.jpg"},"description":null,"endDate":{"day":1,"month":6,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Hentai","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":150880,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/150880","startDate":{"day":1,"month":6,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"K子と病みおじ・番外編","romaji":"K-ko to Yamioji Bangai-hen","userPreferred":"K-ko to Yamioji Bangai-hen"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/129505-NqAAgwSQC5Yt.jpg","chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#5daee4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx129505-dnij1JMUTKIV.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx129505-dnij1JMUTKIV.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx129505-dnij1JMUTKIV.png"},"description":"All pure-hearted Mamoru Hishida wants is to live as a decent human being. So he can’t figure out why his life keeps spiralling out of control. Then one night, he happens upon a beautiful vampire who immediately recognizes him for what he truly is —an incubus—human hybrid, and on the brink of sexual starvation. The vampire strikes a bargain with Mamoru to become his familiar in exchange for a supply of sexual energy... But are familiars usually charged with attending manga conventions? Thus begins a strange romance between a virgin incubus and a sensual, manga-obsessed vampire.","endDate":{"day":14,"month":11,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance","Supernatural"],"id":129505,"idMal":134314,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":80,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/129505","startDate":{"day":25,"month":6,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Dreaming Vampire"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"ゆめみるヴァンパイア","romaji":"Yumemiru Vampire","userPreferred":"Yumemiru Vampire"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bba1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx108770-QBE54mqpQqw3.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx108770-QBE54mqpQqw3.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx108770-QBE54mqpQqw3.jpg"},"description":"\"I don't think you've realized your true nature yet.\" That's what Kon tells Iida, the hottest guy at school, wondering how anyone could be so proper. As popular as he is, Iida doesn't seem interested in any of the girls who come after him. Kon and his buddies try to look into the matter by flipping a coin and having Kon approach him with his confession of love, just to see if he's really interested in guys. \"I've... never looked at guys like that...\" says Iida, falling for Kon's ruse. Kon takes him home, hoping to straighten out the misunderstanding, when Iida suddenly grabs him by the shoulder, and... A story about a mysterious hottie at school and a prince of a certain kind. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Renta!)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003ci\u003eIncludes an extra.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":20,"month":6,"year":2019},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":108770,"idMal":124670,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/108770","startDate":{"day":11,"month":6,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"I Seriously Can't Believe You...","native":"君ってやつはこんなにも","romaji":"Kimitte Yatsu wa Konnanimo","userPreferred":"Kimitte Yatsu wa Konnanimo"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/98055-Erpey32copYA.jpg","chapters":58,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e41a43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/98055-4tm3vmbVHCve.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/98055-4tm3vmbVHCve.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/98055-4tm3vmbVHCve.jpg"},"description":"With rapid developments to the human civilization, the need for God and his angels have decreased at a significant rate. Thus, the angels are experiencing a historic unemployment crisis! With this problem in hand, God decides to start a company that will reduce the unemployment rate in both Heaven and Hell. He hereby founds the company, H\u0026H Roman Company!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin US)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes a prologue and five side story chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":13,"month":4,"year":2018},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Fantasy","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":98055,"idMal":125153,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/98055","startDate":{"day":24,"month":6,"year":2016},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Heaven \u0026 Hell Roman Company"],"title":{"english":"H\u0026H Roman Company","native":"천계지부 로망컴퍼니","romaji":"Cheongyejibu Roman Company","userPreferred":"Cheongyejibu Roman Company"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/97531-eOKFcyiJXjcP.jpg","chapters":1,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e48643","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx97531-KACnhr8seiix.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx97531-KACnhr8seiix.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx97531-KACnhr8seiix.jpg"},"description":"Growing up in an environment full of all kinds of animals, there's only one animal that Shouhei loves and that's rabbits. Because of his love for rabbits, he sometimes helps out in a rabbit specialist shop. And there, he meets Mito Itsuki, his unrequited love. However, he has a secret he has to keep no matter what. Would he be able to keep that secret in order to stay close to the one he loves…?!\n","endDate":{"day":14,"month":1,"year":2016},"format":"ONE_SHOT","genres":["Romance"],"id":97531,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/97531","startDate":{"day":14,"month":1,"year":2016},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"×××アレルギー","romaji":"XXX Allergy","userPreferred":"XXX Allergy"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/30769-iBLn5bcAJaeK.jpg","chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx30769-XUMJiI33mC0q.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx30769-XUMJiI33mC0q.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx30769-XUMJiI33mC0q.png"},"description":"Freelance photographer Akihito Takaba is captured by the very subject he’s been stalking in his viewfinder—the handsome and enigmatic crime lord Asami Ryuichi! The older man ravages him, both body and mind. Does this mean the end for the naive photographer, or will he live to shoot another day?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: SuBLime)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003cbr\u003e\n- Volume 1 includes the one-shot \"Risky Society (リスキーソサエティ)\"; BE×BOY GOLD 2002-02\u003cbr\u003e\n- Volume 1 includes the first part of the Koisuru Series \"Koisuru Shokubutsu (恋する植物)\"\u003cbr\u003e\n- Volume 2 includes the second part of the Koisuru Series \"Koisuru DNA (恋するDNA)\"; b-BOY LUV Vol. 1\u003cbr\u003e\n- Volume 3 includes the second part of the Koisuru Series \"Koisuru Baby Leaf (恋するベビーリーフ)\"\u003cbr\u003e\n- Volume 11 includes the two-part crossover story \"Koisuru Finder no Hyouteki (恋するファインダーの標的 | Target in the Viewfinder…in Love!)\"; Magazine BE×BOY 2009-12~2010-02\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Drama","Romance"],"id":30769,"idMal":769,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/30769","startDate":{"day":15,"month":5,"year":2001},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Viewfinder","Finder no Hyouteki Series","Finder no Ori","Finder no Sekiyoku","Finder no Ryoshuu","Finder no Shinjitsu","Finder no Netsujou","Finder no Katsubou","Finder no Mitsuyaku","Finder no Kodou","Finder no Mitsugetsu","Finder no Saihate","ファインダーの標的シリーズ","파인더 시리즈"],"title":{"english":"Finder","native":"ファインダーシリーズ","romaji":"Finder Series","userPreferred":"Finder Series"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":8,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4935d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx198313-2EVkJ8pAzRdv.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx198313-2EVkJ8pAzRdv.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx198313-2EVkJ8pAzRdv.jpg"},"description":null,"endDate":{"day":15,"month":7,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":198313,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":82,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/198313","startDate":{"day":27,"month":5,"year":2023},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"The Dangerous Convenience Store: Eui-joon's Dream","native":"위험한 편의점-의준이의 꿈 외전","romaji":"Wiheomhan Pyeonuijeom: Eui-Joon-ui Kkum Oejeon","userPreferred":"Wiheomhan Pyeonuijeom: Eui-Joon-ui Kkum Oejeon"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/158373-ijhvFyyIsPwL.jpg","chapters":63,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#d6865d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx158373-KPmOnHMSMUQM.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx158373-KPmOnHMSMUQM.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx158373-KPmOnHMSMUQM.jpg"},"description":"I thought going back in time or going into someone else's body was just imagination. However, I died in a sudden accident, and when I woke up again, I became a grandson of a rich man. My new life begins now. I'm going to be successful and seduce all successful women.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003e\"Boss, this is from me\"\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: DAYcomics)","endDate":{"day":7,"month":1,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Hentai","Romance"],"id":158373,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/158373","startDate":{"day":27,"month":11,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["The Secret Affairs Of The 3rd Generation Chaebol","二度目の人生、ハーレムモード"],"title":{"english":"Dirty Rich Secrets","native":"재벌3세의비밀사정","romaji":"Jaebeol 3-seui Bimilsajeong","userPreferred":"Jaebeol 3-seui Bimilsajeong"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":21,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4d65d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx145033-OyRRnpiyAeya.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx145033-OyRRnpiyAeya.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx145033-OyRRnpiyAeya.jpg"},"description":"Aoi and Ryouta have been friends for as long as they can remember, so when it comes time to head off to college, it only makes sense for them to room together! Practically joined at the hip, they are convinced that their relationship will stay the same forever...until one day, Aoi wakes up to find Ryouta leaning in to kiss him! Now Aoi must unpack this bewildering development, but he just can't seem to forget Ryouta's touch...\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes three extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":22,"month":11,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":145033,"idMal":144109,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/145033","startDate":{"day":28,"month":10,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["I Can't Stand It With My Childhood Friend","童年玩伴忍不住","เป็นเพื่อนสมัยเด็กต่อไปไม่ไหวแล้วครับ","Soyons plus qu'amis d'enfance !"],"title":{"english":"I Can't Stand Being Your Childhood Friend","native":"幼馴染じゃ我慢できない","romaji":"Osananajimi ja Gaman Dekinai  ","userPreferred":"Osananajimi ja Gaman Dekinai  "},"type":"MANGA","volumes":3},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f15d6b","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx141762-vtBt25vNzktg.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx141762-vtBt25vNzktg.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx141762-vtBt25vNzktg.jpg"},"description":"It's been a month since Mikado, an idol otaku worked to the bone by the design company he's employed at, has started dating his superior Anezaki. Even though they've finally gotten consecutive days off, since it feels like they're sex friends as they've just been holed up having sex, he wants to go on a date like normal lovers! Anezaki seems dissatisfied, but then he and Mikado go on a hot springs trip together.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Kaiohsha, translated)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes 2 extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":5,"month":3,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance"],"id":141762,"idMal":144249,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":80,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/141762","startDate":{"day":7,"month":3,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"俺と上司のかくしごと つづきのはなし","romaji":"Ore to Joushi no Kakushigoto: Tsuzuki no Hanashi","userPreferred":"Ore to Joushi no Kakushigoto: Tsuzuki no Hanashi"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/128976-L7WSYIboVlg0.jpg","chapters":92,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1bbae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx128976-hbMhs2CS2qte.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx128976-hbMhs2CS2qte.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx128976-hbMhs2CS2qte.jpg"},"description":"Bullied ruthlessly by girls in high school, Jinhoo’s done his best to put his past as a complete loser behind him. However, one day, he finds out that his newest tutee is his ex-bully, Yejin! Despite flunking the college entrance exam twice, Yejin’s only interested in her dildo and is adamant that she doesn’t need a tutor. However, as she starts to torture Jinhoo as per usual, Yejin realizes that there are some things that Jinhoo can teach her…but they’re going to have to find out the hard way.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Lezhin)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003e Note: Chapter count includes 35 after story chapters. \u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":30,"month":8,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Hentai","Romance"],"id":128976,"idMal":135034,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/128976","startDate":{"day":17,"month":11,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["生意気ギャルの家庭教師、始めます"],"title":{"english":"Learning the Hard Way","native":"일진녀 과외하기","romaji":"Iljinnyeo Gwaoehagi","userPreferred":"Iljinnyeo Gwaoehagi"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":7,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e44350","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx126836-ykNozMq5hfwr.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx126836-ykNozMq5hfwr.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx126836-ykNozMq5hfwr.jpg"},"description":"Hinata's a fox who's become the bride of Kyouya, a member of the wolf pack. Their tribes are bitter enemies, but this marriage should bring about peace.\nHinata's disguised as a female at the wedding and has ulterior motives for his soon-to-be husband: he plans to kill Kyouya, who's the son of the wolf pack's leader...\nThe night of their wedding, he tries to carry out the assassination, but Kyouya catches on and he fails.\nBecause he has nine tails, Hinata's even an outcast in his own pack and he decides to wants to die. But, instead of killing him, Kyouya says, \"It's time for our honeymoon\" and takes him prisoner...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThis is a dramatic inhuman story between an arrogant, self-centered wolf and a downtrodden yet very pretty and submissive fox.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Renta!)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":26,"month":6,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Fantasy","Romance"],"id":126836,"idMal":141398,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/126836","startDate":{"day":25,"month":7,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"The Beast's Bride","native":"バケモノの花嫁","romaji":"Bakemono no Hanayome","userPreferred":"Bakemono no Hanayome"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/125599-b0qVB09uc603.jpg","chapters":137,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1c9ae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx125599-NBH5kjjTr95I.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx125599-NBH5kjjTr95I.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx125599-NBH5kjjTr95I.png"},"description":"Straight-A student, a good social circle... Do-jun had no doubt that his campus life was going to be a breeze—until he reunites with Jae-hee, a friend he ghosted back in high school after he confessed his feelings for him. Well, their past shouldn't be that big of a deal, right? Everyone develops stupid crushes when they're in high school, and it seems like Jae-hee is over it anyway. Or at least, that's what Do-jun thought until Jae-hee offers a deal to him: \"Be my boyfriend for 4 weeks!\"\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin US)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003ci\u003e\nNote: Includes 12 extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":7,"month":9,"year":2025},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance"],"id":125599,"idMal":175687,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/125599","startDate":{"day":18,"month":6,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["4 semanas para enamorarte","4 Semaines pour t'aimer","Novios por 4 semanas","แฟนกัน 4 สัปดาห์"],"title":{"english":"4 Week Lovers","native":"4주 애인","romaji":"4-Ju Aein","userPreferred":"4-Ju Aein"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":7,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1bbae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx123209-swddOqZ6zhni.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx123209-swddOqZ6zhni.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx123209-swddOqZ6zhni.jpg"},"description":"\"How did you manage to hide this lewdness under that suit?\" Kudo is a successful elite office worker, but he's always been regretting he didn't know real love. When he meets younger - but daring and intriguing - carpenter Sato, he finds himself unable to resist the pleasure of being possessed by a man, even though, as a supposedly straight man, he feels he should find it demeaning. But, Sato doesn't hide that he's serious about Kudo, and pushes him to go one step beyond the tentative, fake relationships he's tried to build with women until now...?! A grown-up first love story, vividly awaking the feelings you discover when you seriously fall for someone for the first time in your life.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: futekiya)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":2,"month":10,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":123209,"idMal":131265,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/123209","startDate":{"day":20,"month":3,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Under My Skin 隱於此身皮囊下"],"title":{"english":"Under My Skin","native":"アンダーマイスキン","romaji":"Under My Skin","userPreferred":"Under My Skin"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":28,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bbae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx112366-3OhztfbloceP.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx112366-3OhztfbloceP.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx112366-3OhztfbloceP.jpg"},"description":"When homicide detective Dexter J. Daley’s testimony helps send his partner away for murder, the consequences—and the media frenzy—aren’t far behind. He soon finds himself sans boyfriend, sans friends, and, after an unpleasant encounter in a parking garage after the trial, he’s lucky he doesn’t find himself sans teeth. Dex fears he’ll get transferred from the Human Police Force’s Sixth Precinct, or worse, get dismissed. Instead, his adoptive father—a sergeant at the Therian-Human Intelligence Recon Defense Squadron, otherwise known as the THIRDS—pulls a few strings, and Dex gets recruited as a Defense Agent.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cBr\u003e\nDex is determined to get his life back on track and eager to get started in his new job. But his first meeting with Team Leader Sloane Brodie, who also happens to be his new jaguar Therian partner, turns disastrous. When the team is called to investigate the murders of three Humanitherian activists, it soon becomes clear to Dex that getting his partner and the rest of the tightknit team to accept him will be a lot harder than catching the killer—and every bit as dangerous.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cBr\u003e\n(Source: Dreamspinner Press)","endDate":{"day":20,"month":12,"year":2017},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Romance"],"id":112366,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":78,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/112366","startDate":{"day":5,"month":7,"year":2017},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Hell \u0026 High Water","native":"지옥의 끝에서","romaji":"Jiogui Kkeuteseo","userPreferred":"Jiogui Kkeuteseo"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/1964-p97GLXj9J0lW.jpg","chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f11a6b","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx31964-RvbwFoSgEneB.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx31964-RvbwFoSgEneB.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx31964-RvbwFoSgEneB.jpg"},"description":"\u003cb\u003e\u003cu\u003eVolume 1:\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n1-2. \u003cb\u003eDon't be Cruel, Please \u0026 Don't be Coldhearted, Please\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\"In exchange for me keeping your secret, take off your pants.\" Maya saw Nemugasa's sudden impulse to cheat on a test. In return for keeping silent, Maya makes various demands, but? The bookworm Nemugasa and the playboy Maya's perversions, impatience, and pure-hearted love.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n3. \u003cb\u003eHoukago no Himitsu\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nSequel to one of the side stories in Tsuyogari. Shiba Keisuke still loves his friend Aki and gets in trouble for daydreaming about him during class. They still desire to go further in their relationship, but when it comes to figuring out who should be on top, it's time to play rock-paper-scissors!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n4. \u003cb\u003eWagamama mo Aishite\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nDaijuu is a popular guy with a really moody and selfish boyfriend, Kan. Unfortunately, Kan's selfishness drives them to fighting, and to Kan wanting to be in control of their relationship, leaving Daijuu to try to take control as well.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n5-6. \u003cb\u003ePantsu de Ojama \u0026 Sailor Fuku wo Nuganaide\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nSoramoto is bothered by the fact he's wearing briefs when he goes home with his sex-friend, Hoshina. The reason for his embarrassment? Not too long ago he made fun of Hoshina for wearing briefs despite being a high school student, and has a great fear of being picked on for the same thing.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cb\u003e\u003cu\u003eVolume 2-3:\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nMaya and Nemugasa's story continues...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cb\u003e\u003cu\u003eVolume 4:\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nMaya and Nemugasa's relationship faces new challanges as they become university students. Also story about Jutta (Maya's cousin) and his relationship with his teacher.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cb\u003e\u003cu\u003eVolume 5-6:\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nMaya is being scouted by his university senpai and goes to part time job.\n","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance"],"id":31964,"idMal":1964,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/31964","startDate":{"day":15,"month":7,"year":2005},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Treat me gently, please","Don't be Coldhearted","อย่าโหดร้ายกับฉันนัก"],"title":{"english":"Don't Be Cruel","native":"酷くしないで","romaji":"Hidoku Shinaide","userPreferred":"Hidoku Shinaide"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/191732-xBV6uFGEVrGe.jpg","chapters":21,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1ae86","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx191732-WHkcNyDpT1JK.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx191732-WHkcNyDpT1JK.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx191732-WHkcNyDpT1JK.png"},"description":"Yeo Eun-Seong has always been popular—too popular. With his striking looks, he attracts attention from everyone, regardless of age or gender. But constant gossip and misunderstandings have left him deeply distrustful of people. The last thing he needs is to be popular amongst ghosts too!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nAfter moving into a new home for his job, Eun-Seong finds himself tormented by eerie paranormal activity night after night. One evening, while cowering outside his own apartment, he meets Seo Tae-Jeong, a passing office worker who—much to Eun-Seong’s surprise—can see and talk to ghosts. Desperate for peace, Eun-Seong enlists Tae-Jeong’s help to rid his house of its unwelcome guests. As the two work together, an unexpected and curious friendship begins to take shape… but is there more to Tae-Jeong than meets the eye?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Lezhin US)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes two side story chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":4,"month":8,"year":2025},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Supernatural"],"id":191732,"idMal":185056,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/191732","startDate":{"day":28,"month":4,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["¿Por qué esta Casa es tan Barata","這裡房租怎麼這麼便宜？","1LDK恋付き事故物件"],"title":{"english":"Love at First Fright","native":"이 매물 왜 이렇게 싸요?","romaji":"I Maemul Wae Ireoke Ssayo?","userPreferred":"I Maemul Wae Ireoke Ssayo?"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/163461-PtT9miT9QUOK.jpg","chapters":71,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#1a6be4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx163461-F5czqkVGHokC.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx163461-F5czqkVGHokC.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx163461-F5czqkVGHokC.jpg"},"description":"Han Juwon has the worst habit ever. He’s an average guy with an average college life, but his facial expression and words become terrifying the second he feels shy. Although he’s trying his best to fix it, Juwon realizes he messed up yet again when he says something rude to his hoobae, Jeong-min. And not only that, but he also keeps unintentionally touching Jeong-min’s chest every time they meet! Juwon knows he has to find a way to apologize to Jeong-min, but even while he feels guilty, he can’t stop thinking of what he accidentally discovered about Jeong-min’s chest… Turns out Juwon’s soft-hearted interior and gruff exterior aren’t the only things that are completely inverted…\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin US)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes two extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":12,"month":3,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance","Slice of Life","Sports"],"id":163461,"idMal":185228,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/163461","startDate":{"day":8,"month":6,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["HIGH CLEAR〜お前のハートにアタック〜","Überkopf-clear"],"title":{"english":"High Clear","native":"하이 클리어","romaji":"HIGH CLEAR","userPreferred":"HIGH CLEAR"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":nul