um/bx151890-V0pnQGeudhNh.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx151890-V0pnQGeudhNh.jpg"},"description":"He comes back to his hometown after 7 years, and finds himself stuck between beautiful girls! A sexy girl in a diving suit, and  his friend's mom with a mature body...!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003e\"Want to do things that we couldn't do before?\"\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: TOPTOON+)","endDate":{"day":6,"month":7,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Hentai","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":151890,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/151890","startDate":{"day":16,"month":6,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Childhood Bride","ハジけろ！夏の果実","幸福小島"],"title":{"english":"Childhood Friend","native":"소꿉친구","romaji":"Sokkupchingu ","userPreferred":"Sokkupchingu "},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/125430-2GcOtKe88Mx9.jpg","chapters":62,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1d6c9","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx125430-u4yCiJ2kBIoh.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx125430-u4yCiJ2kBIoh.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx125430-u4yCiJ2kBIoh.jpg"},"description":"\"Should I tell you the truth?” Ever since a traumatic incident caused him to lose all of his childhood memories, Tae-jun has been haunted by terrifying hallucinations and nightmares. While apartment hunting one day, a hallucination leads him to Yeon-woo, a handsome man who recognizes him immediately. But after moving into Yeon-woo's spare room, Tae-jun begins to have recurring nightmares of bloody, disembodied hands groping him… As an unexpected attraction grows between the two men, will Tae-jun be able to uncover the hidden secrets of his past? Or are some secrets better left untold?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tappytoon)","endDate":{"day":25,"month":5,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Mystery","Psychological","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":125430,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/125430","startDate":{"day":22,"month":4,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["暗室","เงาหลอน"],"title":{"english":"The Black Mirror","native":"검은 거울","romaji":"Geomeun Geoul","userPreferred":"Geomeun Geoul"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/108112-GjtlrvkCplud.jpg","chapters":16,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4785d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx108112-SFl6VkHyNGff.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx108112-SFl6VkHyNGff.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx108112-SFl6VkHyNGff.jpg"},"description":"1. \u003cb\u003e3Piece: Winter\u003c/b\u003e (3Piece -Winter-); Comic ExE 06\u003cbr\u003e\n2. \u003cb\u003e3Piece: Spring\u003c/b\u003e (3Piece -Spring-); Comic ExE 07\u003cbr\u003e\n3. \u003cb\u003e3Piece: Summer\u003c/b\u003e (3Piece -Summer-); Comic ExE 08\u003cbr\u003e\n4. \u003cb\u003e3Piece: Summer After\u003c/b\u003e (3Piece -Summer After-); Comic ExE 09\u003cbr\u003e\n5. \u003cb\u003e3Piece: Autumn\u003c/b\u003e (3Piece -Autumn-); Comic ExE 10\u003cbr\u003e\n6. \u003cb\u003e3Piece: After Party\u003c/b\u003e (3Piece -After Party-); kakioroshi\u003cbr\u003e\n7. \u003cb\u003e3Piece: Hitokakera\u003c/b\u003e (3Piece -ひとかけら-); Comic X-Eros #02\u003cbr\u003e\n8. \u003cb\u003e3Piece: Futakakera\u003c/b\u003e (3Piece -ふたかけら-); Comic X-Eros #03\u003cbr\u003e\n9. \u003cb\u003e3Piece: Sankakera\u003c/b\u003e (3Piece -さんかけら-); Comic X-Eros #06\u003cbr\u003e\n10. \u003cb\u003eSeejungfrau\u003c/b\u003e (Seejungfrau); Comic X-Eros #13\u003cbr\u003e\n