r/small/bx156218-O5f4bWlD2jQO.jpg"},"description":"Seung-Bin finds a room near campus, but he has to share it with a mysterious roommate. He's about to say hello... and finds a girl lying there!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003e\"She looks so pretty...!\"\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nHis boring life is about to change!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: DAYcomics)","endDate":{"day":4,"month":12,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Hentai","Romance"],"id":156218,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/156218","startDate":{"day":19,"month":10,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Bunk Beds","同居上下舖","二段ベッド"],"title":{"english":"Bunk Bed","native":"이층침대","romaji":"Icheungchimdae","userPreferred":"Icheungchimdae"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/144650-JQ1VuNv1FsJn.jpg","chapters":1,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1aea1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx144650-PG09MxAhWa8C.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx144650-PG09MxAhWa8C.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx144650-PG09MxAhWa8C.jpg"},"description":"A boy did not understand the hints of his tomboy childhood friend, and when he finally realizes that he also likes her, it was already too late, because someone else was ahead... But, but, but... the mother of the girl offers him to \"practice\" together so he can win her daughter over and steal her from her boyfriend, unaware that she has ulterior motives behind the offer.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003cbr\u003e\n- Digital version was delivered in Fanza (2021/12/03).\u003cbr\u003e\n- Physical version was published in Comic Market 99.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":3,"month":12,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":144650,"idMal":151958,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/144650","startDate":{"day":3,"month":12,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"スケベな娘の落とし方ドスケベなおばさんがシコんであげる","romaji":"Sukebe na Musume no Otoshi-kata Dosukebena Obasan ga Shikonde Ageru","userPreferred":"Sukebe na Musume no Otoshi-kata Dosukebena Obasan ga Shikonde Ageru"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1c9bb","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx138630-dqTs0ueOP2Ku.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx138630-dqTs0ueOP2Ku.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx138630-dqTs0ueOP2Ku.jpg"},"description":"He could never tell him the way he feels about him... but getting physical is different!! Keita is on the hunt for love, but he always seems to get dumped and end up fighting. Ryujiro (Ryu) is his friend since high school that he seeks refuge with, who tends to his wounds... the very guy who made Keita develop a habit of falling for straight guys, and Keita has been in love with him forever. Ryu is a nice guy who was willing to oblige Keita when he got drunk and said he might die if he didn't get horizontal with someone. He holds his hand and rocks him like a lover, so sweetly that Keita can't help getting the wrong idea...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Renta!)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":13,"month":11,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":138630,"idMal":139955,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/138630","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Hooked on Being Dumped","native":"失恋ジャンキー","romaji":"Shitsuren Junkie","userPreferred":"Shitsuren Junkie"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d6ae78","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx124848-G2GzOjBqCSuv.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx124848-G2GzOjBqCSuv.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx124848-G2GzOjBqCSuv.jpg"},"description":"Kiumi is a college student who's famous for being open about his orientation and an active top. Shizume, who's in the closet and the same class as Kiumi, doesn't like how to open Kiumi is about his adventures. One night, Shizume saves Kiumi, who almost gets tricked into becoming a male companion, by taking him to his room to hide. Except, Kiumi gets the wrong idea and thinks Shizume is looking for a one night stand! He comes on to Shizume, only to find out that Shizume is also a top, and away more sadistic one.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Renta!)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":124848,"idMal":131580,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/124848","startDate":{"day":28,"month":3,"year":2019},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Unexpected Attraction","native":"セックスドロップ","romaji":"Sex Drop","userPreferred":"Sex Drop"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":1,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e46b5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx107950-qkWTjudGwv8u.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx107950-qkWTjudGwv8u.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx107950-qkWTjudGwv8u.jpg"},"description":"Kippei pays a surprise visit to Honjou at the ryokan. Is Honjou happy to see him?\n","endDate":{"day":21,"month":10,"year":2018},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":107950,"idMal":130214,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/107950","startDate":{"day":21,"month":10,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Blue! Blue! Blue! dj - After Story"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"ブルー!ブルー!ブルー! After Story","romaji":"Blue! Blue! Blue!: After Story","userPreferred":"Blue! Blue! Blue!: After Story"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":11,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1d6c9","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx103078-xYl04yfZS7hU.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx103078-xYl04yfZS7hU.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx103078-xYl04yfZS7hU.png"},"description":"1. \u003cb\u003eSuccubus Stayed Life\u003c/b\u003e (サキュバステードライフ); Comic Market 87\u003cbr\u003e\nMatsukawa lived the life of a typical high schooler until a certain Touko Sakuramachi forcibly cohabited with him out of the blue. As it turns out, she was a succubus, and as all relationships with these creatures go, it’s semen for breakfast, lunch, and dinner.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n2. \u003cb\u003eSuccubus Stayed Life 2\u003c/b\u003e (サキュバステードライフ2); Comic Market 88\u003cbr\u003e\nMatsukawa’s cohabitation with Sakuramachi continues, often leading them down more adventurous acts of copulation during school hours or with all sorts of costumes and sex paraphernalia…\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n3. \u003cb\u003eSuccubus Stayed Life 3\u003c/b\u003e (サキュバステードライフ3); Comic Market 89\u003cbr\u003e\nA bespectacled girl named Akizono, who turns out to be another succubus,visits Matsukawa and ends up having sex with him, only to wind up getting caught by both Sakuramachi and Yomisawa…\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n4. \u003cb\u003eSuccubus Stayed Life 4\u003c/b\u003e (サキュバステードライフ4); Comic Market 90\u003cbr\u003e\nMatsukawa and Yomisawa begin to get more comfortable with one another to the point that they have sex regularly. But when Sakuramachi goes sex-crazy during her supposed period of ovulation, Matsukawa swears that he senses a hint of affection from her for the first time.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n5. \u003cb\u003eSuccubus Stayed Life 5\u003c/b\u003e (サキュバステードライフ5); Comic Market 91\u003cbr\u003e\nAfter finally getting a clubroom all to themselves, Matsukawa starts to spend some quality time alone with each of the girls. But when it comes to the clubroom and its activities, it’s pure orgy after orgy. With plans of summer camp coming up, looks like Matsukawa is gonna have to prepare himself — both physically and sexually — for what’s to come.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n6. \u003cb\u003eSuccubus Stayed Life 6\u003c/b\u003e (サキュバステードライフ6); Comic Market 92\u003cbr\u003e\nMatsukawa’s grades have been falling as of late, and as such he and the girls decide to lie low for a bit in order to concentrate on their studies. As a result, the pent up sexual urges burble to the surface as the three girls find their own ways of sneaking in a quickie or two in the most unlikely of places, save for Sakuramachi, who takes the demure route and serves as Matsukawa’s personal maid… or at least it appears so…\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n7. \u003cb\u003eSuccubus Stayed Life 7\u003c/b\u003e (サキュバステードライフ7); Comic Market 93\u003cbr\u003e\nSummer vacation has arrived and there's some time before the camp out. Time to take care of summer homework, time to sneak a few rounds of sex in at Yomisawa's house. At the library. Yomisawa and Sakuramachi even drag him off to a hotel for some quality time. With summer in full swing, the girls do everything they can to keep things heating up.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n8. \u003cb\u003eSuccubus Stayed Life 8\u003c/b\u003e (サキュバステードライフ8); Comic Market 94\u003cbr\u003e\nSummer is here, and with it Comiket! Matsukawa and his harem of succubi take a trip to Tokyo so the girls can show off their cosplay. Before that though comes an all night succubus fuck fest at the hotel, complete with sling bikinis, cat keyhole bras, and sex videos! And to top off their trip, the succubi are of course yearning to have sex in their cosplay outfits, especially after getting all excited from being hit on by men all day! Matsukawa needs not to worry though, for these three girls are loyal only to him.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n9. \u003cb\u003eSuccubus Stayed Life 9\u003c/b\u003e (サキュバステードライフ9); Comic Market 95\u003cbr\u003e\nTaking place immediately after their cosplay foursome, the girls continue to ravage Matsukawa with their insatiable libidos. Up to the very last minute of their stay, there's just no stopping the girls from having their way with him.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n10. \u003cb\u003eSuccubus Stayed Life 10\u003c/b\u003e (サキュバステードライフ10); Comic Market 97\u003cbr\u003e\nMatsukawa spends the remaining days of his summer break having lots of sex with Akizono and Miosawa.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n11. \u003cb\u003eSuccubus Stayed Life 11\u003c/b\u003e (サキュバステードライフ11)); Comic Market 104\u003cbr\u003e\nOne chapter, two stories! A secret classroom escapade and Matsukawa getting a very special pick-me-up after being down with a cold!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Fakku)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: A live-action AV adaptation (MIMK-076) was released on November 1st, 2020.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":30,"month":12,"year":2025},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":103078,"idMal":86918,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/103078","startDate":{"day":30,"month":12,"year":2014},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Living with Succubus","native":"サキュバステードライフ","romaji":"Succubus Stayed Life","userPreferred":"Succubus Stayed Life"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":5,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4935d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx87357-gqsIDYMiD5jA.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx87357-gqsIDYMiD5jA.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx87357-gqsIDYMiD5jA.jpg"},"description":"When his sister gets scammed, Tora takes it upon himself to save up enough to make the money she'd lost back. Responding to an ad looking for a \"hotel pick-up driver\" leads him into gay escort service \"Rain,\" where he gets assigned to Shiro, their biggest moneymaker. Tora says he isn't gay and definitely isn't interested in Shiro's services, but can he really knock it when he hasn't even tried it?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Futekiya)","endDate":{"day":27,"month":6,"year":2016},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama"],"id":87357,"idMal":96678,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/87357","startDate":{"day":26,"month":8,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["もッズ"],"title":{"english":"MODS","native":"MODS","romaji":"MODS","userPreferred":"MODS"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":8,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx87310-DlPxmFNgLTmY.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx87310-DlPxmFNgLTmY.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx87310-DlPxmFNgLTmY.png"},"description":"On his way home from picking up a matching set of rings for himself and his lover, Fuji Takahiro is hit by a car. The following amnesia degrades his live-in lover Kotou Tarou to a mere flatmate, and a series of misunderstandings threatens to tear the couple apart. Tossed around by desperation and confusion, can Tarou and Takahiro rebuild their once blissful relationship?\n","endDate":{"day":25,"month":12,"year":2015},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":87310,"idMal":99316,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/87310","startDate":{"day":25,"month":4,"year":2014},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"No Matter How Many Times It Takes","native":"もういちど、なんどでも。","romaji":"Mou Ichido, Nando Demo.","userPreferred":"Mou Ichido, Nando Demo."},"type":"MANGA","volumes":2},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1d6c9","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx178021-298cR8CZY6kQ.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx178021-298cR8CZY6kQ.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx178021-298cR8CZY6kQ.jpg"},"description":"College student Gen, a guitarist for the rock band Eve, meets a man named Mike while playing at one of his gigs. Mike’s the kind of person who has no trouble saying what’s on his mind, and Gen soon finds himself captivated by the smooth talker’s voice. The next day, the two meet again when they realize they go to the same college. Be it on stage or just during casual conversation, Gen finds himself more and more captivated by Mike’s voice, and the more time the two spend together, the more Gen realizes it’s more than just Mike’s voice he’s attracted to…\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Kodansha USA)","endDate":{"day":28,"month":4,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Music","Romance"],"id":178021,"idMal":170531,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":78,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/178021","startDate":{"day":28,"month":10,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Shout Loud, My Heart","native":"シャウト・ラウド・マイハート","romaji":"Shout Loud My Heart","userPreferred":"Shout Loud My Heart"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#aed6e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/fi