n(Source: Shinshokan, translated)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":146432,"idMal":144143,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/146432","startDate":{"day":30,"month":9,"year":2021},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"セブンティーンシロップス","romaji":"Seventeen Syrups","userPreferred":"Seventeen Syrups"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#bb1a5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx134666-qXH1aSdyOSks.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx134666-qXH1aSdyOSks.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx134666-qXH1aSdyOSks.jpg"},"description":"Kou and Maki have been best friends since preschool. Fifteen years later, they are both delinquents that somehow end up in fights. Kou is cool, stoic, and always hangs around Maki. A running skit among their friends is that Kou and Maki are an item and that Kou is head over heels for his pink-haired partner. But... does that joke hold any truth in reality?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Futekiya)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":10,"month":2,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Comedy"],"id":134666,"idMal":139954,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/134666","startDate":{"day":25,"month":11,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["I'll Make You Cry, Yankee-kun","Nakasete Yaruyo Yankee-kun","让你哭噢小混混"],"title":{"english":"I'll Make You Cry","native":"啼かせてやるよヤンキーくん","romaji":"Nakasete Yaru yo Yankee-kun","userPreferred":"Nakasete Yaru yo Yankee-kun"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4a15d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx111244-wKhQBJyr7re0.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx111244-wKhQBJyr7re0.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx111244-wKhQBJyr7re0.jpg"},"description":"Naoki Oikawa was busily fapping away to his naughty porn mags when he was suddenly transported to a fantasy world filled with demon lords, monsters, and… sexy babes? Join the ostensible MC-turned-hero as he helps his comrades defeat the demon lord by using the power of his own semen!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Fakku!)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Fantasy","Hentai"],"id":111244,"idMal":111930,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":79,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/111244","startDate":{"day":31,"month":12,"year":2017},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Tales of a Harem in Another World","native":"異世界ハーレム物語","romaji":"Isekai Harem Monogatari","userPreferred":"Isekai Harem Monogatari"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/128724-YC8IrGtFZquS.jpg","chapters":101,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4d65d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx128724-FDonr0KeVnbC.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx128724-FDonr0KeVnbC.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx128724-FDonr0KeVnbC.jpg"},"description":"Han-Soo is an aspiring civil servant, preparing for the civil service exam. One day, he runs into his first love, Ji-Yeon, who also is preparing for an exam. She is joining a notorious \"study club\" for hookups.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: TOPTOON+, edited)","endDate":{"day":19,"month":2,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Hentai","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":128724,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/128724","startDate":{"day":10,"month":4,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Shall we study at Noryangjin?","Noryangjin","Should I Study at Noryangjin?","セクスタディ"],"title":{"english":"Studying in NORYANGJIN","native":"노량진에서 스터디 할까?","romaji":"Noryangjineseo Study Halkka?","userPreferred":"Noryangjineseo Study Halkka?"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/143637-sMKQRfwmP10A.jpg","chapters":83,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e44335","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b143637-w0yWBN0GRoNV.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b143637-w0yWBN0GRoNV.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b143637-w0yWBN0GRoNV.jpg"},"description":"Cheong-Ho is a national swim team member who has been struggling with poor records. As an alpha, his physical condition could be improved greatly through sex with an omega, but he has a fear of omega pheromones. His hopes of being a top swimmer seem to be sinking, but that all changes when he meets Yi-Rim, an omega whose pheromones don’t give off any scent. Yi-Rim is only too happy to help Cheong-Ho out, and thus the two of them start a purely physical relationship. It’s almost like they’re a match made in heaven. But…why is it so hard for them to close the distance between each other?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin US)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes 33 extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":25,"month":11,"year":2025},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":143637,"idMal":152130,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/143637","startDate":{"day":20,"month":6,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Surge Looking for You","Waves Looking for You"],"title":{"english":"Surge Towards You","native":"너를 찾는 파도","romaji":"Neoreul Channeun Pado","userPreferred":"Neoreul Channeun Pado"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/124613-q6ViiROr3XGy.jpg","chapters":107,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e44343","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx124613-TGw3BxuD0J07.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx124613-TGw3BxuD0J07.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx124613-TGw3BxuD0J07.jpg"},"description":"Born into a family of handsome, wealthy, and well-educated alphas, Woo-Young always expected he would be the same. Come to find out, he was the odd man out as the lone omega, and not even a perfect one at that. To compensate, Woo-Young goes through life pretending to be a beta, but when he begins to experience hormone imbalances, irregular heat cycles, and a distinct lack of control over his impulses, his lowly recessive omega status becomes impossible to ignore. That’s when he meets Kyung-Ju, a powerful and successful dominant alpha who can turn him into a true omega, and also makes him weak in the knees. Now, Woo-Young must use every tactic there is to court Kyung-Ju and make the brooding alpha his very own.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tappytoon)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Chapter count includes a prologue and 23 side story chapters. \u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":7,"month":6,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance"],"id":124613,"idMal":166092,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/124613","startDate":{"day":11,"month":4,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["How to Chase an Alpha","Como Atraer a ese Alfa","Como Conquistar Um Alfa"],"title":{"english":"How to Snag an Alpha","native":"그 알파를 꼬시는 법","romaji":"Geu Alpha-reul Kkosineun Beop","userPreferred":"Geu Alpha-reul Kkosineun Beop"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":6},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/122837-TwQIkky1JNZU.jpg","chapters":65,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d86","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx122837-bdPPlyG1LNlZ.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx122837-bdPPlyG1LNlZ.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx122837-bdPPlyG1LNlZ.jpg"},"description":"Mongryong is having what we’ll call... a tough time. His sister’s having an affair with a married man, and the guy’s wife is the older sister of a major mob boss. To make matters worse, Mongryong's sister’s boyfriend’s wife’s brother decides to take him hostage as bait to lure the lovers out of hiding. Will the madness never end?! ...Still, maybe—JUST maybe—Mongryong can convince his captor to go easy on him. Just not TOO easy. After all, there's nothing wrong with playing a little rough either.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eChapter count includes 5 special chapters.\u003ci\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{"day":2,"month":11,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":122837,"idMal":185063,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/122837","startDate":{"day":1,"month":5,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Um Bando de Loucos","粉色疯子","Madman Combo"],"title":{"english":"Assorted Wildness","native":"미친놈 종합세트","romaji":"Michinnom Jonghapseteu","userPreferred":"Michinnom Jonghapseteu"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":7,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx117857-fI9KOnrJ5m1V.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx117857-fI9KOnrJ5m1V.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx117857-fI9KOnrJ5m1V.png"},"description":"Kasumi and Kyousuke are polar opposites when it comes to personality. Kasumi is reserved, soft-spoken and shy; Kyousuke is energetic and has always been popular among their peers. As the saying goes though, opposites have a tendency to attract, and these two have been fast friends since elementary school. To Kasumi, Kyousuke has always been a hero to look up to, someone who supports him and saves him from the bullies. But now, school is over; their relationship suddenly becomes a lot less simple to describe. Facing the world—and one another—as adults, both men find there are things they struggle to say out loud, even to each other. \n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tokyopop)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes an extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":28,"month":2,"year":2019},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":117857,"idMal":124362,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/117857","startDate":{"day":28,"month":4,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["I Can't Say Anything To You","No te lo puedo decir"],"title":{"english":"There Are Things I Can't Tell You","native":"キミに言えないことがある","romaji":"Kimi ni Ienai Koto ga Aru","userPreferred":"Kimi ni Ienai Koto ga Aru"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":18,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e486bb","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx96554-Z0LckZ2rVS2k.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx96554-Z0LckZ2rVS2k.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx96554-Z0LckZ2rVS2k.jpg"},"description":"Suou and Ryou have been friends since childhood. The hairstylist and writer have lived together for six years now and, though they definitely aren’t dating, their close relationship is hard to define. Will they ever move beyond the nebulous territory of “more than friends” or will they keep living in a stalemate forever?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)","endDate":{"day":20,"month":5,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":96554,"idMal":95105,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/96554","startDate":{"day":21,"month":11,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["안티 로망스"],"title":{"english":"Anti-Romance","native":"アンチロマンス","romaji":"Anti Romance","userPreferred":"Anti Romance"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":2},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/84505-WT87aqSovQMA.jpg","chapters":12,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d65d1a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx84505-U8vVWRmhur1Y.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx84505-U8vVWRmhur1Y.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx84505-U8vVWRmhur1Y.jpg"},"description":"A guy by the name of Kuroda-sensei is given a job as the new coach/adviser of the girls lacrosse club in an all female school called Felinus Academy for Girls but... it turns out to be a bumpy ride as he encounters sex fiends among the squad, and his adventures begins as he attempts to gain their respect as adviser.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n1-6. \u003cb\u003eChapter #1 - #6\u003c/b\u003e (第1話 - 第6話); Comic X-Eros #01, #02, #06, #08, #10, #12\u003cbr\u003e\n* 7. \u003cb\u003e2nd Season!?\u003c/b\u003e (2nd Season!?); Wanimagazine Comics Special \"Anekomori\" kakioroshi\u003cbr\u003e\n* 8. \u003cb\u003eOmake Manga Kumiko-hen\u003c/b\u003e (おまけ漫画久美子編); Joshi Luck! Toranoana Kounyuu Tokuten Shousasshi\u003cbr\u003e\n9. \u003cb\u003eBangai-hen\u003c/b\u003e (番外編); Comic X-Eros #13\u003cbr\u003e\n* 10. \u003cb\u003eAkagi Aya Massage-hen\u003c/b\u003e (赤城綾 マッサージ編); Comic Kairakuten 2014-05\u003cbr\u003e\n* 11-12. \u003cb\u003eAfter School\u003c/b\u003e (After School); Comic X-Eros #19, #21\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: (*) Chapters included in the new edition published on 2018/11/24.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":30,"month":5,"year":2015},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai","Romance","Sports"],"id":84505,"idMal":54505,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/84505","startDate":{"day":26,"month":11,"year":2012},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Jyoshi Luck!","Joshi Lac!","Girls Lacrosse Club"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"じょしラク！","romaji":"Joshi Luck!","userPreferred":"Joshi Luck!"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/44498-7kRbwZzcKeiE.jpg","chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1f1c9","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx44498-vCyKYNwZP4Gj.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx44498-vCyKYNwZP4Gj.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx44498-vCyKYNwZP4Gj.jpg"},"description":"In a run-down city riddled with poverty and gangs, survival is a daily struggle for Yuki and his best friend Tetsu. Selling fake drugs in shady back alleys doesn't make them much money, so in a desperate attempt to pay for Yuki's sick brother's hospitalization, the two of them get caught trying to break into the vault of the Seidoukai – an infamous yakuza group. However, Yuki catches the eye of the gang's young boss, Kazutaka Hyoudo, and the two of them escape imminent death after striking a deal.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nHyoudo is willing to take care of the hospital bills – for a price. A weekly visit to his office doesn't seem like much to pay, but as tensions grow between the Seidoukai and another power-hungry gang, will Yuki and Tetsu be caught up in the resulting fallout?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: TOKYOPOP)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Drama","Psychological"],"id":44498,"idMal":14498,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/44498","startDate":{"day":22,"month":3,"year":2008},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":["アシッド タウン","Город кислоты"],"title":{"english":"Acid Town","native":"ACID TOWN","romaji":"ACID TOWN","userPreferred":"ACID TOWN"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/197386-8CqZj3DnCe4d.jpg","chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx197386-m2FyMYKU0rGY.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx197386-m2FyMYKU0rGY.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx197386-m2FyMYKU0rGY.jpg"},"description":"Jang Baek-Hee is counting the days until he can escape Gicheon before his deadbeat father is released from prison. But then Yang Il-Woo arrives: a delinquent transfer student with a cheap perm, brassy hair, and a loneliness that mirrors Baek-Hee’s own. Slowly, their uneasy friendship deepens into something tender. But Il-Woo came to Gicheon with a secret that could shatter the fragile comfort they've both found in each other. And when the past comes calling, can two broken souls survive the truth?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":197386,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":85,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/197386","startDate":{"day":11,"month":8,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Yang Il-woo and I ","我與楊一宇"],"title":{"english":"Yang Ilwoo and Me","native":"양일우와 나","romaji":"Yang Il-Woo-wa Na","userPreferred":"Yang Il-Woo-wa Na"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":1,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d68650","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx134771-KlXIrMnUIuXS.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx134771-KlXIrMnUIuXS.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx134771-KlXIrMnUIuXS.jpg"},"description":"Set after the events of the main story, Asako and Kotaro stopped using birth control as they wish to have a child.","endDate":{"day":6,"month":6,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":134771,"idMal":142834,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/134771","startDate":{"day":6,"month":6,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["The Childmaking Book"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"こどもつくる本","romaji":"Kodomo Tsukuru Hon","userPreferred":"Kodomo Tsukuru Hon"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/132120-r9bqoaCNjx9s.jpg","chapters":128,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#5dbbe4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx132120-5v7WxbDvm2Aq.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx132120-5v7WxbDvm2Aq.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx132120-5v7WxbDvm2Aq.jpg"},"description":"Do-Won has a problem. His neighbor, Beom, seems awfully rude, but he’s infuriatingly gorgeous. And the completely ridiculous cherry on top? Beom turns out to be Do-Won’s all-time favorite camboy, which only adds to the (sexual) frustration. Beom is a metaphorical pain in Do-Won’s ass, and Do-Won would like to return the favor physically, thank you very much. So, Do-Won has a problem—in his pants. The question is, how is he going to solve it? You’ll find out the answer if you crank the volume up, and watch very, very closely…\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin)","endDate":{"day":13,"month":3,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":132120,"idMal":150815,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/132120","startDate":{"day":31,"month":3,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["I can hear it without a microphone","Maikeu Eobs-ido Deullyeo","隔壁鄰居直播中","フルボリューム！~マイクなしでも聞こえる~","フルボリューム！"],"title":{"english":"Full Volume","native":"마이크 없이도 들려","romaji":"Mic Eobsido Deullyeo","userPreferred":"Mic Eobsido Deullyeo"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/119909-d7DXMUuuKLgY.jpg","chapters":64,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f135d6","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx119909-K5t2WM90IzoU.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx119909-K5t2WM90IzoU.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx119909-K5t2WM90IzoU.png"},"description":"A charming young man with a job at one of the top firms in Korea, Pa-Ram is a catch by everyone’s standards. However, he has a couple secrets that could topple his hard-won elite status: Pa-Ram is gay, and has an oversensitive body that gets turned on at the slightest touch. So far, he’s coped by hiding his crush on his boss and taking care of “emergencies” in the office bathroom. But one day, he’s caught redhanded by the new personal trainer at the company gym. Will this hot, smirking jock ruin Pa-Ram's life, or turn out to be his remedy?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin) \u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Chapter count includes 7 extras and an epilogue. \u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":16,"month":7,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":119909,"idMal":135883,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/119909","startDate":{"day":24,"month":1,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["ANTI P.T〜今日から俺はアンチになる!?〜","Anti Personal Trainer","Abbasso il personal trainer","今日から俺はアンチになる!?","反对PT","拒绝私教"],"title":{"english":"ANTI P.T.","native":"안티피티","romaji":"ANTI P.T.","userPreferred":"ANTI P.T."},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/n106250-MjVj9bAfIQqn.jpg","chapters":49,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4785d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/n106250-HOHzH6eZ0zuB.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/n106250-HOHzH6eZ0zuB.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/n106250-HOHzH6eZ0zuB.png"},"description":"Sangho’s deadline for his PhD thesis is looming near and his future is looking murky. The highlight of his day is smoking on the rooftop of his school building, where, for a few blissful minutes, he can forget about his troubles. But his precious cigarette break is ruined one day by a guy named Hakdo and his bawling ex-boyfriend (who also happens to be Sangho’s ex-ex-ex-boyfriend). What’s more, Sangho later learns that he and Hakdo have not one but many exes in common. This gets them talking and the two agree to have some fun, casual sex. But little does Sangho know that Hakdo’s idea of fun is very different from his...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Lehzin)","endDate":{"day":22,"month":4,"year":2019},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":106250,"idMal":151870,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/106250","startDate":{"day":22,"month":12,"year":2017},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Playtime with Hakdo","native":"학도가 좋아하는 랜덤플레이","romaji":"Hakdoga Joahaneun Raendeompeullei","userPreferred":"Hakdoga Joahaneun Raendeompeullei"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/104449-9f8yf3xrUTgh.jpg","chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx104449-HupiskHd11wG.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx104449-HupiskHd11wG.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx104449-HupiskHd11wG.jpg"},"description":"1. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou 1 Obata Yui to Tachibana Daiki no Baai\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導1 小幡優衣と橘大貴の場合), Comic Market 90\u003cbr\u003e\nUsing hypnosis, Tanaka appoints himself the school's Sexual Counselor, in charge of training the girls of his school how to have sex, all while their boyfriends are watching!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n2. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou 2 Kurashiki Reina no Baai\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導2 倉敷玲奈の場合), Comic Market 91\u003cbr\u003e\nTanaka's adventures continue as he uses his talents to bring Reina, one of the most popular girls at his school, down a peg or two!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n3. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou 2.5 Keika Kansatu\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導 2・5 経過観察), COMIC1☆11\u003cbr\u003e\nThis busty blonde is looking to get better at sex for her boyfriend, and what better way then to engage in some \"sexual counseling\" in the men's bathroom for a crowd. Wait, isn't this just sex? N-No, that can't be...\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n4. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou 2.75 Taiken Shidou\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導 2.75 体験指導), Comic Market 92\u003cbr\u003e\nTanaka generously offers to train even the girls who lack boyfriends, indulging in a variety of girls and teaching them about sex.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n5. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou 3 Miyajima Sakura to Kase Masafumi no Baai\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導 3 宮島桜と加瀬正文の場合), Comic Market 93\u003cbr\u003e\nTanaka's attentions turn to Sakura Miyajima, president of the kendo club, who begs him to teach her how to get pregnant!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n6. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou 4 Ninshin Taiken Shidou (Shi)\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導 4 妊娠体験指導(試)), Comic Market 94\u003cbr\u003e\nContinuing from the events of Hypnotic Sexual Counseling 3, self-elected school sexual counselor Hajime continues his pursuit of Sakura by persuading her to prepare herself for a future of childbearing. When it comes to the point that he is even brought to Sakura's house in order to update her parents on their daughter's progress, Hajime begins to get ideas on his next target after seeing an all-but-alluring Mrs. Miyajima.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNOTE: This is the first part of two in the fourth installment to the mainline stories of the Hypnotic Sexual Counseling series.\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n7. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou Kurashiki Reika no Baai\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導 倉敷麗華の場合), Comic Market 95\u003cbr\u003e\nReina's mother, Reika, is displeased to fine her daughter fraternizing with the self-proclaimed sexual guidance counselor, Hajime. More than simply unimpressed with his general appearance, Reika doubts his capabilities in sex in general, and so decides to test him through a physical show of prowess. Needless to say, Hajime is more than up for the challenge, but will he be able to meet Reika's strict expectations?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n8. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou Nozaki Yuu no Baai\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導 野崎悠の場合), COMIC1☆15\u003cbr\u003e\nHer name is Yuu Nozaki, the so-called \"Sleeping Beauty\" of the academy. Her nonchalance and grace belie her sloth-like attitude towards life. With this in mind, self-proclaimed school sexual counsellor Hajime Tanaka takes it upon himself to instruct the unassuming Yuu regarding the pleasures of sexual intercourse and what makes sexual relationships so great.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n9. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou 4: Ninshin Taiken Shidou\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導4 妊娠体験指導); Comic Market 96\u003cbr\u003e\nHajime Tanaka isn't done with the women of the Miyajima household, this time hypnotizing both mother and daughter to take part in his twisted scheme of teaching Sakura what it means to become pregnant. Using her own mother, Tsubaki, as a visual aid, Tanaka proceeds to inseminate both mother and daughter in the awesome conclusion of the fourth chapter of the Hypnotic Sexual Counseling series.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n10. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou Obata Natsumi no Baai\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導 小幡夏美の場合); Comic Market 97\u003cbr\u003e\nHajime Tanaka visits the house of Yui Obata, only to be informed by her mother, Natsumi Obata, that she is out for the day. Good thing Tanaka's real purpose for visiting was to supplement his Sexual Counseling services for Yui by \"examining\" her own mother. It's all-in-a-day's work for our resident hypnotic sexual counseling expert as he adds yet another mother to his growing collection of women.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n11. \u003cb\u003eSaimin Seishidou 5 Hiiragi Suzuka\u003c/b\u003e (催眠性指導5 柊鈴香)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: fakku)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":104449,"idMal":104219,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":78,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/104449","startDate":{"day":14,"month":8,"year":2016},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Hypnosis Sex Guidance","Training Session One: Yui Obata And Daiki Tachibana","Training Session Two: Reina Kurashiki","Personal Guidance","Pregnancy Guidance Experience","Reika Kurashiki's Case","Yuu Nozaki","Natsumi Obata"],"title":{"english":"Hypnotic Sexual Counseling","native":"催眠性指導","romaji":"Saimin Seishidou","userPreferred":"Saimin Seishidou"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/98245-rVBFf8ZVgQ2z.jpg","chapters":88,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx98245-LBVU2Gm3Ojns.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx98245-LBVU2Gm3Ojns.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx98245-LBVU2Gm3Ojns.jpg"},"description":"“From my earliest memory until now, there wasn't a single moment where I didn't like you.” Eunho Jung proposed to Jaeha Yoo, the older boy next door, for the first time when he was three. It stopped being cute when he confessed his feelings again in high school, and once Jaeha got married, the two lost touch. They're reunited by chance years later, Eunho as a university student, and Jaeha, a jaded divorcee. Eunho's determined to prove he’s not a kid anymore, but does Jaeha’s self-destructive spiral allow for feelings?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tapas) \u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: The chapter count includes a prologue, 12 side story chapters, 2 special chapters and an epilogue previously self-published as a Christmas side story.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":24,"month":12,"year":2019},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":98245,"idMal":150854,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/98245","startDate":{"day":10,"month":7,"year":2016},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["爱慕的少年","Любовник","恋スル少年"],"title":{"english":"Lover Boy","native":"사랑하는 소년","romaji":"Saranghaneun Sonyeon","userPreferred":"Saranghaneun Sonyeon"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":5},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":10,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4435d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx87463-VcQGja1iG8N5.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx87463-VcQGja1iG8N5.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx87463-VcQGja1iG8N5.png"},"description":"Completely disarmed by Minori, gang leader Tatsuyuki Oyamato is sent down to Fukuoka to expand the family's territory in Kyushu, with the hidden intention of revitalizing himself. However, after arriving in Fukuoka, the dismayed Tatsuyuki is still distraught. Completely drunk and lying in a park, he's taken home by someone and treated to an evening of his wildest desires.\n\u003cbr\u003e \u003cbr\u003e(Source: Renta!)","endDate":{"day":30,"month":7,"year":2015},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Psychological","Romance"],"id":87463,"idMal":93122,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/87463","startDate":{"day":null,"month":12,"year":2014},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Fourth Generation Head: Tatsuyuki Oyamato","Show me your Gun","Czwarty: Tatsuyuki Oyamato","Tatsuyuki Ooyamato: Líder de la Cuarta Generación","그남자, 타츠유키","Yondaime Ôyamato Tatsuyuki"],"title":{"english":"Tatsuyuki Oyamato the 4th","native":"四代目・大和辰之","romaji":"Yondaime Ooyamato Tatsuyuki","userPreferred":"Yondaime Ooyamato Tatsuyuki"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":17,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4436b","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx86128-fWTqIK3yGKOO.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx86128-fWTqIK3yGKOO.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx86128-fWTqIK3yGKOO.jpg"},"description":"Shinji Kanou is madly in love with his older married neighbour, Yumi Mishima. One day Yumi suddenly comes onto Shinji leaving him confused. The next day, he meets Yumi with her single twin sister, Nami.","endDate":{"day":27,"month":6,"year":2015},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":86128,"idMal":65453,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/86128","startDate":{"day":28,"month":12,"year":2012},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Twin Milf","native":"ツインミルフ","romaji":"Twin Milf","userPreferred":"Twin Milf"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":2},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":7,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4a11a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx59185-jWKXKqKqkQd0.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx59185-jWKXKqKqkQd0.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx59185-jWKXKqKqkQd0.png"},"description":"1-6. Futari Shitei wa Fela Pure (Two Siblings' Fela Pure)\u003cbr\u003e\n7. Mitari Ryuu Oral Care (Mitarai Style Oral Care)\u003cbr\u003e","endDate":{"day":17,"month":10,"year":2012},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai","Romance"],"id":59185,"idMal":29185,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/59185","startDate":{"day":6,"month":1,"year":2011},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Futari Shitei wa Fela Pure","Two Siblings' Fela Pure","Mitarai Style Oral Care"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"フェラピュア ～御手洗さん家の事情～","romaji":"Fella Pure: Mitarashi-san Chi no Jijou","userPreferred":"Fella Pure: Mitarashi-san Chi no Jijou"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/178692-a76fXro2YTKq.jpg","chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#ae4335","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx178692-FFugfkPnrXAV.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx178692-FFugfkPnrXAV.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx178692-FFugfkPnrXAV.jpg"},"description":"Romance, flowers, and dates-- once upon a time, that was the perfect description of Hae-Su and Min-Cheol. Now, all Hae-Su has is the ashes of their marriage and a mountain of debt. But her world shatters completely when Min-Cheol cheats on her with a young coworker. Hurt and betrayed, Hae-Su finds herself drawn to Tae-Ha, a young man who seems desperate for her affection… and may be hiding more than he shows.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: WEBTOON, edited)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":178692,"idMal":171476,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/178692","startDate":{"day":21,"month":6,"year":2024},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Tears for Withered Flowers","Pleure pour cette fleur","枯萎的花淚","枯れた花に涙を","บุปผารุ่มราคะ"],"title":{"english":"Tears on a Withered Flower","native":"시든 꽃에 눈물을","romaji":"Sideun Kkoche Nunmureul","userPreferred":"Sideun Kkoche Nunmureul"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/164221-dwoTfQp0F9Ab.jpg","chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e40d5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx164221-xxs106Vz80S0.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx164221-xxs106Vz80S0.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx164221-xxs106Vz80S0.jpg"},"description":"In a world where doppelgängers exist and are tasked with killing their human counterparts, a devil named Joon falls prey to distraction and accidentally creates Doh Seong-ah. He’s supposed to be taking the place of Lee Woo-yeol, but instead comes out looking like the male version of Joon’s favorite idol! Undeterred, Seong-ah enters the human realm to start his mission, but Woo-yeol proves to be far more formidable and terrifying than Seong-ah anticipated… Can he succeed in eliminating Woo-yeol? Or will the world be big enough for the two of them after all…?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin US)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":164221,"idMal":185572,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":78,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/164221","startDate":{"day":2,"month":11,"year":2022},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Kill me if you want to live","殺る関係〜僕とヤりたいなら、殺させてください〜","誅殺關係","ภารกิจร้ายกลายเป็นรัก"],"title":{"english":"Kill Me if You Can","native":"죽이는 관계","romaji":"Jugineun Gwangye","userPreferred":"Jugineun Gwangye"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/156220-gA9L2wO4sNKw.jpg","chapters":151,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f18650","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx156220-XIyzoDYiGUGJ.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx156220-XIyzoDYiGUGJ.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx156220-XIyzoDYiGUGJ.jpg"},"description":"Ja-Kang inherited his grandfather's store. In the secret room, there is a secret 'hole'?!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: DAYcomics)","endDate":{"day":24,"month":11,"year":2025},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Hentai","Romance"],"id":156220,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/156220","startDate":{"day":30,"month":10,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Glory Hole Shop","洞洞雜貨店","壁穴開いてます"],"title":{"english":"The Hole is Open","native":"구멍가게, 구멍 열었습니다","romaji":"Gumeonggage, Gumeong Yeoreotseumnida","userPreferred":"Gumeonggage, Gumeong Yeoreotseumnida"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":98,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d78","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx144611-wfw5ON3Q0pN6.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx144611-wfw5ON3Q0pN6.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx144611-wfw5ON3Q0pN6.jpg"},"description":"After years of hardship that culminate in the form of a terminal illness, Rita is determined to do whatever it takes to survive. It might be the wrong thing to steal somebody else’s body, but she doesn’t care about what’s right or wrong anymore. Now, she’s Verta, the affluent and beautiful daughter of Count Alberhart. She’s in the prime position to enjoy a comfortable life…but the people around her seem intent on breaking her. Well, she’s happy to crush whoever gets in her way. It’s time for them to learn how deep her malice goes…\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u2028(Source: Lezhin US)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes eight extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":14,"month":8,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Fantasy","Romance"],"id":144611,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/144611","startDate":{"day":9,"month":11,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["The Intensity of Hate","Au Cœur du Vice","悪意の濃度","惡意的濃度","ปมลึกแรงพยาบาท"],"title":{"english":"Depths of Malice","native":"악의의 농도","romaji":"Aguiui Nongdo","userPreferred":"Aguiui Nongdo"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/143608-qIf7FC9sd4IC.jpg","chapters":93,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e46b5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b143608-OTwHdiZF5HEl.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b143608-OTwHdiZF5HEl.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b143608-OTwHdiZF5HEl.jpg"},"description":"Da-Hyeon and Da-Sol are sisters, and they suddenly look more stunning than I remember. What's going on now?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Toomics, edited)","endDate":{"day":9,"month":3,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Hentai","Romance"],"id":143608,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/143608","startDate":{"day":22,"month":7,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Dorm Room Sisters","พี่สาวครับ...เรามารักกันไหม?"],"title":{"english":"The Late-Bloomers","native":"자취방 누나들","romaji":"Jachwibang Nunadeul","userPreferred":"Jachwibang Nunadeul"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45043","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx133041-HU5SFTENTOAw.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx133041-HU5SFTENTOAw.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx133041-HU5SFTENTOAw.jpg"},"description":"Once upon a time, a man and a woman from two feuding villages fell in love. Forbidden to marry, they committed suicide, pledging to marry in the next life. Various disasters began taking place as a result of their unfortunate fates, and the people in the two villages began offering a man and a woman for holy matrimony to comfort the souls of the sad couple. And, thus, they had continued to avoid calamities for generations...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nMomoki Shirakawa is told about this unbelievable legend and becomes a bride, expected to marry Chikage Kurotaki from the neighboring village. Both young men give in to their family pressure and have no choice but to start living together despite the awkwardness\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nWill they never be a match!? Find out in this yaoi about an odd marriage that's sure to end up in divorce... or will it?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Renta!)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":133041,"idMal":137027,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/133041","startDate":{"day":20,"month":7,"year":2019},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Muri Marriage","Muri Kon"],"title":{"english":"An Impossible Marriage","native":"ムリ婚。","romaji":"Murikon.","userPreferred":"Murikon."},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/123477-61vhdEkwOf4I.jpg","chapters":14,"countryOfOrigin":"TW","coverImage":{"color":"#e43543","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx123477-yBy2Tq6lOUL9.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx123477-yBy2Tq6lOUL9.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx123477-yBy2Tq6lOUL9.jpg"},"description":"Nan-ge is a popular Youtuber about to reach 300,000 subs. But there’s a problem plaguing him... his subscriber count is stalling at 299,000! At his wit’s end, he takes up a friend’s suggestion and tries collaborating with another popular influencer - Prince Mengtai. On-screen, Mengtai's pretty face and cute personality has captured the hearts of young girls everywhere. But in reality, Mengtai's personality is...!?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tong Li, translated)\n\u003cBR\u003e\u003cBR\u003e\n\u003cI\u003eNote: Includes four bonus chapters (two in each volume).\u003c/I\u003e","endDate":{"day":10,"month":2,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":123477,"idMal":154521,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/123477","startDate":{"day":10,"month":2,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["My Influencer Boyfriend"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"我的網紅男友","romaji":"Wo de Wanghong Nanyou","userPreferred":"Wo de Wanghong Nanyou"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":2},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":5,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx117875-2LFLvYVl2urC.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx117875-2LFLvYVl2urC.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx117875-2LFLvYVl2urC.jpg"},"description":"Rui is a rope artist who works in the adult industry. Rui does not have good luck with his friends-with-benefits. Rui is horny. Rui's fantasy is to meet a man who is sexy and just beefy enough with a lonely air behind his downcast eyes. But for him, it was just that: a fantasy. So will he believe his luck when the man of his dreams comes knocking at the door, asking for Rui? And what's more: this hunky, well- built dream man (named Shin Natori) has to stay with Rui for the indefinite future...! Rui can't sleep... But maybe he shouldn't, considering Natori is on the run from a dangerous yakuza boss! What kind of business has Rui been roped into!? \n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Futekiya)","endDate":{"day":25,"month":6,"year":2019},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":117875,"idMal":127653,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/117875","startDate":{"day":25,"month":8,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[" May I Bondage the Yakuza?"],"title":{"english":"May I Tie Up the Yakuza","native":"ヤクザを縛っていいですか？","romaji":"Yakuza wo Shibatte Ii desu ka?","userPreferred":"Yakuza wo Shibatte Ii desu ka?"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/110334-k1iQ1WAHjK0i.jpg","chapters":10,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1bb1a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx110334-4zMSlHBye8yC.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx110334-4zMSlHBye8yC.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx110334-4zMSlHBye8yC.jpg"},"description":"\u003ci\u003eLovely ♡\u003c/i\u003e contains nine stories of busty tsunderes with slender legs and charming personalities. These flirty girls love to play with the guy closest to their heart, but love it even more when they get the tables turned on them, becoming their toy. Collecting ten chapters, \u003ci\u003eLovely ♡\u003c/i\u003e is every bit the title claims to be!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cBR\u003e\n(Source: fakku, edited)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n1. \u003cb\u003eZetchou ♥ Miki-chan\u003c/b\u003e (絶頂♥ミキちゃん, Climax ♥ Miki-chan); Comic Bavel 2018-11\u003cbr\u003e\n2-3. \u003cb\u003eKaede to Suzu\u003c/b\u003e (楓と鈴, Kaede \u0026 Suzu); Comic Bavel 2018-04, 2019-01\u003cbr\u003e\n4. \u003cb\u003eLovely Aina-chan ♥\u003c/b\u003e (らぶりーあいなちゃん♥, Lovely Aina-chan); Comic Bavel 2018-08\u003cbr\u003e\n5. \u003cb\u003eKakurenbo\u003c/b\u003e (かくれんぼ, Hide \u0026 Seek); Comic Bavel 2018-06\u003cbr\u003e\n6. \u003cb\u003eHajimete no XX Date ♡\u003c/b\u003e (初めての××デート♡, Our First XX Date ♡); Comic Bavel 2018-01\u003cbr\u003e\n7. \u003cb\u003eTsundere Kanojo o Shibatte Mita!\u003c/b\u003e (ツンデレ彼女を縛ってみた！, I Tied Up My Tsundere Girlfriend! ); Comic Bavel 2017-10\u003cbr\u003e\n8. \u003cb\u003eMukuchi na Kanojo\u003c/b\u003e (無口な彼女, Silent Girlfriend); Comic Bavel 2017-08\u003cbr\u003e\n9. \u003cb\u003eNise Bitch no Watashi ga Chouhatsu Shite Mita\u003c/b\u003e (偽ビッチの私が挑発してみた, I'm a Fake Slut Who Tried to be a Cocktease); Comic Bavel 2017-05\u003cbr\u003e\n10. \u003cb\u003eMaiden Breed\u003c/b\u003e (Maiden Breed, メイデンブリード); Comic Bavel 2016-10\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Chapter 10 is exclusively from the electronic version of Bavel Comics \"Lovely ♡\" that was released on December 21st, 2018.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":29,"month":11,"year":2018},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":110334,"idMal":136462,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":79,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/110334","startDate":{"day":29,"month":11,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Zetchou ♥ Miki-chan","Kaede to Suzu","Lovely Aina-chan ♥","Kakurenbo","Hajimete no XX Date ♡","Tsundere Kanojo o Shibatte Mita!","Mukuchi na Kanojo","Nise Bitch no Watashi ga Chouhatsu Shite Mita","Maiden Breed","Climax ♥ Miki-chan","Kaede \u0026 Suzu","Lovely Aina-chan","Hide \u0026 Seek","Our First XX Date ♡","Silent Girlfriend","Lovely Heart","I'm a Fake Slut Who Tried to be a Cocktease","I Tied Up My Tsundere Girlfriend!"],"title":{"english":"Lovely","native":"らぶりー♡","romaji":"Lovely ♡","userPreferred":"Lovely ♡"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/n107487-PdgH0F3vkrfH.jpg","chapters":71,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e42828","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx107487-FZZz5cTLUn4G.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx107487-FZZz5cTLUn4G.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx107487-FZZz5cTLUn4G.jpg"},"description":"A certain summer day, as the cicadas sing loudly. A man with no money and no place to belong tries to end his life, however is unable to take the last step. While wavering between life and death, he sees a gourmet food program on television, and realizing he's never once eaten crab in his life decides that \"For my last day on this Earth, I'll eat crab\". Settings his sights on the wife who lives in a high-class neighborhood that he happened across in a library, he forces his way into her home.\nAnd thus, he demands money from her, however... things go in an unexpected direction...","endDate":{"day":26,"month":12,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":107487,"idMal":117964,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/107487","startDate":{"day":28,"month":1,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Eating Crab with a Yukionna","설녀와 게를 먹다"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"雪女と蟹を食う","romaji":"Yuki Onna to Kani wo Kuu","userPreferred":"Yuki Onna to Kani wo Kuu"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":8},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":8,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4d650","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx103879-rfSbzpc3q4FB.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx103879-rfSbzpc3q4FB.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx103879-rfSbzpc3q4FB.jpg"},"description":"After a very rocky start, Asaichi and Yoru begin their passion-filled dating life! Although the band's popularity has remained steady, Asaichi was no longer content with being a small-time band. He wants fame! He wants success! And so, he begins to dream of the band's future. Trouble arises when Yoru reveals that he has some fans stalking him. Asaichi offers Yoru a spare key to his place and they begin officially living together.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nHow will their relationship fare? Where will their band go? As they worry, struggle and fall in love, what does the future hold as their group's plans begin to grow?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Kuma)","endDate":{"day":16,"month":11,"year":2018},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Music","Romance"],"id":103879,"idMal":121045,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/103879","startDate":{"day":31,"month":7,"year":2017},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Yoru to Asa no Uta Encore","The Song of Yoru \u0026 Asa Ec","W rytmie wieczoru i poranka: Bis!","La canción de Yoru y Asa Bis","The Song of Night and Day - La Canzone di Yoru e Asa"],"title":{"english":"The Song of Yoru \u0026 Asa Encore","native":"よるとあさの歌 Ec","romaji":"Yoru to Asa no Uta EC","userPreferred":"Yoru to Asa no Uta EC"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/187324-bECRl24QobZ9.jpg","chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e45dbb","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx187324-QZZV0vLVo6Jv.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx187324-QZZV0vLVo6Jv.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx187324-QZZV0vLVo6Jv.jpg"},"description":"I-Yeon wanted a quiet life as an arborist—but hidden upstairs is a comatose killer who once tried to murder her. When he wakes with no memory, she panics… and lies: \"I'm your wife.\" \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eCan she survive the man who doesn’t remember her—or what he did?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Manta)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Mystery","Romance"],"id":187324,"idMal":184977,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/187324","startDate":{"day":2,"month":2,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Flowers are Bait","花は甘い","花即誘餌"],"title":{"english":"Flower of Allure","native":"꽃은 미끼야","romaji":"Kkocheun Mikkiya","userPreferred":"Kkocheun Mikkiya"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null}],"pageInfo":{"currentPage":6,"hasNextPage":true,"lastPage":104,"perPage":48,"total":5000}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-15T06:40:46.569058+03:00"},"{\"query\":\"query ListManga ($page: Int, $search: String, $perPage: Int, $sort: [MediaSort], $status: [MediaStatus], $genres: [String], $averageScore_greater: Int, $startDate_greater: FuzzyDateInt, $startDate_lesser: FuzzyDateInt, $format: MediaFormat, $countryOfOrigin: CountryCode, $isAdult: Boolean) {\\n\\tPage(page: $page, perPage: $perPage) {\\n\\t\\tpageInfo {\\n\\t\\t\\thasNextPage\\n\\t\\t\\ttotal\\n\\t\\t\\tperPage\\n\\t\\t\\tcurrentPage\\n\\t\\t\\tlastPage\\n\\t\\t}\\n\\t\\tmedia(type: MANGA, isAdult: $isAdult, countryOfOrigin: $countryOfOrigin, search: $search, sort: $sort, status_in: $status, format: $format, genre_in: $genres, averageScore_greater: $averageScore_greater, startDate_greater: $startDate_greater, startDate_lesser: $startDate_lesser, format_not: NOVEL) {\\n\\t\\t\\t... baseManga\\n\\t\\t}\\n\\t}\\n}\\nfragment baseManga on Media {\\n\\tid\\n\\tidMal\\n\\tsiteUrl\\n\\tstatus(version: 2)\\n\\tseason\\n\\ttype\\n\\tformat\\n\\tbannerImage\\n\\tchapters\\n\\tvolumes\\n\\tsynonyms\\n\\tisAdult\\n\\tcountryOfOrigin\\n\\tmeanScore\\n\\tdescription\\n\\tgenres\\n\\ttitle {\\n\\t\\tuserPreferred\\n\\t\\tromaji\\n\\t\\tenglish\\n\\t\\tnative\\n\\t}\\n\\tcoverImage {\\n\\t\\textraLarge\\n\\t\\tlarge\\n\\t\\tmedium\\n\\t\\tcolor\\n\\t}\\n\\tstartDate {\\n\\t\\tyear\\n\\t\\tmonth\\n\\t\\tday\\n\\t}\\n\\tendDate {\\n\\t\\tyear\\n\\t\\tmonth\\n\\t\\tday\\n\\t}\\n}\\n\",\"variables\":{\"isAdult\":true,\"page\":7,\"perPage\":48,\"sort\":[\"SCORE_DESC\"]}}":{"value":{"Page":{"media":[{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/148117-SU7dXdhl0Lbp.jpg","chapters":97,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1c9ae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx148117-ovY5QW9uaeZc.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx148117-ovY5QW9uaeZc.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx148117-ovY5QW9uaeZc.jpg"},"description":"Hi, I'm Gyeon-U, a freshman in college. I have no friends, so I joined a club with three other girls. I wonder how my life'll be now...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Toomics, edited)","endDate":{"day":23,"month":10,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Hentai","Romance"],"id":148117,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/148117","startDate":{"day":7,"month":2,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["College Life Starts With Clubs","La Universidad empieza con los Clubes","No seré un marginado","Plötzlich Insider","Le Comité Étudiant","大学生活はサークルから","大学生活就从社团开始","大學生活就從社團開始","ชมรมเปลี่ยนชีวิต"],"title":{"english":"An Outsider’s Way In","native":"대학생활은 동아리부터","romaji":"Daehaksaenghwareun Dongaributeo","userPreferred":"Daehaksaenghwareun Dongaributeo"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f14393","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx133268-mLjwrclrfib4.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx133268-mLjwrclrfib4.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx133268-mLjwrclrfib4.jpg"},"description":"Sachio Kurumizawa is an omega mouse manga artist, and Ukano, the alpha fox, is his editor... but Sachio can't help but feel uncomfortable around Ukano. He always seems to look at Sachio with predatory eyes. One night, Sachio goes into heat at an omega-only bar, and Ukano saves him. Unfortunately, Sachio has no idea how long he'll stay in heat... and then, Ukano offers to help him stop it. Will Sachio say yes to getting between the sheets with Ukano despite his terror of being devoured...!?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Renta!)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Fantasy","Romance"],"id":133268,"idMal":141473,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/133268","startDate":{"day":31,"month":10,"year":2020},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Gochisou Omega wa Chuu to Naku","맛있는 오메가는 찍하고 운다","To Make A Delicious Omega Squeak"],"title":{"english":"The Foxy Mouse's Romance","native":"ごちそうΩはチュウと鳴く","romaji":"Gochisou Ω wa Chuu to Naku","userPreferred":"Gochisou Ω wa Chuu to Naku"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb86","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/nx101463-NYotUjtPJ96w.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/nx101463-NYotUjtPJ96w.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/nx101463-NYotUjtPJ96w.jpg"},"description":"Akihisa Hase was bullied for being an otaku, but the chance to change his appearance and start anew in a different school appeared when his father had to transfer. Going around the school, he found a volume of his favorite manga and got so entranced he didn't notice the owner of the manga, Yuu Onozuka, was right there and saw him on full otaku mode. Akihisa thought he had blown his cover, but Yuu was unexpectedly nice to him and they soon became friends. All was well until Akihisa became puzzled by the fact Yuu would randomly kiss him without saying anything.\n","endDate":{"day":22,"month":6,"year":2017},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":101463,"idMal":113594,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/101463","startDate":{"day":22,"month":10,"year":2016},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"あさってにキス","romaji":"Asatte ni Kiss","userPreferred":"Asatte ni Kiss"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/176815-xBaxySWBeib6.jpg","chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e43528","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx176815-2kZbSKY4qN7l.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx176815-2kZbSKY4qN7l.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx176815-2kZbSKY4qN7l.jpg"},"description":"Ju Min-Chan had always suffered from frequent fevers as a kid because of some unfortunate curse. Now as a young adult, his condition has worsened into seizures which he can only keep at bay by hunting spirits. As if things couldn’t get any worse, the effectiveness of this method starts diminishing as his seizures become more recurrent. Then, he learns about a powerful being who could lift his curse. Despite the risk that comes with hunting down this being, Min-Chan readily jumps at this chance to finally escape his harsh fate only to find out that he was never destined to live a normal life…\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tappytoon)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":176815,"idMal":187330,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":78,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/176815","startDate":{"day":8,"month":12,"year":2023},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["算魎夢"],"title":{"english":"Dreaming of the Dokkaebi","native":"산가지는 도깨비의 꿈을 꾼다","romaji":"Sangajineun Dokkaebiui Kkumeul Kkunda","userPreferred":"Sangajineun Dokkaebiui Kkumeul Kkunda"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":52,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#783528","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx132745-hNndsdcZw77N.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx132745-hNndsdcZw77N.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx132745-hNndsdcZw77N.jpg"},"description":"On the opening day of veterinarian Choi Jung’s new animal hospital, everything goes wrong when he discovers a pesky little lizard out front. But this creature insists he is the son of the Dragon King of the East Sea. This being is not only a dragon, but in his human form, insists on sharing, ahem, “life essence” with the human. And in his pursuit of becoming a proper adult dragon, will Woonwoo the dragon prince succeed in finding the inverted scales he so desperately seeks?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin US)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes 10 extra chapters.\u003ci\u003e","endDate":{"day":1,"month":4,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Fantasy","Romance"],"id":132745,"idMal":185060,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/132745","startDate":{"day":9,"month":9,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Eunwoo's Designation","Making Love","L’amour entre les nuages et la pluie","ลิขิตรักเทพมังกร","雲雨之情"],"title":{"english":"Love of Cloud and Rain","native":"운우지정","romaji":"Unujijeong","userPreferred":"Unujijeong"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":13,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx128200-tZiGp03KQLSp.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx128200-tZiGp03KQLSp.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx128200-tZiGp03KQLSp.jpg"},"description":"The very popular omega model, Masatsugu Otonashi, hates alphas on a totally different level. However, one day, Otonashi is assigned an assistant, Mei Todoroki, an alpha who ends up being at the mercy of his unreasonable demands. Despite the hardships of being Otonashi's assistant, Todoroki flawlessly does his job and eventually gains Otonashi's trust...and Todoroki soon becomes drawn to Otonashi's vulnerability and kindness...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003ci\u003eNote: Chapter count includes one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":8,"month":4,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":128200,"idMal":132497,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":78,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/128200","startDate":{"day":8,"month":11,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"俺だけの専属アルファ","romaji":"Ore dake no Senzoku Alpha","userPreferred":"Ore dake no Senzoku Alpha"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":2},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":5,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4935d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx123368-s4gdTELQUBAV.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx123368-s4gdTELQUBAV.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx123368-s4gdTELQUBAV.jpg"},"description":"In this world, there are humans without beast ears and humans with beast ears, called Bestia. Dr. Akira Miyaji specializes in treating Bestian patients at the general hospital and is a Bestia himself. At first, he despises the hospital's hottie manager--ahem, I mean... haughty manager, Sougo Kijima, for being the embodiment of the very Bestia instincts that Akira tries to suppress. But when The Doctor realizes that both he and Sougo may be victims of similar circumstances, his impressions shift. Now, they are living their happily-ever-after welcoming a baby into their new life together. But with both parents of a toddler working in the highly demanding medical field, they must figure something out if they want to make it out in one piece! And to top it all off, Sougo and Akira will have to face their biggest hurdle yet: Sougo's Bestia father.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Futekiya)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":10,"month":4,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Fantasy","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":123368,"idMal":140908,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/123368","startDate":{"day":7,"month":8,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Beast's Storm: Hug Me Baby!","native":"ケダモノアラシ－Hug me baby!－","romaji":"Kedamono Arashi: Hug me baby!","userPreferred":"Kedamono Arashi: Hug me baby!"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/109549-1bezhx7fTioD.jpg","chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4e45d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx109549-qw56DtOZ3XOk.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx109549-qw56DtOZ3XOk.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx109549-qw56DtOZ3XOk.jpg"},"description":"After getting caught late at night doing some really kinky things in the office by his own boss, Kasuya gets demoted from his highly placed position and is transferred to the middle of the countryside. He's determined to quickly prove himself and get good results so he can get back to Tokyo. However, his neighbor Kuzuya – who also happen to love anal play – reveals the reason why he got demoted and transferred, right in the middle of the bar where the villagers gather! Even if he lost all his dignity as a human being, Kasuya still smiles and says this one thing to Kuzuya, \"Anal sex is the best!!\" To be fucked or getting fucked... Partners in crime, fuck buddies, or anal buddies... Here's the shitty erotic comedy of Kuzu and Kasu, two good-for-nothings navigating their sexuality.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Takeshobo)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":109549,"idMal":119916,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/109549","startDate":{"day":29,"month":9,"year":2018},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Happy Shitty Life"],"title":{"english":"Happy Crappy Life","native":"ハッピークソライフ","romaji":"Happy Kuso Life","userPreferred":"Happy Kuso Life"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":11,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1a16b","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx90314-RXWzyfIXY42z.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx90314-RXWzyfIXY42z.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx90314-RXWzyfIXY42z.jpg"},"description":"\u003ci\u003ePart 3 of the Kuroneko Kareshi series.\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nShingo and Kakami have finally understood their feelings and continued with their relationship, and for some reason, Kakami wants to take it to the next level by living together?\n","endDate":{"day":14,"month":7,"year":2014},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance","Supernatural"],"id":90314,"idMal":66001,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/90314","startDate":{"day":14,"month":9,"year":2013},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Kuroneko Kareshi no Itoshikata","Kuroneko Kareshi no Nakasekata"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"クロネコ彼氏の愛し方","romaji":"Kuroneko Kareshi no Aishikata","userPreferred":"Kuroneko Kareshi no Aishikata"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":2},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d93","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx185053-84w447NzSY9z.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx185053-84w447NzSY9z.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx185053-84w447NzSY9z.png"},"description":"Woo-Yeon never liked Alphas, not before, and definitely not after he manifested as an Omega. The only person who ever made him feel seen was his tutor, Do-Hyun. Years later, Woo-Yeon follows him to university, hoping for a fresh start. But when they meet again, Do-Hyun doesn't recognize him. Woo-Yeon, however, never forgot—not his voice, his kindness, or the way Do-Hyun still makes his heart flutter. Then he learns the truth. Do-Hyun is an Alpha...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":185053,"idMal":184997,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":78,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/185053","startDate":{"day":17,"month":10,"year":2024},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Alpha Trauma","native":"알파 트라우마","romaji":"Alpha Trauma","userPreferred":"Alpha Trauma"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":7,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#1a286b","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx157070-0Cr9lhhRjvKA.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx157070-0Cr9lhhRjvKA.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx157070-0Cr9lhhRjvKA.jpg"},"description":"\u003cb\u003eJapan, 1950s. Seishiro is unable to sleep alone at night due to the trauma of the war, and lives a dull life.\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nOne day, he meets Jim, a kind American soldier stationed in Japan. Jim falls in love with Seishiro at first sight. This could be the perfect chance to change his life... Their relationship started out of calculation, but as they sleep in each other's sweet embrace, Seishiro's heart gradually melts. However, he cannot imagine a future where they live together... \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Tokyopop)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":21,"month":10,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":157070,"idMal":151587,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/157070","startDate":{"day":15,"month":10,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Can't Stay A Night Alone.","O Fim das Minhas Noites de Solidão","Le soldat qui m'a rendu mes nuits","I Can't Stand Another Night Alone"],"title":{"english":"I Can't Get Through the Night Alone","native":"ひとりで夜は越えられない","romaji":"Hitori de Yoru wa Koerarenai","userPreferred":"Hitori de Yoru wa Koerarenai"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#ff78ae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx145695-baXPBdq8vMRr.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx145695-baXPBdq8vMRr.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx145695-baXPBdq8vMRr.jpg"},"description":"Recent graduate Jin has been assigned to help out his upperclassman Seto, a highly competent but somewhat standoffish systems engineer. Though Jin is good at his job, he does seem to have his head in the clouds more often than not... and Seto's eyes always seem to linger on him more than they should!\n\u003cBR\u003e\u003cBR\u003e\nA fresh new boys' love office romance in which opposites attract! \n\u003cBR\u003e\u003cBR\u003e\n(Source: TOKYOPOP)\n\u003cBR