Change\u003c/b\u003e (恥じらいChange, Bashful Change); \u003ci\u003eComic Anthurium 2020-08\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n8. \u003cb\u003eChikakute Tooi Anata\u003c/b\u003e (近くて遠いあなた, The You Who's Near and Yet So Far); \u003ci\u003eComic Anthurium 2020-06\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n9. \u003cb\u003eMachikirenai Kouhai Kanojo Tsujinaka-chan\u003c/b\u003e (待ちきれない後輩彼女辻中ちゃん, Junior Girlfriend Miss Tsujinaka Can't Wait); kakioroshi (Digital version exclusive)","endDate":{"day":25,"month":1,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai","Romance"],"id":144524,"idMal":143666,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":78,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/144524","startDate":{"day":25,"month":1,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Kono Koi ni Kiduite","この恋に気づいて","Notice This Love","Kouhai Kanojo Tsujinaka-chan no Oshioki","後輩彼女辻中ちゃんのおしおき","Junior Girlfriend Miss Tsujinaka's Punishment","Boku wa Umeda-san ni Sakaraenai","僕は梅田さんに逆らえない","I Can't Go Against Miss Umeda","Futagomori","ふたご盛り","Twins in Heat","Suteneko Kanojo","捨て猫彼女","Abandoned Cat Girlfriend","Wanko na Kanojo","わんこな彼女","Puppy-like Girlfriend","Hajirai Change","恥じらいChange","Bashful Change","Chikakute Tooi Anata","近くて遠いあなた","The You Who's Near and Yet So Far","Machikirenai Kouhai Kanojo Tsujinaka-chan","待ちきれない後輩彼女辻中ちゃん","Junior Girlfriend Miss Tsujinaka Can't Wait"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"この恋に気づいて","romaji":"Kono Koi ni Kizuite","userPreferred":"Kono Koi ni Kizuite"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/134470-TkEMTokri9DN.jpg","chapters":8,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d61a43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx134470-GmnjijUU0i3L.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx134470-GmnjijUU0i3L.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx134470-GmnjijUU0i3L.jpg"},"description":"Once a child prodigy pianist, Shion Kirino is now a burnt-out, bitter shell of himself, lost in grief over his mother's passing and his own dying passion toward the musical career that had defined his connection to her. When he's approached by Kei Takase—a talented younger colleague who professes his admiration for Kirino—he ends up inviting him home for sex, intending on toying with his feelings.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nWhen Takase isn't deterred by Kirino's abrasive exterior, Kirino finds that he cannot deny Takase's unwavering devotion... But practicing piano together and celebrating Takase's successes also stirs up Kirino's own insecurities and distorted sense of jealousy. After a lifetime of loneliness, can he find salvation in Takase without dragging him down?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: TOKYOPOP)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes one extra chapter.\u003ci\u003e","endDate":{"day":20,"month":8,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Music","Romance"],"id":134470,"idMal":140241,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/134470","startDate":{"day":17,"month":7,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["嫉妒使愛面露愁容","질투는 사랑을 흐리게 한다","ความริษยาทําให้คนตาบอด","O Ciúme cega o Amor"],"title":{"english":"Jealousy Blinds Love","native":"嫉妬は愛を曇らせる","romaji":"Shitto wa Ai wo Kumoraseru","userPreferred":"Shitto wa Ai wo Kumoraseru"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1c9ae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx134233-xFdJUvexOMcS.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx134233-xFdJUvexOMcS.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx134233-xFdJUvexOMcS.jpg"},"description":"Leo Asaka, an alpha male and a second-generation actor, hates it when people say he's just like his actor father. Leo is working hard to make it big on his own when he receives an offer to star in a film to be shot by a world-famous director. He then learns who his co-star is: Eito Yanagi, another alpha male and a second-generation actor who's known for living a scandalous life. The two of them get locked in a hotel room so they can get to know each other, where Leo glimpses a secret about Eito that may change the course of their destiny.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\n(Source: Renta!)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Contains an extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":25,"month":12,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":134233,"idMal":138887,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/134233","startDate":{"day":28,"month":2,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["My Partner is the Thoroughbred Omega","Ore no Tsugai ha Thoroughbread Omega","Mein Partner ist ein Vollblut-Omega"],"title":{"english":"His Partner, the Thoroughbred Omega","native":"僕の番はサラブレットΩ","romaji":"Boku no Tsugai wa Thoroughbred Ω","userPreferred":"Boku no Tsugai wa Thoroughbred Ω"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bba1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx82047-VqpU7aHv8j1M.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx82047-VqpU7aHv8j1M.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx82047-VqpU7aHv8j1M.jpg"},"description":"\u003ci\u003ePart 2 of the Kuroneko Kareshi series.\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nKagami and Shingo are a passionate couple. Is their mutual attraction strong enough to survive some misunderstandings? Will the bond between them grow stronger or will the relationship break apart? Continues the story of Shingo and Kagami.\n","endDate":{"day":15,"month":7,"year":2013},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":82047,"idMal":52047,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/82047","startDate":{"day":14,"month":3,"year":2013},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Kuroneko Kareshi no Amae Kata"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"クロネコ彼氏の甘え方","romaji":"Kuroneko Kareshi no Amaekata","userPreferred":"Kuroneko Kareshi no Amaekata"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":95,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b166769-hB5fDtipFUrf.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b166769-hB5fDtipFUrf.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b166769-hB5fDtipFUrf.png"},"description":"Do-Hyun Nam, a college student, gets put in a snowy white space with a stranger. Then a beautiful goddess appears with a mirror filled with screaming people. Still confused, the two hear shocking words from the goddess.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003e\"Only you can save these people. Please have sex now!\"\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: DAYcomics)","endDate":{"day":12,"month":5,"year":2025},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Hentai","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":166769,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/166769","startDate":{"day":3,"month":7,"year":2023},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["初次深交，請多指教","いきなり知らない人とシろって!?"],"title":{"english":"I Have to Sleep with a Stranger?","native":"모르는 여자랑 하라고요?","romaji":"Moreuneun Yeojarang Haragoyo?","userPreferred":"Moreuneun Yeojarang Haragoyo?"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1c9ae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx137618-yvMnPtXg38xj.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx137618-yvMnPtXg38xj.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx137618-yvMnPtXg38xj.jpg"},"description":"A 50s x 60s BL. We met when we were 18 and 28, from that time... until now, I've always loved you.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\"I'll wait no matter how long, even 10 years or 20 years. Even when we've become old men.\"\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nFollowing the life path of two people from different generations—this is a tender life story. Akihiko, an employee in his 50s and Makoto, who's 10 years older than him, are lovers, sons and family. From when we meet as tutor and pupil, things that have changed, and things that are unchanged...","endDate":{"day":8,"month":6,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":137618,"idMal":138950,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":80,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/137618","startDate":{"day":25,"month":6,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Our Lovely Days"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"いとおしき日々","romaji":"Itooshiki Hibi","userPreferred":"Itooshiki Hibi"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":9,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4505d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx132049-tyDB8b1nZUqG.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx132049-tyDB8b1nZUqG.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx132049-tyDB8b1nZUqG.jpg"},"description":"Miki Kuroda, a college student, was forced to wear a collar in the past and has come to reject Doms due to his trauma. However, his body continues to seek for more, and he deals with the overflowing heat by reading erotic novels.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nOne day, when working as a babysitter, Miki meets Moriya, a Dom. Despite being confused, he manages to finish his work, but happens to go into heat. Moreover, when he finds an erotic novel, Moriya notices his lower half-!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Kasakura Press, translated)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes an extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":1,"month":9,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":132049,"idMal":141659,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/132049","startDate":{"day":7,"month":10,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Collar Kiss","Kiss the Collar"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"カラーにくちづけ","romaji":"Collar ni Kuchizuke","userPreferred":"Collar ni Kuchizuke"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/127154-zkPRsRRwuPki.jpg","chapters":96,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#78bbd6","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx127154-3fZ0xOyWr22K.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx127154-3fZ0xOyWr22K.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx127154-3fZ0xOyWr22K.png"},"description":"The friendzone. A dangerous place for any man. A soul-sucking abyss that takes away all your happiness, drive, and future. But if your childhood friend comes to live with you? Well maybe it's time start exploring. Hey, maybe she'll say yes this time?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: TOPTOON+)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes six extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":29,"month":6,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Hentai","Romance"],"id":127154,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/127154","startDate":{"day":15,"month":8,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["どちらか選べと言われたら"],"title":{"english":"Between Us","native":"우리 사이","romaji":"Uri Sai","userPreferred":"Uri Sai"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":7,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1d6c9","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx125746-tB0C370RXgnT.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx125746-tB0C370RXgnT.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx125746-tB0C370RXgnT.png"},"description":"The thoroughbred, Shiba Toshimasa, and the lion, Shishidou Ouga, are childhood friends and now lovers. But, as the son of a good family, Shiba faces the talk about an engagement to his thoroughbred friend, Touma Rei. Although he asked Touma to reject the engagement, Shishidou finds out about it...?!","endDate":{"day":30,"month":12,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Fantasy","Romance"],"id":125746,"idMal":130921,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/125746","startDate":{"day":30,"month":8,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Thoroughbred Doesn't Shake","Thoroughbred Doesn't Waver"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"サラブレッドはゆるがない","romaji":"Thoroughbred wa Yuruganai  ","userPreferred":"Thoroughbred wa Yuruganai  "},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":1,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bba1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx114539-eIRALACJtoJi.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx114539-eIRALACJtoJi.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx114539-eIRALACJtoJi.jpg"},"description":"Otomo Hisashi tries to seduce Mao after reading some BL stories brought to the drama club by Ichikawa.","endDate":{"day":10,"month":8,"year":2019},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":114539,"idMal":124402,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/114539","startDate":{"day":10,"month":8,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"soft focus en rose","native":"恋色ソフトフォーカス","romaji":"Koiiro Soft Focus","userPreferred":"Koiiro Soft Focus"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1c9bb","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/57095-PDsq8omosCY0.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/57095-PDsq8omosCY0.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/57095-PDsq8omosCY0.jpg"},"description":"1-2) Renai-rubi no Tadashii Furikata (The Proper Way to Write Love)\u003cbr\u003e\n\"I wanted to see him make this kind of face.\" I was a gloomy nerd in high school, and at that time I was entwined with Washizawa Natsuo – my dark past. Now, a few years later, we have reunited and Natsuo asked me out. This is my chance. We’ll go out, then I’ll break up with him, leaving him in tatters! \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n3) Renai-Rubi no Yarashii Furikata (The Sexy Way to Write Love)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n4-5) Hodokeru Kaibutsu (A monster falls apart)\u003cbr\u003e\n\"At best, you get hurt and it’s over.\" One of Natsuo’s friends from high school, Hayashida Kan, had a drunk encounter with flashy subordinate Shuuna, and they became fuck buddies. Long before, Hayashida hit his lover. Hayashida, with as many regrets as he has piercings, wonders if Shuuna will hold him forever? (Hayashida Kan also appears in Sabita Yoru Demo Koi wa Sasayaku)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n6) Extra Monster Sugar\u003cbr\u003e\nHayashida and Shuuna are buying new camera.\n","endDate":{"day":30,"month":1,"year":2015},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":87095,"idMal":81189,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/87095","startDate":{"day":14,"month":3,"year":2014},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Renai Ruby no Tadashii Furikata","Renai Ruby no Yarashii Furikata","Renai-rubi no Tadashii Furikata","The Proper Way to Write Love","Jak odczytać miłość?"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"恋愛ルビの正しいふりかた","romaji":"Renai Rubi no Tadashii Furikata","userPreferred":"Renai Rubi no Tadashii Furikata"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1e435","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx143114-FqO5RXZLGPT0.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx143114-FqO5RXZLGPT0.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx143114-FqO5RXZLGPT0.jpg"},"description":"When daydreaming part-timer Chihiro gets forced to order from a random maid cafe for a punishment game, he's expecting sweet, delicate maids to cater to his every whim... so why is this tall, buff dude wearing a frilly maid outfit and calling him \"Master\"? Mako may not look like the ideal pretty maid, but Chihiro's about to find out what happens when you judge a maid by their muscles!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Futekiya)","endDate":{"day":25,"month":2,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Ecchi","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":143114,"idMal":142782,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/143114","startDate":{"day":25,"month":6,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"I'll Make You My Number One Idol!","native":"俺の最推しをキミに捧ぐ！","romaji":"Ore no Saioshi wo Kimi ni Sasagu!  ","userPreferred":"Ore no Saioshi wo Kimi ni Sasagu!  "},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/139463-ES7QSEM4Du9S.jpg","chapters":90,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#a10000","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx139463-hpa1j3JFYrla.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx139463-hpa1j3JFYrla.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx139463-hpa1j3JFYrla.jpg"},"description":"Lee-Won, who works as a poor lawyer in Russia, visits City Councilor Zdanov, who is in conflict over Nikolai's commission, and there he meets the mafia boss, Caesar. Behind City Councilor Zdanov, there was a mafia involved. The meeting between the two is extraordinary.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Lezhin, edited)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Chapter count includes 37 side story chapters and 1 special.\u003ci\u003e","endDate":{"day":7,"month":5,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Drama","Fantasy","Romance"],"id":139463,"idMal":172664,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":72,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/139463","startDate":{"day":28,"month":7,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["薔薇與香檳","Rosen \u0026 Champagner","Die Rose und der Champagner","Rosas y Champán","Roses et Champagne"],"title":{"english":"Roses and Champagne","native":"장미와 샴페인","romaji":"Jangmiwa Champagne","userPreferred":"Jangmiwa Champagne"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/123104-pQ57TDrSkHip.jpg","chapters":63,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#d6a178","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx123104-GONMh29vDaTI.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx123104-GONMh29vDaTI.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx123104-GONMh29vDaTI.jpg"},"description":"Former thug Choi Mun-hyeok will do anything to protect his younger siblings. When he’s defeated in an underground fight club and sold in an auction to Seo Yeonjin, he reluctantly allows himself to be put on a leash for his family’s sake. Yeon-jin, on the other hand, doesn’t care much for family. In fact, he intends to cause a scandal that will outrage his billionaire father by embarking on a twisted, carnal affair with Mun-hyeok. All Mun-hyeok needs to do is serve Yeonjin well, in work and in bed. However, their passionate encounters might turn into something greater than they bargained for. After all, the line between passion and madness is a thin one….\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin US)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes three extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":16,"month":9,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Hentai","Psychological","Thriller"],"id":123104,"idMal":189144,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/123104","startDate":{"day":25,"month":6,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["열광","Enthusiasm","Fièvre","Con locura","Leidenschaft"],"title":{"english":"Mania","native":"열광","romaji":"Yeolgwang","userPreferred":"Yeolgwang"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae93","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx115965-LAIJPQIYPTow.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx115965-LAIJPQIYPTow.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx115965-LAIJPQIYPTow.jpg"},"description":"Maki confessed to his best friend Katsumi, but was told he was “disgusting”. They are coincidentally reunited after 10 years apart. Although their reunion should be a joyous one, Maki discovered that the once straight man is now sleeping with men who have dangerous reputations. Little did he know, after once being assaulted, Katsumi began to have violent sex to punishing himself for hurting Maki in his terrible self-protection. In response to those feelings, Maki says, \u003ci\u003e“Katsumi-kun, I will punish you.”\u003c/i\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Takeshobo, translated)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes the one-shot “Mijuku na Bokura wa Natsu ni Naru (未熟な僕らは夏に為る)” and one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e\n","endDate":{"day":7,"month":2,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":115965,"idMal":124888,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/115965","startDate":{"day":1,"month":7,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["未熟な僕らは夏に為る","Mijuku na Bokura wa Natsu ni Naru"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"1人と一人の3650日","romaji":"Hitori to Hitori no 3650-nichi","userPreferred":"Hitori to Hitori no 3650-nichi"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":11,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1505d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx101051-AYA7HiDTosPP.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx101051-AYA7HiDTosPP.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx101051-AYA7HiDTosPP.jpg"},"description":"Thirty-two year old Suwa Misumi is a Master of Sake and has just recently been fired from his job due to causing trouble from being \"too friendly\" since he doesn't like to refuse requests. At the lowest point in his life, he now finds a restaurant he desperately wants to work at. Only problem is that his latest drunken one night stand is the owner!!\n","endDate":{"day":29,"month":9,"year":2018},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":101051,"idMal":109897,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/101051","startDate":{"day":30,"month":7,"year":2016},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Yoidore Koi o Sezu","Zbyt pijany na miłość"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"酔いどれ恋をせず","romaji":"Yoidore Koi wo Sezu","userPreferred":"Yoidore Koi wo Sezu"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":2},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":7,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1a128","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx98020-on3NSDgFkZ70.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx98020-on3NSDgFkZ70.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx98020-on3NSDgFkZ70.jpg"},"description":"Closet idol fan, Mikado, hates his superior, Anezaki. Anezaki is very capable in his work, but he hands all the grunt work to Mikado. One day, Mikado is charged with sending a drunk Anezaki home after a company drinking party. But they missed the last train and end up spending the night at a love hotel. There, Anezaki suddenly mounts Mikado and continues to do the dirtiest things.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes 2 extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":7,"month":7,"year":2016},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":98020,"idMal":102178,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/98020","startDate":{"day":7,"month":3,"year":2016},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["The Secret of Me and My Boss","나와 상사의 비밀"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"俺と上司のかくしごと","romaji":"Ore to Joushi no Kakushigoto","userPreferred":"Ore to Joushi no Kakushigoto"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#d69378","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx166296-bF9a7SwTjfGx.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx166296-bF9a7SwTjfGx.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx166296-bF9a7SwTjfGx.jpg"},"description":"Mun Geon-U’s first love comes crashing into him smelling like the sweetest cookie around! After learning he’s a new bakery owner in town named Yu Ha-Jin, Geon-U asks him for a part-time job in the hopes of winning over his heart. Unfortunately, his plan is doomed from the start as Ha-Jin is completely done with relationships now. But a little pushback is hardly an issue for the ace judo athlete Geon-U. He’s prepared to do anything to make Ha-Jin fall for him, even if that means letting the baker squeeze his hot buns...!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tappytoon, edited)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":166296,"idMal":184959,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/166296","startDate":{"day":6,"month":4,"year":2023},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Honey Bear","native":"허니베어","romaji":"Honey Bear","userPreferred":"Honey Bear"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":12,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#ae6b1a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx108975-uC9B4x8NFiiV.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx108975-uC9B4x8NFiiV.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx108975-uC9B4x8NFiiV.png"},"description":"High school teacher, Aoki is reluctant to go to the infirmary. Because he does not like the doctor there, Mr. Tengoku for no reason. But one day, he is forced to pay a visit to talk about a student who often skips class there. At the first contact, Tengoku easily sees through Aoki's nature of disguising an exemplary teacher, and smiles mysteriously. Tengoku tells him that he has been watching Aoki ever since he is assigned to this school. While discussing about the student, Tengoku points out the naivety of Aoki, and then gives him a kiss all of sudden. In his embarrassment, Aoki is unable to refuse at that moment. Later on, he remembers his childhood memories and starts to see his true self. What awaits for the timid teacher, Aoki? In the end, is he in heaven or hell?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Takeshobo)","endDate":{"day":24,"month":7,"year":2018},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Psychological","Romance"],"id":108975,"idMal":121940,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/108975","startDate":{"day":26,"month":2,"year":2016},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Un démon au paradis","鬼與天國"],"title":{"english":"Heaven and Demon","native":"鬼と天国","romaji":"Oni to Tengoku","userPreferred":"Oni to Tengoku"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":2},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/108724-w0BfyJJeP0hJ.jpg","chapters":9,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e48643","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx108724-K0sz50MXSt68.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx108724-K0sz50MXSt68.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx108724-K0sz50MXSt68.jpg"},"description":"Tasaki is caught peeking by a group of gals who use the evidence to blackmail him into becoming their slave. One day Tasaki manages to hypnotize his masters. And so his revenge begins.\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: fourberie)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n1. \u003cb\u003eIjirare ~Fukushuu Saimin~ #1\u003c/b\u003e (イジラレ ～復讐催眠～ #1, Bullied ~Revenge Hypnosis~); Comic X-Eros #53\u003cbr\u003e\n2. \u003cb\u003eIjirare ~Fukushuu Saimin~ #2\u003c/b\u003e (イジラレ ～復讐催眠～ #2, Bullied ~Revenge Hypnosis~ #2); Comic X-Eros #55\u003cbr\u003e\n3. \u003cb\u003eIjirare ~Fukushuu Saimin~ #3\u003c/b\u003e (イジラレ ～復讐催眠～ #3, Bullied ~Revenge Hypnosis~ #3); Comic X-Eros #61\u003cbr\u003e\n4. \u003cb\u003eIjirare ~Fukushuu Saimin~ #4\u003c/b\u003e (イジラレ ～復讐催眠～ #4, Bullied ~Revenge Hypnosis~ #4); Comic X-Eros #63\u003cbr\u003e\n5. \u003cb\u003eIjirare ~Fukushuu Saimin~ #5\u003c/b\u003e (イジラレ ～復讐催眠～ #5, Bullied ~Revenge Hypnosis~ #5); Comic X-Eros #66\u003cbr\u003e\n6. \u003cb\u003eIjirare ~Sai Shuushou Zenpen~\u003c/b\u003e (イジラレ ～最終章前編～, Bullied ~Final Act Part 1~); Comic X-Eros #70\u003cbr\u003e\n7. \u003cb\u003eIjirare ~Sai Shuushou Chuuhen~\u003c/b\u003e (イジラレ ～最終章中編～, Bullied ~Final Act Part 2~); Comic X-Eros #73\u003cbr\u003e\n8. \u003cb\u003eIjirare ~Sai Shuushou Kouhen~\u003c/b\u003e (イジラレ ～最終章後編～, Bullied ~Revenge Hypnosis~ Finale); kakioroshi, Comic X-Eros #74\u003cbr\u003e\n9. \u003cb\u003eIjirare ~Epilogue~\u003c/b\u003e (イジラレ ～エピローグ～, Bullied ~Revenge Hypnosis~ Epilogue); kakioroshi\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: There are 2 store exclusive bonus chapters of 8 pages each one:\u003cbr\u003e\n- A chapter of Sae Hinata with the purchase in Toranoana (とらのあな).\u003cbr\u003e\n- A chapter of Minako Sanada with the purchase in Melonbooks (メロンブックス).\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":28,"month":3,"year":2019},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":108724,"idMal":113369,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/108724","startDate":{"day":28,"month":3,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Izirare ~Hukusyu Saimin~"," Hipnoza – zemsta ofiary "],"title":{"english":"Bullied ~Revenge Hypnosis~","native":"イジラレ ～復讐催眠～","romaji":"Ijirare: Fukushuu Saimin","userPreferred":"Ijirare: Fukushuu Saimin"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/n105862-UuVvWzcC5iTL.jpg","chapters":108,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f15d50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b105862-vMh5u9UawroA.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b105862-vMh5u9UawroA.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b105862-vMh5u9UawroA.jpg"},"description":"Hae-Soo is a cynical writer of a romance column, while Joo-Won, his former stepbrother, is a famous actor. The two go way back - thrust together when their parents remarried, their relationship is far from simple. Brothers? Soulmates? Friends with benefits? Or nothing at all? Theirs is a delicate balance between lust and loathing, dating and breaking up, irritation and infatuation. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nWhen the mysterious photographer “K” takes an interest in Hae-Soo, events begin to spiral out of control. As the lines between art and reality become increasingly blurred, what direction will this story take? Cheap romance? Sensual erotica? Or something much more twisted?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Lezhin US)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Chapter count includes two special side stories released in 2024.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":27,"month":2,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Psychological","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":105862,"idMal":123788,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":72,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/105862","startDate":{"day":22,"month":9,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Love or Hate","native":"러브 오어 헤이트","romaji":"Love or Hate","userPreferred":"Love or Hate"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":8},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":13,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#fff143","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx94819-DppuE4Wqmb1p.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx94819-DppuE4Wqmb1p.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx94819-DppuE4Wqmb1p.jpg"},"description":"\u003ci\u003ePart 5 of the Kuroneko Kareshi series.\u003c/i\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nShingo and Kagami are enjoying passionate relationship, but then Kagami's work starts to be more and more demanding. Or is it something else that is going on?\n","endDate":{"day":14,"month":5,"year":2016},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance","Supernatural"],"id":94819,"idMal":88850,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/94819","startDate":{"day":14,"month":5,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"クロネコ彼氏のあふれ方","romaji":"Kuroneko Kareshi no Afurekata","userPreferred":"Kuroneko Kareshi no Afurekata"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":3},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":8,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d61a86","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx164921-pYrgC7rZw0RG.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx164921-pYrgC7rZw0RG.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx164921-pYrgC7rZw0RG.jpg"},"description":"The long-awaited first compilation by Enokido, the newcomer who has jumped to the top of readers' surveys at Comic Anthurium!\n\u003cBR\u003e\u003cBR\u003e\nNanase is a gal who is frustrated because she is not satisfied with her boyfriend's selfish sex.\nOne day, she decides to take out her frustrations on her nerdy classmate Nozaki, trying to humiliate him by posting pictures of his dick. But when she sees Nozaki's huge cock, she can't help but feel a tingle in her body...?\n\u003cBR\u003e\u003cBR\u003e\nThe \u003cI\u003eGyaru to Kimoota\u003c/i\u003e series, which was very popular in the original magazine publication, leads off the collection.\u003cBR\u003e\nThis book is a must-see for all erotic manga lovers, filled with girls who just can't get enough once they get a taste of the sex!\n\u003cBR\u003e\u003cBR\u003e\n(Source: GOT Comics, translated)\n\u003cBR\u003e\u003cBR\u003e\nIncluded Stories:\u003cBR\u003e\n1-2. \u003cB\u003eBijo to Yajuu: Gal to KimoOta\u003c/b\u003e (美女と野獣 〜ギャルとキモオタ〜, The Beauty and The Beast ~The Gyaru and The Disgusting Otaku~); Comic Anthurium 2021-08, 2023-01\u003cBR\u003e\n3. \u003cB\u003eKyouei Senpai ni Nuite Morau\u003c/b\u003e (競泳先輩に抜いてもらう, Getting Jerked off by the Swimming Club Senpai); Comic Anthurium 2022-09\u003cBR\u003e\n4-5. \u003cB\u003eNen-ichi Ouse\u003c/b\u003e (年いち逢瀬, Yearly Secret Meeting); Comic Anthurium 2022-03, 2022-05\u003cBR\u003e\n6. \u003cB\u003eKenkou Yuuryou Boyish Shoujo Papakatsu wo Suru.\u003c/B\u003e (健康優良ボーイッシュ少女パパ活をする。)\u003cBR\u003e\n7. \u003cB\u003eOtonashi Ookami\u003c/b\u003e (おとなしオオカミ, The Quiet Wolf); Comic Anthurium 2021-03\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cu\u003e\u003cb\u003eDigital exclusive:\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n8. \u003cb\u003eOtonashi Ookami Sonogo\u003c/b\u003e (おとなしオオカミ その後); kakioroshi","endDate":{"day":13,"month":4,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":164921,"idMal":158833,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/164921","startDate":{"day":13,"month":4,"year":2023},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Bijo to Yajuu: Gal to KimoOta","Kyouei Senpai ni Nuite Morau","Nen-ichi Ouse","Kenkou Yuuryou Boyish Shoujo Papakatsu wo Suru.","Otonashi Ookami","Otonashi Ookami Sonogo"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"性欲つよつよ","romaji":"Seiyoku Tsuyo Tsuyo","userPreferred":"Seiyoku Tsuyo Tsuyo"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/152411-gBUryzmtDavF.jpg","chapters":155,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e46b5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx152411-7jvoGOyC3Eeq.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx152411-7jvoGOyC3Eeq.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx152411-7jvoGOyC3Eeq.jpg"},"description":"\u003ci\u003e\"Hey, loser. Did you just try to look at my panties?\"\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAn ordinary guy gains the power of the Incubus, and stops time right before getting slapped by a sexy girl...!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003e\"How dare you try to hit me? You need to be punished!!\"\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: DAYcomics)","endDate":{"day":3,"month":8,"year":2025},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Fantasy","Hentai","Supernatural"],"id":152411,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":72,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/152411","startDate":{"day":15,"month":7,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Sex Stopwatch","セッ◯ストップウォッチ","セックスストップウォッチ","色輪眼"],"title":{"english":"Sextopwatch","native":"섹톱워치","romaji":"Sextopwatch","userPreferred":"Sextopwatch"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/132686-T3dEh6Ma4NqZ.jpg","chapters":51,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4c95d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx132686-K8TgoHlN1S31.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx132686-K8TgoHlN1S31.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx132686-K8TgoHlN1S31.jpg"},"description":"All Joowon has ever wanted is a steady career outside of the spotlight. A single steamy night with an attractive stranger shouldn't derail that plan so thoroughly, except said attractive stranger is Aiden, an international top model. When they meet again on professional terms, Joowon is given a choice: have his steady career destroyed when Aiden turns down a contract with his company, or accept Aiden's offer to become sex partners until the contract period is over. And thus begins Joowon's ventures in bending over in more ways than one to meet Aiden’s demands...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin US)","endDate":{"day":24,"month":12,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":132686,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/132686","startDate":{"day":17,"month":10,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Run Away, Assistant Manager Ha!  ","Run, Mr. Ha!"],"title":{"english":"Bend Over Backwards","native":"도망쳐요! 하대리님","romaji":"Domangchyeoyo! Ha Daeri-nim","userPreferred":"Domangchyeoyo! Ha Daeri-nim"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/128826-b9CVSoSQc1GU.jpg","chapters":45,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4c9a1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b128826-9ZZhPHeZGVI4.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b128826-9ZZhPHeZGVI4.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b128826-9ZZhPHeZGVI4.jpg"},"description":"Lim Iro is a BL writer, and a pretty successful one at that! His last project was lavished with praise by everyone… Well, almost everyone. Under pressure from his unimpressed parents, Iro is forced into applying for a “real” job. But instead of a cover letter, he accidentally submits an unreleased extract from his book instead! Disaster! Or maybe not…? Faced with Iro’s unconventional application, Baek Ho-ryung, the dashing CEO of Beus drinks company, is intrigued. But once Iro joins Beus, will his office life begin to emulate his steamy writing…?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin)","endDate":{"day":12,"month":10,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance"],"id":128826,"idMal":147918,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/128826","startDate":{"day":20,"month":2,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["It's Not Like That","No es lo que parece","Ce n'est pas ça","Nicht Falsch Verstehen, Boss!","才不是那樣的啦","มันไม่ใช่แบบนั้น..จริงๆ นะ"],"title":{"english":"Don't Get Me Wrong, Boss!","native":"그런 게 아닙니다만","romaji":"Geureon Ge Animnidaman","userPreferred":"Geureon Ge Animnidaman"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/125648-fZ6A11eUnFGq.jpg","chapters":45,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx125648-gV1Bmm2JxHJq.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx125648-gV1Bmm2JxHJq.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx125648-gV1Bmm2JxHJq.jpg"},"description":"All Isaac the beta wants is to live a normal life as a slightly unskilled florist and leave his turbulent past behind. That dream quickly goes out the window, however, when the infamous arms dealer Felix waltzes into his shop and takes a liking to him. It just so happens that Isaac's family needs protection from a mysterious enemy, and luckily, Felix is more than willing to provide it in return for Isaac's body. The more Felix falls for the reserved florist, the more he wants to unlock his many secrets. And as things heat up in the bedroom, Isaac finds it harder to resist the handsome alpha and his powerful pheromones. Meanwhile, the secret about their shared past hangs in the air like a ticking timebomb...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Tappytoon)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Drama","Hentai","Romance"],"id":125648,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/125648","startDate":{"day":2,"month":2,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Dear Benjamin","native":"디어 벤자민","romaji":"Dear Benjamin","userPreferred":"Dear Benjamin"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e47843","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx117658-AAVfryoWonjg.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx117658-AAVfryoWonjg.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx117658-AAVfryoWonjg.png"},"description":"A prestigious school can't let its students have sex willy-nilly. That'd be irresponsible. Instead, it'll provide them with pre-approved, school-sanctioned gigolos.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source:  Irodori Comics)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003cbr\u003e\n- Originally self-published under the name \"\u003cb\u003eSeika Jogakuin Koutoubu Kounin Sao Oji-san\u003c/b\u003e (聖華女学院高等部公認竿おじさん)\".\u003cbr\u003e\n- A live-action AV adaptation (EBOD-918) was released on June 21st, 2022.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":117658,"idMal":136314,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":79,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/117658","startDate":{"day":31,"month":12,"year":2018},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Seika Jogakuin Koutoubu Kounin Sao Oji-san","聖華女学院高等部公認竿おじさん"],"title":{"english":"The Seika Girls and the School-Sanctioned Gigolo","native":"聖華女学院公認竿おじさん","romaji":"Seika Jogakuin Kounin Sao Oji-san","userPreferred":"Seika Jogakuin Kounin Sao Oji-san"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4d650","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/nx106714-wWbtsgKSeMDR.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/nx106714-wWbtsgKSeMDR.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/nx106714-wWbtsgKSeMDR.jpg"},"description":"19-year-old Nana is a good-looking, popular college student who'd like nothing more than to keep rumors of his prowess in the bedroom alive. He has a secret, though: his age equals the number of years he hasn't had a girlfriend! In other words, he's completely inexperienced!! Nana's so committed to living up to the idea others have of him that he can't even say he likes sweetened coffee. His classmate, Akira Mizuno, doesn't even try to hide the fact that he's gay, and Nana's drawn to Akira's unapologetic way of living life while being true to himself... Will Nana's first love ever bear fruit, and will he be able to lose his v-card without mishap!? This is a cute and sexy romantic-comedy about popping your cherry!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Renta!)","endDate":{"day":25,"month":7,"year":2018},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":106714,"idMal":116514,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/106714","startDate":{"day":24,"month":11,"year":2017},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Virgin Nana-kun foreign love","Doutei Nana-kun ☆ Foreign Love"],"title":{"english":"Inexperienced and in Love","native":"童貞ナナくん☆フォーリンラブ","romaji":"Doutei Nana-kun ☆ Fall in Love","userPreferred":"Doutei Nana-kun ☆ Fall in Love"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/98168-a26rsZPfNch2.jpg","chapters":13,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4501a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx98168-16X4yG0TIzui.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx98168-16X4yG0TIzui.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx98168-16X4yG0TIzui.jpg"},"description":"Shoukichi is a stylist who struggles with being unpopular due to him being unfriendly and overly serious about everything. Fukusuke, a top stylist who is frivolous and sarcastic, starts working at Shoukichi’s salon. One night, Shoukichi lets Fukusuke stay over at his place because Fukusuke missed the last train. While Shoukichi is sleeping, Fukusuke climbs on top of him and pushes his dick in his face. Because of this perverted thing that Fukusuke does, Shoukichi begins to hate him more and more. However, as creepy things continue to happen to Shoukichi, his thoughts about Fukusuke begin to change…\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nMaybe he’s a prince…?\u003cbr\u003e\n\nWhat happens to someone who is stubborn but passionate about something they really want….?","endDate":{"day":1,"month":6,"year":2018},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Psychological","Romance"],"id":98168,"idMal":90822,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":72,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/98168","startDate":{"day":30,"month":3,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[" คัลเลอร์เรซิพี"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"カラーレシピ","romaji":"Color Recipe","userPreferred":"Color Recipe"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":2},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":5,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx86489-K7oTqv8Ycs6f.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx86489-K7oTqv8Ycs6f.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx86489-K7oTqv8Ycs6f.png"},"description":"He hit me again today. My lover Kan-chan, that is. But that doesn’t really matter. My love is being rusted by our bodily fluids. Mayama, my middle school classmate, has appeared before my rusted self and become conscious of my bruises and scars. But you want it to be like the past, on that rainy day you kissed me and froze… I won’t be satisfied with a naïve love. Drawn by Ogeretsu Tanaka, this is a story of true love and pain.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Shinshokan, translated)","endDate":{"day":14,"month":10,"year":2014},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":86489,"idMal":88314,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/86489","startDate":{"day":14,"month":7,"year":2014},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Love Whispers"," Even in the Rusted Night","Sabita Yorudemo Koiwa Sasayaku","Jak usłyszeć miłość? "],"title":{"english":null,"native":"錆びた夜でも恋は囁く","romaji":"Sabita Yoru Demo Koi Wa Sasayaku","userPreferred":"Sabita Yoru Demo Koi Wa Sasayaku"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":13,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae86","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx41670-2P7Hni2TOsUx.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx41670-2P7Hni2TOsUx.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx41670-2P7Hni2TOsUx.png"},"description":"Reno's got a new roommate and his name is Roger Brower. His nickname is \"Casanova\" and there are rumors that he sells his body for money. Soon after arriving he asks Reno if he can leave the room for 3 hours once every 2 to 3 days so he can have sex with his clients, and Reno realizes the rumors are true. He tells Reno that he'll give him some of the money he makes as payment for renting out the room for that time. Reno reluctantly agrees and everything is going just fine until the day he accidentally walks back into their shared room and is confronted with the sight of Roger having sex with one of his customers.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Manga Planet)","endDate":{"day":16,"month":8,"year":2014},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":41670,"idMal":11670,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/41670","startDate":{"day":12,"month":8,"year":2006},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["神様の腕の中～満ちる部屋season１～","The Full Room"],"title":{"english":"Inside God's Arms: A Room Filled With Love","native":"満ちる部屋","romaji":"Michiru Heya","userPreferred":"Michiru Heya"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":2},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/765-Ez3MQgQFCIdg.jpg","chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f135a1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/765-TAPxKFkDrekO.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/765-TAPxKFkDrekO.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/765-TAPxKFkDrekO.jpg"},"description":"The \u003ci\u003eJunjou Romantica\u003c/i\u003e series features the stories of three couples, which are all loosely interconnected.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eJunjou Romantica\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nMisaki Takahashi, struggling to pass his college entrance exams, is in need of a tutor to help pump up his failing grades. Unfortunately, his only option is the cool and sexy Akihiko Usami. Usami happens to be a famous boys’ love novelist, which doesn’t exactly float Misaki’s boat, especially since his main characters are “Akihiko” and “Takahiro,” the name of Misaki’s older brother and Usami’s childhood friend. Understandably, Misaki is pretty disgusted by the thought of someone using his older brother as his personal fantasy-material, but then after some tender loving from Usami, Misaki is also pretty confused. He may even be developing feelings for the older man...And when Takahiro introduces them to his lovely (female) fiancée, so begins the bumpy relationship of this odd couple, filled with comedy and pure romance.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eJunjou Egoist\u003c/b\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nKamijou Hiroki is a broken man, consumed by unrequited love for his childhood friend, Usami Akihiko.  Along comes Kusama Nowaki, whose name \"Nowaki\" means \"typhoon\", an orphan working his way through life since middle school.  Like the typhoon he is named for, he whirls into Hiroki's life and heart, blowing all resistance away before him.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eJunjou Terrorist\u003c/b\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nAs fate would have it,  Professor Miyagi Yoh (whom Hiroki is working with as assistant professor), and Takatsuki Shinobu, a high school student, cross paths.  Miyagi, when in high school, loved (and still cannot forget) a female teacher who had a terminal illness, is now faced with Shinobu, who just says whatever is on his mind. The wheel of destiny is beginning to turn once again...","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance"],"id":30765,"idMal":765,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":72,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/30765","startDate":{"day":30,"month":4,"year":2002},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Pure Romance","Jyunjyou Romantica","Junjou Egoist"],"title":{"english":"Junjo Romantica","native":"純情ロマンチカ","romaji":"Junjou Romantica","userPreferred":"Junjou Romantica"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/200205-XvvRf3w51uBO.jpg","chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#50fe50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx200205-FqN9nV27wACK.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx200205-FqN9nV27wACK.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx200205-FqN9nV27wACK.jpg"},"description":"Four years ago, the idol group Dream Boy disbanded after being embroiled in some kind of scandal. And now... Jae-Young, formerly known as \"Happy\" in Dream Boy, was struggling financially and working a part-time delivery job when he heard that the group's leader, Su-Kyum, had passed out drunk at a club, and he rushed to him. Although they share the same stage name, Seung-Min, aka \"Happy\" and the most popular rapper and producer these days, saves Jae-Young from collapsing from photosensitivity syndrome and suggests they work together... \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003ci\u003e\"You know who I am, right? Let's work together.\"\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Ridibooks, translated)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":200205,"idMal":191004,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":85,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/200205","startDate":{"day":4,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["해피2게더","Happy Together"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"해피투게더","romaji":"HAPPY Twogether","userPreferred":"HAPPY Twogether"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx176580-MxoCOhiYelE4.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx176580-MxoCOhiYelE4.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx176580-MxoCOhiYelE4.jpg"},"description":"\u003ci\u003e\"He looks like a cold and handsome Alpha…who’d ever think he was actually a twisted and sexy Omega!\"\u003c/i\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nKota is a college student, and an Alpha. Still, he dreads bumping into his neighbor, a super-intimidating hunk with big, black tattoos. He always assumed this mystery man was an Alpha, too, and avoided him like the plague...until, one day, a scent wafts in so powerful it puts even the dull-headed Kota in a daze. It’s the scent of Omega pheromones, from next door! He assumes his neighbor's brought an Omega home, but when he tries to leave, what should he find but the source of the pheromones: his hot neighbor! How will he get out of this situation unscathed, and without his neighbor finding out he’s a virgin?!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Kodansha USA)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":176580,"idMal":167686,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/176580","startDate":{"day":28,"month":10,"year":2022},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"How to Deal When Your Intimidating Neighbor is Actually an Omega","native":"コワモテの隣人がΩだった時の対処法","romaji":"Kowamote no Rinjin ga Ω datta Toki no Taishohou","userPreferred":"Kowamote no Rinjin ga Ω datta Toki no Taishohou"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#c9d6f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx160501-vpzrbQnu9eXv.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx160501-vpzrbQnu9eXv.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx160501-vpzrbQnu9eXv.png"},"description":"Kuroda drops by her geeky classmate's home whenever she likes to read his comics, but not without a fair trade. While she lounges in his room, he’s allowed to use her body.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Irodori Comics)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003cbr\u003e\n- Released at Comic Market 101, 103, 104, 105, 106\u003cbr\u003e\n- It has live-action AV adaptations: MIMK-138 (2023/12/01) and a remake, MIMK-186 (2024/11/29), MIMK-253 (2025/10/17)\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":160501,"idMal":155748,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/160501","startDate":{"day":31,"month":12,"year":2022},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Iribitari Gal ni Ma〇ko Tsukawasete Morau Hanashi","The Gyaru I Hang Out with Lets Me Use Her Pussy"],"title":{"english":"Drop-in Gyaru Lets Me Use Her Pussy","native":"入り浸りギャルにま〇こ使わせて貰う話","romaji":"Iribitari Gal ni Manko Tsukawasete Morau Hanashi","userPreferred":"Iribitari Gal ni Manko Tsukawasete Morau Hanashi"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null}],"pageInfo":{"currentPage":7,"hasNextPage":true,"lastPage":104,"perPage":48,"total":5000}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-15T06:40:48.470639+03:00"},"{\"query\":\"query ListManga ($page: Int, $search: String, $perPage: Int, $sort: [MediaSort], $status: [MediaStatus], $genres: [String], $averageScore_greater: Int, $startDate_greater: FuzzyDateInt, $startDate_lesser: FuzzyDateInt, $format: MediaFormat, $countryOfOrigin: CountryCode, $isAdult: Boolean) {\\n\\tPage(page: $page, perPage: $perPage) {\\n\\t\\tpageInfo {\\n\\t\\t\\thasNextPage\\n\\t\\t\\ttotal\\n\\t\\t\\tperPage\\n\\t\\t\\tcurrentPage\\n\\t\\t\\tlastPage\\n\\t\\t}\\n\\t\\tmedia(type: MANGA, isAdult: $isAdult, countryOfOrigin: $countryOfOrigin, search: $search, sort: $sort, status_in: $status, format: $format, genre_in: $genres, averageScore_greater: $averageScore_greater, startDate_greater: $startDate_greater, startDate_lesser: $startDate_lesser, format_not: NOVEL) {\\n\\t\\t\\t... baseManga\\n\\t\\t}\\n\\t}\\n}\\nfragment baseManga on Media {\\n\\tid\\n\\tidMal\\n\\tsiteUrl\\n\\tstatus(version: 2)\\n\\tseason\\n\\ttype\\n\\tformat\\n\\tbannerImage\\n\\tchapters\\n\\tvolumes\\n\\tsynonyms\\n\\tisAdult\\n\\tcountryOfOrigin\\n\\tmeanScore\\n\\tdescription\\n\\tgenres\\n\\ttitle {\\n\\t\\tuserPreferred\\n\\t\\tromaji\\n\\t\\tenglish\\n\\t\\tnative\\n\\t}\\n\\tcoverImage {\\n\\t\\textraLarge\\n\\t\\tlarge\\n\\t\\tmedium\\n\\t\\tcolor\\n\\t}\\n\\tstartDate {\\n\\t\\tyear\\n\\t\\tmonth\\n\\t\\tday\\n\\t}\\n\\tendDate {\\n\\t\\tyear\\n\\t\\tmonth\\n\\t\\tday\\n\\t}\\n}\\n\",\"variables\":{\"isAdult\":true,\"page\":8,\"perPage\":48,\"sort\":[\"SCORE_DESC\"]}}":{"value":{"Page":{"media":[{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e42835","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx158465-71jyBqVcMnYX.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx158465-71jyBqVcMnYX.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx158465-71jyBqVcMnYX.jpg"},"description":"Kaoru, a high school student infamously known as a fighting-fanatic, gains a sudden fascination with a new transfer student who is rumored to be incredibly dangerous. One day, he witnesses this mysterious underclassman, Shun, in a blood-boiling fight and ends up falling head-over-heels in love... But, when he goes to confess, he's mistaken as another attacker and must defend himself against the younger boy's lethal strikes! While the fight leaves Kaoru beaten and bruised, he suddenly finds himself being kissed...!? As if that wasn't confusing enough, Shun seems endeared by Kaoru's inexperience with love and agrees to date him, kicking off the start of a terrifying romance!\n\u003cBR\u003e\u003cBR\u003e\n(Source: Renta!)\n\u003cBR\u003e\u003cBR\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":28,"month":1,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Comedy","Romance"],"id":158465,"idMal":152138,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/158465","startDate":{"day":30,"month":4,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Don't Get in the Way of Shun's Romance","native":"牧田くんの恋路をジャマすると死ぬ","romaji":"Makita-kun No Koiji wo Jamasuru to Shinu","userPreferred":"Makita-kun No Koiji wo Jamasuru to Shinu"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":16,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx143206-BqHzINCKEdLW.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx143206-BqHzINCKEdLW.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx143206-BqHzINCKEdLW.jpg"},"description":"\"It's my first time with a man or a human, but... Like this, the only way we'll be able to calm down is to fuck each other.\"While relationships between humans and beastmen are still rare, an omega with a beastman fetish, Sakutaro, spends his days taking his suppressants and dreaming of beastmen. However, one day, Sakutarou suddenly goes into heat in the middle of the street. Then, he's saved by a beastman he's never seen before...!? With such an excellent man in front of him, he can't stop himself from obscenely connecting their scorching bodies together...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Renta!)\n\u003cBR\u003e\u003cBR\u003e\n\u003cI\u003eNote: Chapter count includes two extras.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":2,"month":11,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Fantasy","Romance"],"id":143206,"idMal":144747,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/143206","startDate":{"day":11,"month":6,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Mr. Wolf Is Violently Smothering Me with Love","native":"オオカミ様の一途な暴愛","romaji":"Ookami-sama no Ichizu na Bouai  ","userPreferred":"Ookami-sama no Ichizu na Bouai  "},"type":"MANGA","volumes":2},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":14,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#0da1e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx136419-NWgjnWU3DhXV.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx136419-NWgjnWU3DhXV.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx136419-NWgjnWU3DhXV.jpg"},"description":"Ms. Sumire Mizuno, an efficient office worker has a secret hobby... She wears cute and very erotic lingerie and posts sexy selfies on social media! To relieve the stress of everyday work, she does it on her secret account. But one day, Murasaki, a designer of the company's supplier has identified her by chance. In exchange for keeping it a secret, he makes an unexpectedly serious proposal. He wants Sumire to model the lingerie he designs so he can get feedback and test the texture and functionality of the product in real situations. Puzzled as she has imagined much worse, but mixed with such shame and confusion, she spontaneously asks him to \"Have sex with me\"!!!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: MangaPlaza)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":19,"month":10,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":136419,"idMal":143855,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/136419","startDate":{"day":15,"month":1,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["星期五的紫羅蘭寶貝","See U on Friday, Baby violet"],"title":{"english":"Friday Night Baby Violet","native":"金曜日のベイビーヴァイオレット","romaji":"Kinyoubi no Baby Violet","userPreferred":"Kinyoubi no Baby Violet"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":2},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/132623-baxCVrFPhVQW.jpg","chapters":12,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e42835","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx132623-0VLr2UQPeoZo.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx132623-0VLr2UQPeoZo.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx132623-0VLr2UQPeoZo.png"},"description":"Two people in the catalogue department fall in love, get quickly married, and emigrate to another country, leaving their positions to be filled by new recruits “Bada Lee” and “Seomin Hyun.” While Bada manages song playlists, and Seomin hoards glasses cloths, the two are competing rivals.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Copincomics)","endDate":{"day":28,"month":4,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":132623,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":76,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/132623","startDate":{"day":28,"month":4,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Glasses Cloth and Playlist","native":"안경닦이와 재생목록","romaji":"Angyeongdakk-Iwa Jaesaengmongnok","userPreferred":"Angyeongdakk-Iwa Jaesaengmongnok"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1c9ae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx129247-RGL3XrhlpoY0.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx129247-RGL3XrhlpoY0.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx129247-RGL3XrhlpoY0.jpg"},"description":"Jeong Taeui has always lived in the shadow of his genius twin brother, but he’s never been unhappy with his ordinary life. When his uncle shows up at his doorstep with a dangerous job offer disguised as a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity, Taeui is skeptical, but he reluctantly agrees to work as an agent for half a year. Despite his initial qualms, he quickly adjusts to his new environment using his outgoing, positive personality. But from the moment Taeui meets Ilay Riegrow, an agent from another branch, his peaceful life slowly starts to change. Everyone says Ilay is a sadistic psychopath who should be avoided at all costs, but Taeui knows there’s more to him than meets the eye. But getting to know Ilay is like playing with fire, and Taeui isn’t sure if he’s ready to get burned.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tappytoon)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Drama","Romance"],"id":129247,"idMal":184873,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/129247","startDate":{"day":27,"month":10,"year":2020},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["盛情难却","受难曲","PASSION แพชชัน"],"title":{"english":"PASSION","native":"패션","romaji":"PASSION","userPreferred":"PASSION"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":7,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#3593ae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx126113-dK7FlPhSY5oS.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx126113-dK7FlPhSY5oS.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx126113-dK7FlPhSY5oS.png"},"description":"\u003ci\u003e“I’ve killed someone, please arrest me!”\u003c/i\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n...is what he said as he rushed into the police station, but it was all just a dream. 27-year-old Kaga Mitsuki has just done something unspeakably embarrassing. Later, Kaga goes to the police station to apologize and is greeted by Seto Kenya, a young police officer who is kind and has great taste. Moreover, Seto tells Kaga, “If you have another nightmare and feel anxious, please come see me!” and they become closer and closer friends... At this rate, Kaga won't be able to resist falling for Seto! From then on, Kaga’s nightmares turn into erotic dreams of Seto…\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAn erotic and heart-wrenching romantic comedy BL featuring a young, dog-like police officer and a corporate slave!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Media Soft, translated)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":25,"month":6,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":126113,"idMal":131430,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/126113","startDate":{"day":28,"month":6,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["How Far Is My Dream Allowed?","Le droit de rêver"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"夢ならどこまで許されますか?","romaji":"Yume nara Doko made Yurusaremasu ka?","userPreferred":"Yume nara Doko made Yurusaremasu ka?"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/124443-OrOi3zZxfKQW.jpg","chapters":130,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e44350","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx124443-kK3SzxpSjZP4.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx124443-kK3SzxpSjZP4.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx124443-kK3SzxpSjZP4.jpg"},"description":"One wedding, two heartbreaks.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nYu-Ri attends the wedding of his unrequited love. There, he runs into his former homeroom teacher Seon-Woo, who seems just as heartbroken by the union. But little does he know that Seon-Woo's tears are meant not for the bride, but for the groom...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Manta)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes 38 side story chapters and 17 epilogue chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":13,"month":9,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":124443,"idMal":134658,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/124443","startDate":{"day":6,"month":8,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Form of Sympathy","同情的形態","同情のカタチ","Une forme de compassion","A Form of Sympathy","La silueta de tu compasión"],"title":{"english":"The Shape of Sympathy","native":"동정의 형태","romaji":"Dongjeongui Hyeongtae","userPreferred":"Dongjeongui Hyeongtae"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":7},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4a15d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx112934-g7SVeolDMC3G.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx112934-g7SVeolDMC3G.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx112934-g7SVeolDMC3G.jpg"},"description":"In a world where humans and demi-humans life together and both populations are declining, humans deemed \"supporters\" assist various races once they reach an age of maturity. With matchmaking automated and pairings a mystery, a teacher is surprised when his match is not only an elf princess, but also his own student!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Fakku)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n1. \u003cb\u003eEnjo Kouhai\u003c/b\u003e (援助交配); Comic Market 91\u003cbr\u003e\n2. \u003cb\u003eEnjo Kouhai 2\u003c/b\u003e (援助交配2); Comic1☆11\u003cbr\u003e\n3. \u003cb\u003eEnjo Kouhai 3\u003c/b\u003e (援助交配3); Comic Market 92\u003cbr\u003e\n4. \u003cb\u003eEnjo Kouhai 4\u003c/b\u003e (援助交配4); Comic Market 93\u003cbr\u003e\n5. \u003cb\u003eEnjo Kouhai 5\u003c/b\u003e (援助交配5); Comic1☆13\u003cbr\u003e\n6. \u003cb\u003eEnjo Kouhai 6\u003c/b\u003e (援助交配6); Comic Market 94\u003cbr\u003e\n7. \u003cb\u003eEnjo Kouhai 7\u003c/b\u003e (援助交配7); Comic Market 95\u003cbr\u003e\n8. \u003cb\u003eEnjo Kouhai 8\u003c/b\u003e (援助交配8); Comic Market 96\u003cbr\u003e\n9. \u003cb\u003eEnjo Kouhai 9\u003c/b\u003e (援助交配9); Comic Market 97\u003cbr\u003e\n10. \u003cb\u003eEnjo Kouhai 10\u003c/b\u003e (援助交配10); Comic Market 98\u003cbr\u003e\n11. \u003cb\u003eEnjo Kouhai 11\u003c/b\u003e (援助交配10); Sunshine Creation 2021 Summer\u003cbr\u003e\n12. \u003cb\u003eEnjo Kouhai 12\u003c/b\u003e (援助交配10); Comic Market 99\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003cbr\u003e\n- Includes 7 extra chapters\u003cbr\u003e","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":112934,"idMal":122342,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":80,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/112934","startDate":{"day":31,"month":12,"year":2016},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Enjyo Kouhai"],"title":{"english":"Assisted Mating","native":"援助交配","romaji":"Enjo Kouhai","userPreferred":"Enjo Kouhai"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/110017-gyp9AJZoYiKI.jpg","chapters":46,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b110017-q331nSicDy4o.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b110017-q331nSicDy4o.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b110017-q331nSicDy4o.jpg"},"description":"Junwoo, a hikikomori, passes his days alone, nestled within the darkness of his room that protects him from the outside world. The one strand of light capable of piercing his world is Hanbit, his neighbor and love interest. But when Hanbit leaves to study abroad, Junwoo is forced to take on a roommate to make ends meet. Could this break to his routine be the very thing that Junwoo needs to free himself of his darkness?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Lezhin)","endDate":{"day":15,"month":3,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Hentai","Romance"],"id":110017,"idMal":124405,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":72,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/110017","startDate":{"day":29,"month":5,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Incidentally Living Together","Casual Cohabitation"],"title":{"english":"Home Alone Together","native":"우연한 동거","romaji":"Uyeonhan Donggeo","userPreferred":"Uyeonhan Donggeo"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/97897-8vmCocYMGk0i.jpg","chapters":71,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#d61a28","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx97897-VRFGDkWdrYIE.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx97897-VRFGDkWdrYIE.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx97897-VRFGDkWdrYIE.jpg"},"description":"Yoon Bum, a scrawny and quiet man, has a crush on one of the most popular and handsome guys in his college: Sangwoo. After the two cross paths again, Yoon Bum's feelings grow in intensity until they become an obsession–and he breaks into Sangwoo's home. But what he sees inside is not the Sangwoo of his fantasies; his dreams of this alluring man abruptly turn into a nightmare.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003cbr\u003e\n- Won the Grand Prize in Lezhin's 2nd World Comic Contest.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Includes four extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":21,"month":3,"year":2019},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Horror","Mystery","Psychological","Thriller"],"id":97897,"idMal":121079,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":71,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/97897","startDate":{"day":3,"month":11,"year":2016},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Killing Stalking","native":"킬링 스토킹","romaji":"Killing Stalking","userPreferred":"Killing Stalking"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":8},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":5,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e47850","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx95889-d0iSPLTeNoew.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx95889-d0iSPLTeNoew.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx95889-d0iSPLTeNoew.jpg"},"description":"Shy Mii-kun and lively Kei-chan have been friends ever since their first meeting in the snowy countryside. The two are inseparable—that is until Kei-chan gets a girlfriend. Mii-kun, who is secretly carrying a torch for his best friend, is devastated. How will their relationship change?","endDate":{"day":7,"month":1,"year":2013},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama"],"id":95889,"idMal":92583,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/95889","startDate":{"day":1,"month":3,"year":2012},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["The Long Way Home: Otaru-hen","El largo camino a casa"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"いとしの猫っ毛 小樽篇","romaji":"Itoshi no Nekokke: Otaru-hen","userPreferred":"Itoshi no Nekokke: Otaru-hen"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":30,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e40d0d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx164701-4jeWt3Vu9ZY1.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx164701-4jeWt3Vu9ZY1.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx164701-4jeWt3Vu9ZY1.png"},"description":"Calahan, a famous hunter who has captured 999 wanted criminals, chooses Johnny the Grifter as the final target of his career for a reward of 10 million pais. But Johnny, a con man who preys on the pockets of the elderly, insists he's innocent... \"If I prove my innocence, you give me a million pais.” Calahan and Johnny embark on a wild ride with a million pais on the line, and a mysterious group of men in hot pursuit. There's only ten days until they reach their destination, and both will do whatever it takes to win the bet - dead or alive.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin US)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Chapter count includes a prologue and an epilogue.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":6,"month":5,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":164701,"idMal":177258,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/164701","startDate":{"day":17,"month":11,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["데드 오어 어라이브"],"title":{"english":"Dead Or Alive","native":"DEAD OR ALIVE","romaji":"DEAD OR ALIVE","userPreferred":"DEAD OR ALIVE"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d6bb1a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx155029-T86eN14X12Ej.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx155029-T86eN14X12Ej.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx155029-T86eN14X12Ej.jpg"},"description":"From the sight of the sun beaming through the bright blue sky to the smell of green grass to the sound of hot, sweaty sex, summer carries a lot of memories. When Keito goes back to his hometown in the countryside for the first time in years, he's met with those memories in the flesh — his two childhood friends, Suiren and Aoi, but this time, they might want to be more than friends.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Irodori Comics)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":155029,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":82,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/155029","startDate":{"day":11,"month":12,"year":2021},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Summer Friends and Summer Flings","native":"夏のヤリなおし","romaji":"Natsu no Yari Naoshi","userPreferred":"Natsu no Yari Naoshi"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":1,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1d6bb","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx153376-VLEhOo6zsWBB.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx153376-VLEhOo6zsWBB.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx153376-VLEhOo6zsWBB.png"},"description":null,"endDate":{"day":14,"month":8,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":153376,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":80,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/153376","startDate":{"day":14,"month":8,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["My Neighbor Ayane ~Coincidental Meeting~"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"となりのあやねさん 出先でばったり編","romaji":"Tonari no Ayane-san: Desaki de Battari-hen","userPreferred":"Tonari no Ayane-san: Desaki de Battari-hen"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":1,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb86","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx138782-Y9rKFyfGMOtk.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx138782-Y9rKFyfGMOtk.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx138782-Y9rKFyfGMOtk.png"},"description":null,"endDate":{"day":28,"month":8,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":138782,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/138782","startDate":{"day":28,"month":8,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Ayane-san From Next-Door Naughty Selfies and Punishment Sex Volume","My Neighbor Ayane ~Teasing Selfies and Smutty Punishment~"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"となりのあやねさん いたずら自撮りとお仕置きえっち編","romaji":"Tonari no Ayane-san: Itazura Jidori to Oshioki Ecchi-hen","userPreferred":"Tonari no Ayane-san: Itazura Jidori to Oshioki Ecchi-hen"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":7,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4785d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx135387-hv5sjl7mQxtX.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx135387-hv5sjl7mQxtX.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx135387-hv5sjl7mQxtX.png"},"description":"When Omega Akihiro and Alpha Reiya are pushed into an engagement arranged by their parents, they’re doubtful they can ever be happy together. But as they get to know each other, their reluctance shifts into… something else. Their passion verges on obsession: Every moment apart is spent yearning to be together again, affecting their ability to concentrate on the rest of their studies and relationships. As their feelings grow, they will have to push past the fears and expectations they have for each other (and themselves) to discover a love they never thought possible.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: TOKYOPOP)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":26,"month":2,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":135387,"idMal":137254,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/135387","startDate":{"day":28,"month":4,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"I Wanna Love You, Kiss You, Bite You","native":"恋して キスして かんじゃいたい","romaji":"Koishite Kiss Shite Kanjaitai","userPreferred":"Koishite Kiss Shite Kanjaitai"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/124002-be3fMeg97cNI.jpg","chapters":55,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae93","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx124002-cz7V4soh3l3M.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx124002-cz7V4soh3l3M.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx124002-cz7V4soh3l3M.jpg"},"description":"Hyuk is a happy-go-lucky college student who’s dating the girl of his dreams. But there’s one issue: when it’s showtime in the bedroom, he gets massive performance anxiety. Desperate to keep his girlfriend, Hyuk works up the courage to go see a urologist. He prepares for the worst, but his first prostate exam actually feels…amazing?! Thanks to one smooth Dr. Han and his masterful hands, Hyuk is now on the path to recovery through regular massage sessions! How lucky of him to have found such an attentive doctor, one who’ll even take him out for drinks to listen to his woes. But as the treatments unfold, Dr. Han has a way of slipping into Hyuk’s mind, not just his bum… \n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin US)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cI\u003eNote: Includes five extras.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":25,"month":4,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":124002,"idMal":185227,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/124002","startDate":{"day":1,"month":6,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["ラブミードクター！"],"title":{"english":"Love Me, Doctor!","native":"럽미닥터!","romaji":"Love Me Doctor!","userPreferred":"Love Me Doctor!"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":9,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b122840-5pPOO4bzcxyP.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b122840-5pPOO4bzcxyP.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b122840-5pPOO4bzcxyP.jpg"},"description":"Misaki has always loved video games and would do anything to break into the industry. Despite his silly, happy-go-lucky attitude, he’s always putting his head down to be the best game designer around. And Misaki’s certain he is—at least, until he meets Kaname, a stoic genius who tops him in just about every way. With his skills, smarts, and sweet smile, Kaname has Misaki swirling in a pool of envy, admiration, and maybe even love. Will Misaki be able to overcome his jealousy and learn how to love Kaname?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: SuBLime)","endDate":{"day":7,"month":7,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":122840,"idMal":119917,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/122840","startDate":{"day":7,"month":3,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["デイジージェラシー","เดซีเจลัสซี"],"title":{"english":"Daisy Jealousy","native":"Daisy Jealousy","romaji":"Daisy Jealousy","userPreferred":"Daisy Jealousy"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx120188-FlAdHCwygyjE.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx120188-FlAdHCwygyjE.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx120188-FlAdHCwygyjE.jpg"},"description":"Will you make love to me? Just once? Ryohei is a guy who cannot commit. He is tired of being asked by the people he sleeps with, \"Do you actually like me!?\" On the day of their high school graduation, the smartest guy in their grade, Yuma, asks Ryohei for a favor. \"Two guys? He can't be serious.\" Ryohei can't believe what Yuma's asking him to do, but he is intrigued by Yuma's offer of \"no strings attached.\" It's Ryohei's first time with a guy, and he finds himself growing curious as he watches Yuma's sensitive body twist and turn. Even if he doesn't say it in words, Ryohei can tell Yuma has deep feelings for him, which triggers Ryohei's assertive side...! \n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nA tantalizing story about a devoted bottom who awakens something in a stubborn top.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Renta!)","endDate":{"day":19,"month":2,"year":2019},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":120188,"idMal":131574,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/120188","startDate":{"day":21,"month":8,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["A body that only knows me","Oreshika Shiranai Karada"],"title":{"english":"I'm the Only One Who Knows Your Body","native":"俺しか知らないカラダ","romaji":"Ore Shika Shiranai Karada","userPreferred":"Ore Shika Shiranai Karada"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":7,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae28","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx117482-Hs56szKRHXyR.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx117482-Hs56szKRHXyR.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx117482-Hs56szKRHXyR.jpg"},"description":"Kaname and Shima have been living together for a year. They have sex almost every day, and things are going well for the couple—at least until Kaname begins to think he’s a sex addict and starts avoiding sex with Shima. Shima, on the other hand, mistakenly believes Kaname is bored of him. Will their long-awaited trip to Tokyo resolve this misunderstanding before it snowballs into an avalanche?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes two extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":10,"month":4,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":117482,"idMal":131100,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/117482","startDate":{"day":6,"month":10,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Our Sweet One-Room Apartment","native":"スイートアワー1R","romaji":"Sweet Our 1R","userPreferred":"Sweet Our 1R"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":7,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e44378","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx112061-Cwd3RAwiUkn7.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx112061-Cwd3RAwiUkn7.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx112061-Cwd3RAwiUkn7.jpg"},"description":"When Makoto is practicing his professions of love in the park one night, Shiro happens to hear the words \"I love you\" while passing by. As a monster that consumes words, Shiro finds Makoto's particularly tasty and the two soon find themselves living together.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Renta!)","endDate":{"day":20,"month":5,"year":2019},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance","Supernatural"],"id":112061,"idMal":130610,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/112061","startDate":{"day":24,"month":3,"year":2018},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Kimi to Oishii Ai no Kotoba"],"title":{"english":"Love at First Bite","native":"君と美味しい愛のコトノハ","romaji":"Kimi to Oishii Ai no Kotonoha","userPreferred":"Kimi to Oishii Ai no Kotonoha"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45035","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx107949-gSud0ZNWB78e.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx107949-gSud0ZNWB78e.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx107949-gSud0ZNWB78e.png"},"description":"Makoto Kanekura works hard every day to pay off his father's debt. One day, the black-market lender Manami Godai hooks him up with a lucrative job. \"Every time you sleep with me, I'll slash $300 off your debt.\" Makoto steels himself for the worst, but it turns out he's not the bottom...! This is a money-driven romance about an innocent young man and a loan shark who loves to bottom!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Renta!)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cb\u003eIncluded one-shot:\u003c/b\u003e Magic Banana.","endDate":{"day":1,"month":8,"year":2017},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":107949,"idMal":111135,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/107949","startDate":{"day":1,"month":2,"year":2017},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Go Riyou wa Keikakuteki ni","Magic Banana","Gaste con moderación"],"title":{"english":"Spend Wisely","native":"ご利用は計画的に","romaji":"Goriyou wa Keikaku Teki ni","userPreferred":"Goriyou wa Keikaku Teki ni"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/31999-YOwPwyGrzm3v.jpg","chapters":21,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#fe9328","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx31999-gJbqrxefKX2l.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx31999-gJbqrxefKX2l.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx31999-gJbqrxefKX2l.png"},"description":"Sen Owari, a student from Japan, is studying at Columbia University. During his stay in the US, he has an affair with his professor... later to be discovered by her husband! Sen confronts him and, leading to a fight, shoots and kills him! Now convicted of murder, Sen is sentenced to serve 80 years in prison at \"Under Grand Hotel\" (UGH). The only imprisoned Asian boy in the institution, he's an outcast, vulnerable and alone. When he approaches Swordfish, a prison gang leader, to get protection, Swordfish seizes the opportunity and claims Sen as his \"personal property.\"\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: 801 Media)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":5,"year":2005},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":31999,"idMal":1999,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/31999","startDate":{"day":null,"month":12,"year":2000},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Under Grand Hotel Hi no Ataru Basho","Under Grand Hotel Toraware no Shirushi","Under Ground Hotel","アンダーグラウンドホテル","UGH"],"title":{"english":"Under Grand Hotel","native":"アンダーグラ〔×ウ〕ンドホテル","romaji":"Under (xGround) Grand Hotel","userPreferred":"Under (xGround) Grand Hotel"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":3},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/30801-yE0T6vjsoY1K.jpg","chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f17843","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx30801-GdS5Adc7Kvlv.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx30801-GdS5Adc7Kvlv.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx30801-GdS5Adc7Kvlv.jpg"},"description":"Chiaki Sakaguchi appears to be a sociable, popular high school senior, but he carries a dark secret with him that he can tell no one about \u0026ndash; not even his closest friends. When Chiaki meets fellow student Eiji Yukimura \u0026ndash; an under-achieving social misfit \u0026ndash; for the first time, he believes he\u0026rsquo;s found someone who can understand his inner pain. As the two become closer, Chiaki learns that Eiji has a secret also \u0026ndash; a secret so dark, it threatens to overshadow his own. United by common dysfunction and angst, Chiaki and Eiji begin to search for pleasure together beyond their pain. Will the pair\u0026rsquo;s growing bond enable them to break free of their troubled pasts and create a brighter future? Or is the damage that\u0026rsquo;s been done to both of them beyond any healing that love can provide?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Juné)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes an epilogue\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":10,"month":5,"year":2003},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Psychological","Romance"],"id":30801,"idMal":801,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/30801","startDate":{"day":7,"month":8,"year":2002},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["カット"],"title":{"english":"CUT","native":"CUT","romaji":"CUT","userPreferred":"CUT"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/144854-0Xgsz2yHQKXk.jpg","chapters":77,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1a178","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx144854-kdWgjGbmn9fk.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx144854-kdWgjGbmn9fk.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx144854-kdWgjGbmn9fk.jpg"},"description":"Do-Min is preparing for the bar exam but his sister’s friends just won’t leave him alone. One day, he falls in love with Seon-Hwa, a florist, and he decides to ask his sister’s friends for help. This will be one very thorough lesson!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u2028(Source: TOPTOON+, edited)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes seven extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":17,"month":7,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai","Romance"],"id":144854,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/144854","startDate":{"day":31,"month":1,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["お姉さんの友達","姊姊們的調教"],"title":{"english":"My Sister's Friends","native":"누나의 친구들","romaji":"Nunaui Chingudeul","userPreferred":"Nunaui Chingudeul"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45086","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx134997-JpVKjLZuDVgv.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx134997-JpVKjLZuDVgv.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx134997-JpVKjLZuDVgv.jpg"},"description":"Alex Lowe, a young but ruthless mafia boss falls in love at first sight with Shirai Kanata, a quiet student. However, Kanata is actually the skilled assassin known as \"Black Swan\" and his next target is Alex! Unlike his previous targets, Alex gives him genuine and sincere love and Kanata's heart is in turmoil... \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Julian Publishing)","endDate":{"day":30,"month":10,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Romance"],"id":134997,"idMal":137286,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/134997","startDate":{"day":27,"month":3,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["A Kiss on Double Face"],"title":{"english":"A Kiss for Each Face","native":"ダブルフェイスにくちづけ","romaji":"Double Face ni Kuchizuke","userPreferred":"Double Face ni Kuchizuke"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx133030-EmC4Wk0V3Y1e.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx133030-EmC4Wk0V3Y1e.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx133030-EmC4Wk0V3Y1e.jpg"},"description":"New Omega mother Tatsumi snaps at the yakuza Ryuuga and catches his interest. Cajoled and pampered... the start of a life as a yakuza's wife!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Chapter count includes one extra.\u003ci\u003e","endDate":{"day":1,"month":12,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":133030,"idMal":146456,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/133030","startDate":{"day":1,"month":4,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"子連れΩと暴君ヤクザ","romaji":"Kozure Omega to Boukun Yakuza","userPreferred":"Kozure Omega to Boukun Yakuza"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/127207-qzVqOb2H5y2Y.jpg","chapters":7,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d6b","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx127207-2F9ScND3q228.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx127207-2F9ScND3q228.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx127207-2F9ScND3q228.jpg"},"description":"At the spring season in college sophomore, Kotaro should be enjoying his youth, freedom and his campus life. But without a girlfriend or any close friends, his life has been rather unspectacular. One day, Miyako, Kotaro's female friend from his childhood asks him to pretend to be her boyfriend so that she can blow off a boy, Aoi who is making an unwanted move to her. Before Kotaro can make a decision, he accidentally meets Aoi and they happen to have teas together. It looks that Kotaro successes in making Aoi give up Miyako, but Aoi easily spots his lie and says \"Instead of giving up her, get along with me\". He takes Kotaro into the bathroom of the college, saying that he can teach many things....... A philanderer boy with a modest boy who wants to spend a quiet life....... A pure love story, stepping up awkwardly from a normal friendship.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Renta!)","endDate":{"day":24,"month":7,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy"],"id":127207,"idMal":131979,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":72,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/127207","startDate":{"day":24,"month":6,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Clumsy Love Step"],"title":{"english":"The Awkward Steps of Love","native":"ヘタクソラブステップ","romaji":"Hetakuso Love Step","userPreferred":"Hetakuso Love Step"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/203247-ixgTWkCIKI84.jpg","chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e49350","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b203247-dbpoo6XYv9U4.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b203247-dbpoo6XYv9U4.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b203247-dbpoo6XYv9U4.png"},"description":"To secure an alliance between the northern kingdom of Leracal and the southern realm of Arnata, the countries’ royal families agree to a political marriage. Tei, known across the frozen battlefields as the most fearsome warrior and monster hunter, volunteers himself as the kingdom’s hostage, trading his life as a warrior for that of a bride. In Arnata, Tei finds not the hostility he anticipated but the calm, steady gaze of Shuraka, the young crown prince destined to become both his spouse and future Padisha of the empire. For Shuraka to claim the throne, however, he must survive an uprising that threatens the kingdom - once that forces him to draw the blood of his own brothers. Moved by the courage and gentle integrity of his betrothed, Tei pledges to protect him at any cost…and in the quiet hours of a white night, two hearts caught between loyalty and longing begin to bloom.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Lezhin US)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Fantasy","Romance"],"id":203247,"idMal":189145,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":81,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/203247","startDate":{"day":1,"month":12,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["La ventura del caballero blanco","บุปผาใต้คืนตะวันฉาย","白夜的花路"],"title":{"english":"Blossoms of the White Night","native":"백야의 꽃길","romaji":"Baengnyaui Kkotgil","userPreferred":"Baengnyaui Kkotgil"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":67,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#4378e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx157250-xFjPoQkmkta0.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx157250-xFjPoQkmkta0.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx157250-xFjPoQkmkta0.png"},"description":"We’ve all had that nightmare where we’re late for a test, right? How about the one where your teacher’s trying to kill you?! Just me, huh? Guess it’s only fair then that I woke up in an actual zombie-infested nightmare! Almost everyone on my campus has become a creepy, flesh-eating monster! Except for this one ax-wielding badass named Youngwon Ki. He seems perfectly fine with all the chaos. I’m glad he’s here, but I don’t get why he acts like we’re close!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{"day":24,"month":1,"year":2025},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Mystery","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":157250,"idMal":185332,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/157250","startDate":{"day":10,"month":11,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["데드맨스위치","デッドマン・スイッチ","Deadman Switch：末日校園"],"title":{"english":"Dead Man's Switch","native":"데드맨 스위치","romaji":"DEAD MAN SWITCH","userPreferred":"DEAD MAN SWITCH"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/145344-x7J1z2hN4OTp.jpg","chapters":58,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1d6c9","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx145344-Zx9apqn7N1g5.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx145344-Zx9apqn7N1g5.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx145344-Zx9apqn7N1g5.png"},"description":"One frigid December dawn, Song Yeon-woo meets an injured runaway alpha; inexplicably drawn toward his woodsy scent, he is compelled to help the young man. Despite his aversion to alphas due to trauma in his past, Yeon-woo somehow feels safe and welcomed in his presence. The two part in the moonlight, never to see one another again...but fate has other plans. Two years later, Yeon-woo has finally returned to the city to begin anew—still wary of alphas around him, he has built barriers in nearly every aspect of his life to keep himself safe. But when that a familiar scent begins to pierce through his boundaries, Yeon-woo is unable to stop himself from following them in pursuit of something thrilling...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin US)","endDate":{"day":1,"month":10,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":145344,"idMal":184994,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/145344","startDate":{"day":29,"month":12,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["December","Diciembre"],"title":{"english":"December","native":"12월","romaji":"12 Wol","userPreferred":"12 Wol"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/143411-YC3EHfZu9VjC.jpg","chapters":7,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1e40d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx143411-GKnrm6zVOO8y.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx143411-GKnrm6zVOO8y.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx143411-GKnrm6zVOO8y.jpg"},"description":"A construction worker, Saeki is very interested in anything that has to do with sexual pleasure. When his coworker tells him about the red-light district where a man plays with his butt, he instantly denies the sexual hobby but cannot resist trying it later at his home. He tries to find the erogenous zone and happens to push a buttery deeper. He cannot take out the battery. So, he meets Dr. Kirishima, a handsome male gastroenterologist with long hair, for the treatment and dares to ask the whereabouts of his prostate. The doctor technically indicates the place. But the feelings are so good for Saeki that, to his surprise, he asks Kirishima, “Could you put your dick in...?”\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Takeshobo)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes 1 extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":30,"month":6,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":143411,"idMal":143345,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/143411","startDate":{"day":31,"month":8,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["คุณหมอครับ ช่วยตรวจผมที"],"title":{"english":"Give Me a Physical, Doc","native":"先生触診してくださいッ","romaji":"Sensei Shokushin Shite Kudasai","userPreferred":"Sensei Shokushin Shite Kudasai"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/127354-6fmrNgiZaOzx.jpg","chapters":130,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#5dbbe4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx127354-xg2OjyRTatoT.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx127354-xg2OjyRTatoT.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx127354-xg2OjyRTatoT.png"},"description":"College is a lot of fun. You meet hot girls, maybe go all the way. It's even more fun when you live at a friend's house, and his mom is smoking hot. But what will you do if you catch her masturbating? Is there a chance that...?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: TOPTOON+)","endDate":{"day":19,"month":2,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Hentai","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":127354,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":72,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/127354","startDate":{"day":27,"month":9,"year":2020},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["ハーレムライフ","寄宿日記"],"title":{"english":"Boarding Diary","native":"하숙일기","romaji":"Hasugilgi","userPreferred":"Hasugilgi"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45050","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx123900-REojuxcrjsut.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx123900-REojuxcrjsut.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx123900-REojuxcrjsut.png"},"description":"Minori has spent his life attracting demons, but he’s learned to live with their unwanted attention. That is, until the night he rescues what appears to be a sickly stray dog—only to discover it’s actually a demon in disguise. Stripped of his true name, the demon has been left powerless, a shadow of what he once was. To regain his strength, the demon binds Minori into an unholy pact—one that demands more than just blood. Their nights together should be nothing more than transactional, yet as the demon’s touch grows more possessive and Minori’s defenses begin to wane, something unspoken stirs between them.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes one extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":21,"month":12,"year":2019},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance","Supernatural"],"id":123900,"idMal":134789,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/123900","startDate":{"day":22,"month":4,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Demon Under the Waxing Moon","native":"待宵の鬼","romaji":"Matsuyoi no Oni","userPreferred":"Matsuyoi no Oni"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/116774-3NPvf9b3Vb4i.jpg","chapters":82,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1d6ae","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx116774-yCYyRI2chEC3.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx116774-yCYyRI2chEC3.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx116774-yCYyRI2chEC3.png"},"description":"Bae Woong was once a strong and fit athlete – at least in his mind. Eager to get back to his old physique, he goes looking for a gym in the neighborhood. He stumbles upon one that seems oddly expensive and discrete. He isn’t even allowed to hear about the specific workouts they provide until after he signs a nondisclosure agreement. He finds it strange, but the women working there are very attractive and Woong has nothing to lose. After signing the agreement, he learns the secret to their bodies: sex.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Lezhin US)","endDate":{"day":14,"month":2,"year":2022},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Hentai","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":116774,"idMal":125804,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":71,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/116774","startDate":{"day":16,"month":9,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["SEXERCICIO","セクササイズ〜世にもエッチな痩せ方〜"],"title":{"english":"Sexercise","native":"섹서사이즈","romaji":"Sexercise","userPreferred":"Sexercise"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":20,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b111315-DCsZwjpgBqr6.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b111315-DCsZwjpgBqr6.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b111315-DCsZwjpgBqr6.jpg"},"description":"Recent grad Wujin has no job, no purpose, no one in his life…till he meets Jin. Suave and sulking, Jin has a tough past but a soft exterior. Now, as next-door neighbors, Wujin can’t hide his feelings but…is Jin just toying with him? In that hot, wet, summer, will love reign?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Tapas)","endDate":{"day":26,"month":10,"year":2016},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Hentai","Psychological","Romance"],"id":111315,"idMal":163261,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/111315","startDate":{"day":22,"month":6,"year":2016},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Today Rain"],"title":{"english":"Rain Again","native":"오늘도 비가","romaji":"Oneuldo Biga","userPreferred":"Oneuldo Biga"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/100335-6K9ebsMMREj9.jpg","chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4a15d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/nx100335-fu9X22aOS0D8.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/nx100335-fu9X22aOS0D8.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/nx100335-fu9X22aOS0D8.png"},"description":"On the way home from work, Okazaki Taichi finds a man named Fuji, sleeping on a bench one day. Okazaki ends up bringing Fuji to his house, and somehow, he ends up on top of him, and they become friends with benefits. It's the start of an erotic BL between a heterosexual salaryman and a lewd bartender.\n","endDate":{"day":22,"month":3,"year":2017},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance"],"id":100335,"idMal":109547,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/100335","startDate":{"day":30,"month":11,"year":2016},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Will you set love aside?"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"恋だ愛だはさておいて","romaji":"Koi da Ai da wa Sateoite","userPreferred":"Koi da Ai da wa Sateoite"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/171804-xIqSmv31kfwh.jpg","chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1e4c9","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx171804-srkrruzEBnBd.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx171804-srkrruzEBnBd.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx171804-srkrruzEBnBd.jpg"},"description":"A life in the spotlight is a dream for many...but it's behind the scenes where the real drama takes place. Baek Yeong-Woon plays manager for Seo Hae-Yul, an up-and-coming actor at All One Pictures with a secret: his success is fueled by an industry \"sponsor\" who loves more than just his talent. So when a love affair between the young star and a mysterious figure threatens the livelihood of their company, it is up to Yeong-Woon to track his client down and put an end to their risky romp. But the truth may be too much for him to bear, as the other party turns out to be top model—and Yeong-Woon's first love—Han Seo-In. As Yeong-Woon struggles to reconcile his unresolved feelings for Seo-In with his sense of duty toward his work, the two fall into a intricate web woven of unanswered questions and lingering emotions that changes the trajectory of their lives forever...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Lezhin, edited)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":171804,"idMal":164685,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/171804","startDate":{"day":21,"month":11,"year":2023},"status":"HIATUS","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Backlight","native":"백라이트","romaji":"Backlight","userPreferred":"Backlight"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e41a86","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b156056-SrT8nm0IvAYb.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/b156056-SrT8nm0IvAYb.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/b156056-SrT8nm0IvAYb.png"},"description":"At a school filled with beastmen, two young pups have an awkward encounter that could lead to something more. Joseph, a young border collie, catches the shy and quiet bloodhound Noi sniffing his shirt one day in between classes. Rather than being put off, Joseph treats Noi with kindness and understanding, and even manages to get the timid bloodhound to open up. Turns out, Noi loves Joseph’s scent! With this new revelation, a bond grows between them and before they know it, the pups are obsessed with each other’s scent. Are they just messing around, fueled by raging hormones, or is there something more between Joseph and Noi?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)","endDate":{"day":30,"month":11,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":156056,"idMal":153730,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/156056","startDate":{"day":30,"month":9,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"SMELL","native":"SMELL","romaji":"SMELL","userPreferred":"SMELL"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/144245-JApHX4VifL2q.jpg","chapters":93,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#6b1a1a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx144245-8G4sagnqADGJ.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx144245-8G4sagnqADGJ.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx144245-8G4sagnqADGJ.jpg"},"description":"“I’ll repay that 450 thousand for you…but in exchange, you’re mine.”\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n \nDue to the debt left behind by his father, alpha Seo Taeyoon is at the mercy of Park Jae-in, a mob boss with a penchant for violence. But when Taeyoon is able to identify Jae-in as an omega by scent alone, the ruthless criminal is taken aback – because nobody should be able to smell his pheromones. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nSeeing this as his opportunity to regain what once was lost, Jae-in offers to pay off Taeyoon’s father’s loan in exchange for a life of servitude. Now Jae-in holds the key to both the physical and metaphorical locks around Taeyoon’s neck. And so begins their relationship as master and slave...but there's no telling how it will end.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Lezhin US)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes 25 extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":8,"month":11,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Fantasy","Romance"],"id":144245,"idMal":185210,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/144245","startDate":{"day":19,"month":1,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Minmotion Syndrome","ンモーション〜飼いならされた男〜","Dangereuse Essence","Erbsünde"],"title":{"english":"Minmotion Syndrome","native":"민모션","romaji":"Minmotion","userPreferred":"Minmotion"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":1,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d6936b","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx135516-YktKBFuBCMqK.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx135516-YktKBFuBCMqK.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx135516-YktKBFuBCMqK.jpg"},"description":"Akemi is bad at communicating. Our protagonist spends his free time in the library that she’s running. The distance between them seems wide, but one accidental pantyshot will lit a fire in both of them that will not subside until the fuck like animals.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: 2D market)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: A live-action AV adaptation (MIMK-163) was released on June 14th, 2024\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":30,"month":12,"year":2019},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":135516,"idMal":124347,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":75,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/135516","startDate":{"day":30,"month":12,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Addicted to Sex With a Taciturn Library Committee Member","native":"無口な図書委員とセックス漬け。","romaji":"Mukuchi na Tosho Iin to Sex Zuke.","userPreferred":"Mukuchi na Tosho Iin to Sex Zuke."},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/101175-lBSZPYyjtP6v.jpg","chapters":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e43578","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/nx101175-P2x32Sd0yiDx.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/nx101175-P2x32Sd0yiDx.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/nx101175-P2x32Sd0yiDx.jpg"},"description":"In a world where an endless variety of humanoid species coexist, there’s an equally endless variety of sexy shops for all your nightlife needs! Join Stunk, Zel, and Crim on their erotic adventures as they sample the many deviant delights that the world of succubus joints has to offer!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Yen Press)","endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Comedy","Ecchi","Fantasy"],"id":101175,"idMal":109408,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":71,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/101175","startDate":{"day":9,"month":7,"year":2016},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Międzygatunkowi recenzenci","이종족 리뷰어스"],"title":{"english":"Interspecies Reviewers","native":"異種族レビュアーズ","romaji":"Ishuzoku Reviewers","userPreferred":"Ishuzoku Reviewers"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":7,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1c95d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx95810-El8gp6DdLINn.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx95810-El8gp6DdLINn.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx95810-El8gp6DdLINn.jpg"},"description":"1-2. \u003cb\u003eNemuri Otoko to Koi Otoko\u003c/b\u003e (眠り男と恋男, A sleeping man and a loving man)\u003cbr\u003e\nJude and Royce have been long-term business partners and housemates. Things were going well for the platonic life partners, one of whom is openly gay while the other is straight; that is until a mysterious sleeping disease befalls Royce...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n3. \u003cb\u003eYasashii Dinner\u003c/b\u003e (優しいディナー, Sweet dinner)\u003cbr\u003e\nChef Kirino reconditions Aoi-kun, whose issues with food began during a previous relationship.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n4. \u003cb\u003eYoru wo Nigeru\u003c/b\u003e (夜を逃げる, Run from the night)\u003cbr\u003e\nAfraid of the dark and afraid of attachments, Haru has emotional scars from childhood trauma. When his relationship with Hugo starts to turn into something more than just sex, Haru is conflicted.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n5. \u003cb\u003eTaiyou to Himitsu\u003c/b\u003e (太陽と秘密, Sun and secrets)\u003cbr\u003e\nKaito has an intense affair with Cody one summer, and feels betrayed when Cody suddenly announces he's returning to his family. But now Cody is back, and wants to pick up where they left off.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n6. \u003cb\u003eMatsu Hana\u003c/b\u003e (待つ花, A waiting flower)\u003cbr\u003e\n\"A sacred place, a forbidden deed. Such a thing, though I understand that it is not allowed.\"\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n7. \u003cb\u003eNemuri Otoko to Koi Sonogo\u003c/b\u003e (眠り男と恋男ーその後, A sleeping man and a loving man -epilogue-)\nRoyce goes out of town on his own, forgetting something important.\n","endDate":{"day":10,"month":7,"year":2015},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":95810,"idMal":92256,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/95810","startDate":{"day":10,"month":7,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Yasashii Dinner","Sweet dinner","Yoru wo Nigeru","Run from the night","Escape from the night","Taiyou to Himitsu","Sun and secrets","Matsu Hana","A waiting flower","A Sleeping Man and a Loving Man","Zakochany we śnie"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"眠り男と恋男","romaji":"Nemuri Otoko to Koi Otoko","userPreferred":"Nemuri Otoko to Koi Otoko"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":1},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/30771-lFnLGkMWpdmI.jpg","chapters":50,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1c943","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx30771-IabJVdaQcpTv.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx30771-IabJVdaQcpTv.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx30771-IabJVdaQcpTv.jpg"},"description":"The curse of the magical crimson sword has turned Prince Vald into a monster... To break the spell, he sets out on a journey with the sexy and gorgeous magician, Havi. Vald has no idea that when he turns into a beast at night, Havi uses his unique talents to pacify his beastly appetite... The luscious journey of Vald and Havi begins.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n- Original magazine serialization is 75 chapters long, which were later collated for print release under 46 main story chapters and four extras\u003cbr\u003e\n- Volume 1 includes the extra \"Tabi no Tochuu (旅の途中)\"\u003cbr\u003e\n- Volume 3 includes the side-story \" Yousei no Mayu (妖精の繭 | The Fairy's Cocoon)\"\u003cbr\u003e\n- Volume 5 includes the side-story \"Tabi no Yado nite (旅の宿にて | At an Inn along the Road)\"\u003cbr\u003e\n- Volume 7 includes the side-story \"Kaijuu no Tabi no Owari no Saki ni (解呪の旅の終わりの先に | After Journey's End)\"\n","endDate":{"day":22,"month":1,"year":2021},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Adventure","Fantasy","Romance"],"id":30771,"idMal":771,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/30771","startDate":{"day":22,"month":5,"year":2004},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["The Crimson Spell","[비애] 크림슨 스펠"],"title":{"english":"Crimson Spell","native":"クリムゾン・スペル","romaji":"Crimson Spell","userPreferred":"Crimson Spell"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":7},{"bannerImage":null,"chapters":100,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d78","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx145498-Y067Ag2otsJk.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx145498-Y067Ag2otsJk.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx145498-Y067Ag2otsJk.jpg"},"description":"\u003ci\u003e\"Why did I turn into a character from an adult game?\"\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e \nThe time has come now to take action! Lucius the loser character has transformed into a villain overnight. With his new found vengeance, Lucius will set out to enjoy the action packed, harem fantasy adventure!!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: TOPTOON+)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes four extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":22,"month":2,"year":2024},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Drama","Fantasy","Hentai","Romance"],"id":145498,"idMal":null,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":72,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/145498","startDate":{"day":3,"month":2,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["The Main Character Is The Villain","目覚めた先は、エロゲ悪役！？"],"title":{"english":"I AM THE VILLAIN","native":"주인공이 빌런임","romaji":"Juingongi Villain-im","userPreferred":"Juingongi Villain-im"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":null},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/130308-aV75NpRLmrlx.jpg","chapters":49,"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#f1505d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx130308-1WjKupAukCTz.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx130308-1WjKupAukCTz.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx130308-1WjKupAukCTz.jpg"},"description":"When high school teacher Na Aejoon shows up for work on an ordinary day, he never expects to bump into his favorite celebrity in the hallway. But when his school becomes a filming location for a show starring Choi Siyeol, his bias from the idol group A-One, that’s exactly what happens! \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nIf that’s not enough to give a fanboy a heart attack, Siyeol takes an interest in Aejoon and asks him to join the show as his “co-teacher.” Desperate to keep his fan life a secret, Aejoon is forced to put his acting skills to the test, and not just on camera. But as he spends more and more time with Siyeol, the deception becomes harder to keep up. Not to mention, he might not be the only one keeping secrets…\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Tappytoon)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes nine extra chapters.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":23,"month":12,"year":2023},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Romance"],"id":130308,"idMal":191327,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":73,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/130308","startDate":{"day":24,"month":2,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["My Bias Appeared?!","我的偶像倒追我"],"title":{"english":"My Bias Is Showing?!","native":"최애가 나타났다?!","romaji":"Choeaega Natanassda?!","userPreferred":"Choeaega Natanassda?!"},"type":"MANGA","volumes":3},{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/banner/129674-mmGKVCWxA0Rm.jpg","chapters":6,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d6281a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/large/bx129674-ktuAsbca4otX.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/medium/bx129674-ktuAsbca4otX.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/manga/cover/small/bx129674-ktuAsbca4otX.jpg"},"description":"In a world where demi-beasts and humans co-exist, Riku Kurobuchi, a panther demi-beast, finds himself facing a dilemma.\nHe is sociable, good looking, talented at sports, and popular with girls, but for some reason he still hasn't experienced his \"heat\" like everyone else. After an unexpected transfer, he begins sharing his dorm room with the mature and handsome albino lion demi-beast, Touma Shishigaya. Riku wants to keep his secret hidden from the confrontational Touma, but it's Touma's pheromones that bring about Riku's first heat!!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThis is a story of desire between a beautiful albino and an inexperienced demi-beast.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Renta!)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: Includes an extra chapter.\u003c/i\u003e","endDate":{"day":17,"month":7,"year":2020},"format":"MANGA","genres":["Drama","Romance"],"id":129674,"idMal":135418,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/manga/129674","startDate":{"day":10,"month":11,"year":2019},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Playboy Beast","native":"プレイボーイ・ビースト","romaji":"Playboy Beast","userPrefe