He enjoys a life of peace, free of enemy threats and surrounded by precious friends, new and old. But ominous shadows grow near yet again. Enemies that enter into the fissures of the mind. And Fushi learns of the true goals of his creator, the Beholder.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nFaced with new trials, the time approaches for Fushi to make the ultimate decision.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: NHK PR, edited)","duration":25,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":22,"format":"TV","genres":["Adventure","Drama","Fantasy","Psychological","Supernatural"],"id":162669,"idMal":54703,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":76,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774104300,"episode":20,"timeUntilAiring":556726},"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/162669","startDate":{"day":4,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"To Your Eternity Season 3","native":"不滅のあなたへ Season 3","romaji":"Fumetsu no Anata e Season 3","userPreferred":"Fumetsu no Anata e Season 3"},"trailer":{"id":"JmT51BjIJ5w","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/JmT51BjIJ5w/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-48074},{"airingAt":1773498600,"episode":11,"id":406886,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/166617-P4w3p0H4lE1O.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#1a1af1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx166617-34fpC9y47tTx.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx166617-34fpC9y47tTx.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx166617-34fpC9y47tTx.png"},"description":"In a Holy Grail War, Mages (Masters) and their Heroic Spirits (Servants) fight for the control of the Holy Grail—an omnipotent wish-granting device said to fulfill any desire. Years have passed since the end of the Fifth Holy Grail War in Japan. Now, signs portend the emergence of a new Holy Grail in the western American city of Snowfield. Sure enough, Masters and Servants begin to gather... \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nA missing Servant class...\u003cbr\u003e\nImpossible Servant summonings...\u003cbr\u003e\nA nation shrouded in secrecy...\u003cbr\u003e\nAnd a city created as a battleground.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nIn the face of such irregularities, the Holy Grail War is twisted and driven into the depth of madness. Let the curtain rise on a masquerade of humans and heroes, made to dance upon the stage of a false Holy Grail. \u003ci\u003eThis is a Holy Grail War covered in lies.\u003c/i\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Official Site, Aniplex USA, edited)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n•  \u003ci\u003eSpecial premiere of Episode 1 in its English Dub occurred in Los Angeles at the Fate 20th Anniversary Showcase event and as well through Crunchyroll’s YouTube Channel on November 23, 2024 before the Japanese television premiere.\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n•  \u003ci\u003eThe Japanese advanced premiere occurred during the \"Fate New Year's Eve TV Special 2024\" on December 31, 2024.\u003c/i\u003e","duration":25,"endDate":{"day":28,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":13,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy","Mystery","Supernatural"],"id":166617,"idMal":55830,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":83,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774103400,"episode":12,"timeUntilAiring":555826},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/166617","startDate":{"day":3,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Судьба/Странная подделка"],"title":{"english":"Fate/strange Fake","native":"Fate/strange Fake","romaji":"Fate/strange Fake","userPreferred":"Fate/strange Fake"},"trailer":{"id":"k1G8EvZg_BY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/k1G8EvZg_BY/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-48974},{"airingAt":1773498600,"episode":10,"id":405106,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/187901-03I5T8QVX1FG.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#35bbf1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx187901-T91HmZAaNwOF.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx187901-T91HmZAaNwOF.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx187901-T91HmZAaNwOF.jpg"},"description":"Always ready for a fight! Destruction for destruction’s sake! The online streamer Aoringo is a troll, making the worst of the worst of boundary-pushing flamebait content and raking in the revenue from the hate-watchers. You may think he’s nothing more than a bottom feeder and a drain on society, but in reality, he’s high school dropout Souji Enishiro, a caring older brother with a sweet tooth who loves nothing more than his little sister. His viral videos? Just a way to pay his sister’s medical bills. And even if all of humanity hates him, he doesn’t care, so long as his little sister gets better. But then, something very strange begins to happen...\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":28,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Supernatural"],"id":187901,"idMal":61196,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":62,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774103400,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":555826},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/187901","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["デドアカ","เดดแอ็กเคานต์ พิฆาตบัญชีมรณะ"],"title":{"english":"Dead Account","native":"デッドアカウント","romaji":"Dead Account","userPreferred":"Dead Account"},"trailer":{"id":"ynnk0CIyu10","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ynnk0CIyu10/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-48974},{"airingAt":1773496800,"episode":10,"id":404750,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/163144-e6vGlARSvwyE.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx163144-XdVwFRxPGY6j.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx163144-XdVwFRxPGY6j.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx163144-XdVwFRxPGY6j.jpg"},"description":"Sequel season to \u003ci\u003eTRIGUN STAMPEDE\u003c/i\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nIt’s been two and a half years since the Lost JuLai tragedy, which laid waste to an entire city and engulfed the whole planet in chaos. Meryl, now a senior journalist, continues her search for Vash with her new younger sidekick, Milly, and runs into Wolfwood along the way. As plant robberies begin taking place once again, they sense Millions Knives’s organization conspiring behind the scenes.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nMeanwhile, Vash has taken the new name Eriks and is living in hiding in a backwater town when he gets an abrupt visit from Jessica, a young girl with an SOS from the third ship they call home. He thus decides to put an end to a long-standing feud in order to protect those dear to him.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nJust as the pieces of the story begin falling back together again, the planet receives a message from the far reaches of outer space: “We are a fleet of colony ships from Earth... Those who wish may accompany us to a new frontier.” The entire population rejoices at this news. However, as if to mock their celebration, the one-winged angel returns to wreak havoc and despair. Fates collide to forge a final conclusion for the panicked planet.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":28,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Comedy","Drama","Sci-Fi"],"id":163144,"idMal":54863,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":71,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774101600,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":554026},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/163144","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["トライガン スタンピード 完結編","TRIGUN STAMPEDE: Kanketsu-hen","トライガン スターゲイズ"],"title":{"english":"TRIGUN STARGAZE","native":"TRIGUN STARGAZE","romaji":"TRIGUN STARGAZE","userPreferred":"TRIGUN STARGAZE"},"trailer":{"id":"JBYLkW--zmI","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/JBYLkW--zmI/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-50774},{"airingAt":1773493200,"episode":11,"id":405075,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#4393c9","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx199446-2jYnGrTItjyu.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx199446-2jYnGrTItjyu.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx199446-2jYnGrTItjyu.jpg"},"description":"The story of Saioshi no Gikei Mederutame, Nagaikishimasu! follows the struggle of a player to protect his favorite character, who gets reincarnated as his older brother-in-law in a simulation raising game - however, the player is reincarnated as the younger brother who was meant to die.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: ANN)","duration":4,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV_SHORT","genres":["Fantasy","Romance"],"id":199446,"idMal":61969,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":51,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774098000,"episode":12,"timeUntilAiring":550426},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/199446","startDate":{"day":3,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["I’ll Live A Long Life to Adore My Absolute Fave—Currently My Stepbrother"],"title":{"english":"I'll Live a Long Life to Dote on My Favorite Stepbrother!","native":"最推しの義兄を愛でるため、長生きします！","romaji":"Saioshi no Gikei Mederu Tame, Nagaikishimasu!","userPreferred":"Saioshi no Gikei Mederu Tame, Nagaikishimasu!"},"trailer":{"id":"kH6Yrpboous","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/kH6Yrpboous/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-54374},{"airingAt":1773491400,"episode":10,"id":406966,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4505d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx202419-BmPPSzsegbcv.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx202419-BmPPSzsegbcv.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx202419-BmPPSzsegbcv.png"},"description":"Light anime for \u003ci\u003eOmae wa Mada Gunma wo Shiranai\u003c/i\u003e.","duration":6,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV_SHORT","genres":["Comedy"],"id":202419,"idMal":62864,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":46,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774096200,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":548626},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/202419","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["You Don't Know Gunma Yet"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"お前はまだグンマを知らない～令和版～ ","romaji":"Omae wa Mada Gunma wo Shiranai: Reiwa-ban","userPreferred":"Omae wa Mada Gunma wo Shiranai: Reiwa-ban"},"trailer":{"id":"O5_4AGv44sU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/O5_4AGv44sU/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-56174},{"airingAt":1773491400,"episode":10,"id":405275,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/187941-wdkhGnf4LUH0.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1930d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx187941-ykmc8WRedPpw.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx187941-ykmc8WRedPpw.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx187941-ykmc8WRedPpw.jpg"},"description":"Our hero needs to come out of his shell... literally! Reborn in another world inside a dragon egg, he doesn’t have the amazing magic or mighty physical strength of your typical isekai’d adventurer just yet. He’ll need to break free and grow from a weak hatchling and into a fearsome beast if he wants to escape the deep, dark forest unscathed. What battles and adventures await him in this unique take on the isekai phenomenon?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: HIDIVE)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":187941,"idMal":61207,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":63,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774096200,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":548626},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/187941","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["DoraTama"],"title":{"english":"Reincarnated as a Dragon Hatchling","native":"転生したらドラゴンの卵だった","romaji":"Tensei Shitara Dragon no Tamago Datta","userPreferred":"Tensei Shitara Dragon no Tamago Datta"},"trailer":{"id":"VPLmZd3ByAM","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/VPLmZd3ByAM/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-56174},{"airingAt":1773480300,"episode":19,"id":404837,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx186736-zYDrRDuC55s5.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx186736-zYDrRDuC55s5.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx186736-zYDrRDuC55s5.png"},"description":"The second season of \u003ci\u003eKagaku×Bouken Survival!\u003c/i\u003e","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":[],"id":186736,"idMal":60983,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":44,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774085100,"episode":20,"timeUntilAiring":537526},"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/186736","startDate":{"day":4,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"科学×冒険サバイバル！ 第2シリーズ","romaji":"Kagaku×Bouken Survival! 2nd Season","userPreferred":"Kagaku×Bouken Survival! 2nd Season"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-67274},{"airingAt":1773478800,"episode":1193,"id":409738,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/235-MTmiz0uB0fMd.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#28a1e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx235-MyYT7K3chBdO.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx235-MyYT7K3chBdO.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx235-MyYT7K3chBdO.jpg"},"description":"Kudo Shinichi is a seventeen year-old high school detective whom people call the \"Modern Sherlock Holmes.\" However, one night after a date with his childhood sweetheart, Ran, Shinichi witnessed an illegal trade and, caught off his guard, was knocked unconscious and fed a drug that was supposed to kill him... but he woke up and found himself shrunken to a seven year-old. In order to track down the men who did this to him, Shinichi hid his identity and lived with Ran, whose father happened to be a hopeless detective, and with that came a series of murders and mysteries that he must solve. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote:\u003cbr\u003e\n- Includes Keisatsu Gakkou-hen - Wild Police Story in episodes 1029, 1038, 1042, 1061\u003cbr\u003e\n- Episodes 11, 52, 76, 118, 162, 184, 208, 342, 356, 449, 452, 487, 488, 489, 490, 515, 516, 521, 522, 651, 734, 804, 805, 927, 928, 1187 aired with a runtime of ~50 minutes as opposed to the standard 25 minute long episode.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Episodes 96, 129, 174, 219, 263, 304, 383, 479 aired with a runtime of ~90 minutes as opposed to the standard 25 minute 