lt":false,"meanScore":83,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774110600,"episode":9,"timeUntilAiring":562800},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/189275","startDate":{"day":25,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Medalist Season 2","native":"メダリスト 第2期","romaji":"Medalist 2nd Season","userPreferred":"Medalist 2nd Season"},"trailer":{"id":"GTaqXo7scOY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/GTaqXo7scOY/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-42000},{"airingAt":1773503760,"episode":10,"id":404726,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/187989-ELfQpRahhT3L.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d6a178","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx187989-IjVYJxi0bEcr.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx187989-IjVYJxi0bEcr.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx187989-IjVYJxi0bEcr.jpg"},"description":"In the mid-21st century, Tokyo's mafia can turn into ether-enhanced Demon Lords, and Braves hunt them down. Yashiro, the Grim Reaper, reluctantly takes a new apprentice named Aki Jogamine, a high school girl training to become a Brave. He soon finds himself dragged into one troublesome case after another. The supernatural story of a scumbag master and his self-proclaimed apprentice begins!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":23,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":24,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Comedy","Drama","Fantasy","Sci-Fi"],"id":187989,"idMal":61217,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":63,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774108560,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":560760},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/187989","startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["ผู้กล้าสวะ","Pahlawan Sampah"],"title":{"english":"Scum of the Brave","native":"勇者のクズ","romaji":"Yuusha no Kuzu","userPreferred":"Yuusha no Kuzu"},"trailer":{"id":"Lh-0y-O7GIg","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Lh-0y-O7GIg/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-44040},{"airingAt":1773502200,"episode":23,"id":405660,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/187464-JRW0ASx02H83.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx187464-NJtK3VC54vPm.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx187464-NJtK3VC54vPm.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx187464-NJtK3VC54vPm.jpg"},"description":"Tanzaburo Tojima has dreamt of becoming a Kamen Rider his whole life. But now that he’s 40 years old, he’s starting to think his dream may never come true…until he’s swept up in a series of crimes inspired by the infamous “Shocker”! From Air Master and 81 Diver’s Shibata Yokusaru comes a wild, heartfelt tale about adults who love Kamen Rider a little too much and start playing pretend—for real!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":24,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Comedy"],"id":187464,"idMal":61159,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":74,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774107000,"episode":24,"timeUntilAiring":559200},"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/187464","startDate":{"day":5,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Tojima Tanzaburo Wants To Be A Masked Rider","โทจิมะอยากเป็นคาเมนไรเดอร์","토지마 탄자부로는 가면라이더가 되고 싶어"],"title":{"english":"Tojima Wants to Be a Kamen Rider","native":"東島丹三郎は仮面ライダーになりたい","romaji":"Toujima Tanzaburou wa Kamen Rider ni Naritai","userPreferred":"Toujima Tanzaburou wa Kamen Rider ni Naritai"},"trailer":{"id":"76c3cCV1BcU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/76c3cCV1BcU/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-45600},{"airingAt":1773500400,"episode":21,"id":409965,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/185116-eQ55D57Wj1oJ.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#43aee4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx185116-DIFRjiMgz1IS.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx185116-DIFRjiMgz1IS.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx185116-DIFRjiMgz1IS.jpg"},"description":"The story of \u003ci\u003eGNOSIA\u003c/i\u003e takes place on a ship drifting through space. Gnosia is an enemy that disguises itself as a human and attacks them. It is now on the spaceship, causing everyone onboard to be suspicious of each other. The crew decides to vote on the most suspicious-looking person every day and put them into a cold sleep.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nIf the humans succeed in putting Gnosia to sleep, they'll win. On the other hand, if they don't, everyone on board is in danger. The right decision must be made. No matter what decision is made by the main character, Yuri, she finds herself in a time loop that returns her to the first day of the crisis. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nWill the crew on board make the right decision? What is the secret behind the time loop? What secrets hide behind the faces of everyone on board?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003ci\u003eGNOSIA\u003c/i\u003e begins now – a story of looping, fleeting moments that feels like an eternity but passes by in an instant.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nHave a pleasant journey.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":25,"endDate":{"day":15,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":21,"format":"TV","genres":["Drama","Mystery","Sci-Fi","Thriller"],"id":185116,"idMal":60427,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":76,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/185116","startDate":{"day":12,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"GNOSIA","native":"グノーシア","romaji":"Gnosia","userPreferred":"Gnosia"},"trailer":{"id":"Rm4ipMdFpeA","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Rm4ipMdFpeA/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-47400},{"airingAt":1773500400,"episode":10,"id":406138,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/198374-cnzGgIW2KzHr.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#4386ff","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx198374-ROZU3qJGX4uS.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx198374-ROZU3qJGX4uS.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx198374-ROZU3qJGX4uS.jpg"},"description":"After a traumatic incident ends his teaching career, Rei Hitoma is certain he hates humans. Yet when he sees a job for “a teacher who truly cares for their students,” he’s compelled to apply. Before he knows it, he’s hired—only to find out his students are demi-humans. What begins as a job becomes a journey for healing for both a teacher who’s lost faith in humanity and students who dream of it.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":5,"month":4,"year":2026},"episodes":13,"format":"TV","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Fantasy","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":198374,"idMal":62432,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":61,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774105200,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":557400},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/198374","startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["ห้องเรียนต่างสายพันธุ์ ของอาจารย์ผู้เกลียดมนุษย์"],"title":{"english":"A Misanthrope Teaches a Class for Demi-Humans","native":"人外教室の人間嫌い教師","romaji":"Jingai Kyoushitsu no Ningengirai Kyoushi","userPreferred":"Jingai Kyoushitsu no Ningengirai Kyoushi"},"trailer":{"