:{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/179062-ZnxW4uWEsV3H.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#febb28","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx179062-pbzYE1miZq61.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx179062-pbzYE1miZq61.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx179062-pbzYE1miZq61.png"},"description":"The second cour of \u003ci\u003eEnen no Shouboutai: San no Shou\u003c/i\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e \n\nAs chaos spreads, Shinra and Company 8 fight to stop a final, world-ending blaze.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e \n\n(Source: Crunchyroll News)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":13,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Drama","Sci-Fi","Supernatural"],"id":179062,"idMal":59229,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":80,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774025580,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":477780},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/179062","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Enen no Shouboutai 3rd Season Part 2","หน่วยผจญคนไฟลุก ภาค 3"],"title":{"english":"Fire Force Season 3 Part 2","native":"炎炎ノ消防隊 参ノ章 第2クール","romaji":"Enen no Shouboutai: San no Shou Part 2","userPreferred":"Enen no Shouboutai: San no Shou Part 2"},"trailer":{"id":"voLZJvdwUEE","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/voLZJvdwUEE/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-127020},{"airingAt":1773419700,"episode":10,"id":405090,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/185262-6EExIkvGk1dI.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#bbe450","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx185262-95wbx3Y9hCwm.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx185262-95wbx3Y9hCwm.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx185262-95wbx3Y9hCwm.jpg"},"description":"Thirty-five-year-old Kenichi Yamada has spent his life playing every single MMORPG he can get his hands on. Tired of new games that cater to casual players, he leaps at the chance to try out a never-ending game with an intimidating “Hell Mode” that raises the difficulty (and chances to level up) to impossible heights. But, as soon as he selects the “Summoner,” Kenichi finds himself transported into the world of the game and reborn to a family of serfs as a baby named Allen! With nothing but his memories and wits to guide him, Allen sets off to conquer Hell Mode, unearth the secrets of the Summoner class, and free his newfound family from their fate.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: HIDIVE)","duration":23,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":185262,"idMal":60460,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":67,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774024500,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":476700},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/185262","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["HELL MODE อยากเล่นโหด ขอโหมดนรก"],"title":{"english":"HELL MODE: The Hardcore Gamer Dominates in Another World with Garbage Balancing","native":"ヘルモード ～やり込み好きのゲーマーは廃設定の異世界で無双する～","romaji":"Hell Mode: Yarikomi Suki no Gamer wa Haisettei no Isekai de Musou Suru","userPreferred":"Hell Mode: Yarikomi Suki no Gamer wa Haisettei no Isekai de Musou Suru"},"trailer":{"id":"CjO1Bo297N4","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/CjO1Bo297N4/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-128100},{"airingAt":1773414000,"episode":10,"id":403980,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/181443-Euz60QKDzsLs.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d6281a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx181443-Df41Nlf7x