thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/3wNyyhzLqA0/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-21204},{"airingAt":1773579600,"episode":12,"id":408494,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/186333-JN8lx2aNOTg1.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#5da1e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx186333-32qDHxLkndpg.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx186333-32qDHxLkndpg.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx186333-32qDHxLkndpg.png"},"description":"Kunon, a young man who cannot see, has the goal of creating new eyes with water magic. After just five months of learning sorcery, Kunon surpassed his own mentor and honed his talent as he tried to do a feat that's never been done before. A fantasy about a young man, a blind genius, who opens up the world through curiosity in the pursuit for magic is about to begin.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":22,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":13,"format":"ONA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":186333,"idMal":60810,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":64,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774184400,"episode":13,"timeUntilAiring":579996},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/186333","startDate":{"day":4,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["จอมเวทผู้มองเห็นทุกสิ่ง คุนอน"],"title":{"english":"Kunon the Sorcerer Can See","native":"魔術師クノンは見えている","romaji":"Majutsushi Kunon wa Mieteiru","userPreferred":"Majutsushi Kunon wa Mieteiru"},"trailer":{"id":"8AdpUgiFs2o","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/8AdpUgiFs2o/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-24804},{"airingAt":1773577800,"episode":12,"id":406734,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#fff193","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx177580-ujQw6Ws3oVCi.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx177580-ujQw6Ws3oVCi.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx177580-ujQw6Ws3oVCi.jpg"},"description":"Mizuki Ashiya is on a mission: disguise herself as a boy and enroll in a male boarding school to meet her idol, high jump star Izumi Sano. But after successfully infiltrating the school, she discovers he’s suddenly quit the sport! Now Mizuki must dodge suspicion, protect her cover, and somehow reach the boy she came all this way for—all while surviving the chaos of an all-boys dorm!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":12,"format":"ONA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":177580,"idMal":58861,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":67,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/177580","startDate":{"day":4,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Hana-Kimi: For You in Full Blossom","สับขั้วมาลุ้นรัก"],"title":{"english":"Hana-Kimi","native":"花ざかりの君たちへ","romaji":"Hanazakari no Kimitachi e","userPreferred":"Hanazakari no Kimitachi e"},"trailer":{"id":"CemNP0vIiJI","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/CemNP0vIiJI/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-26604},{"airingAt":1773567000,"episode":2823,"id":394963,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/2406-ROqXxejQ5bH9.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1bb43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx2406-nP8NIct9Sci3.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx2406-nP8NIct9Sci3.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx2406-nP8NIct9Sci3.jpg"},"description":"The main character is a mother named Sazae-san. She lives in a house with her husband, her kid, her siblings and her parents. The show is the ultimate family program and tends to follow traditional themes. Think of this show as the Japanese equivalent to \"The Partridge Family\" and you'll get a good feel for this show's atmosphere. Don't expect to see things like violence, swearing, kung-fu action or magical girls. The plots are more like \"Today, Sazae-san goes to the new mall and gets lost\". Such \"boring\" plotlines and the simplistic art are often a turn-off to non-Japanese audiences, but most Japanese find the show incredibly good. As a result, it continues to be one of the top ratings grabbers on TV and is one of the few anime that is considered \"acceptable\" by adults.","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Comedy","Slice of Life"],"id":2406,"idMal":2406,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":58,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774171800,"episode":2824,"timeUntilAiring":567396},"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/2406","startDate":{"day":5,"month":10,"year":1969},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Mrs. Sazae"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"サザエさん","romaji":"Sazae-san","userPreferred":"Sazae-san"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-37404},{"airingAt":1773565200,"episode":357,"id":408745,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/118123-BvHyzWd850nZ.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx118123-xqn5fYsjKXJU.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx118123-xqn5fYsjKXJU.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx118123-xqn5fYsjKXJU.png"},"description":"From unraveling the secrets of opening and closing doors to defusing surprise packages more commonly known as bombs, there is never a dull day at the Hololive Production office! \u003ci\u003eHolo 