:63,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774108560,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":504156},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/187989","startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["ผู้กล้าสวะ","Pahlawan Sampah"],"title":{"english":"Scum of the Brave","native":"勇者のクズ","romaji":"Yuusha no Kuzu","userPreferred":"Yuusha no Kuzu"},"trailer":{"id":"Lh-0y-O7GIg","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Lh-0y-O7GIg/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-100644},{"airingAt":1773502200,"episode":23,"id":405660,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/187464-JRW0ASx02H83.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx187464-NJtK3VC54vPm.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx187464-NJtK3VC54vPm.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx187464-NJtK3VC54vPm.jpg"},"description":"Tanzaburo Tojima has dreamt of becoming a Kamen Rider his whole life. But now that he’s 40 years old, he’s starting to think his dream may never come true…until he’s swept up in a series of crimes inspired by the infamous “Shocker”! From Air Master and 81 Diver’s Shibata Yokusaru comes a wild, heartfelt tale about adults who love Kamen Rider a little too much and start playing pretend—for real!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":24,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Comedy"],"id":187464,"idMal":61159,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":74,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774107000,"episode":24,"timeUntilAiring":502596},"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/187464","startDate":{"day":5,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Tojima Tanzaburo Wants To Be A Masked Rider","โทจิมะอยากเป็นคาเมนไรเดอร์","토지마 탄자부로는 가면라이더가 되고 싶어"],"title":{"english":"Tojima Wants to Be a Kamen Rider","native":"東島丹三郎は仮面ライダーになりたい","romaji":"Toujima Tanzaburou wa Kamen Rider ni Naritai","userPreferred":"Toujima Tanzaburou wa Kamen Rider ni Naritai"},"trailer":{"id":"76c3cCV1BcU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/76c3cCV1BcU/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-102204},{"airingAt":1773500400,"episode":21,"id":409965,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/185116-eQ55D57Wj1oJ.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#43aee4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx185116-DIFRjiMgz1IS.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx185116-DIFRjiMgz1IS.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx185116-DIFRjiMgz1IS.jpg"},"description":"The story of \u003ci\u003eGNOSIA\u003c/i\u003e takes place on a ship drifting through space. Gnosia is an enemy that disguises itself as a human and attacks them. It is now on the spaceship, causing everyone onboard to be suspicious of each other. The crew decides to vote on the most suspicious-looking person every day and put them into a cold sleep.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nIf the humans succeed in putting Gnosia to sleep, they'll win. On the other hand, if they don't, everyone on board is in danger. The right decision must be made. No matter what decision is made by the main character, Yuri, she finds herself in a time loop that returns her to the first day of the crisis. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nWill the crew on board make the right decision? What is the secret behind the time loop? What secrets hide behind the faces of everyone on board?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003ci\u003eGNOSIA\u003c/i\u003e begins now – a story of looping, fleeting moments that feels like an eternity but passes by in an instant.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nHave a pleasant journey.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":25,"endDate":{"day":15,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":21,"format":"TV","genres":["Drama","Mystery","Sci-Fi","Thriller"],"id":185116,"idMal":60427,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":77,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/185116","startDate":{"day":12,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"GNOSIA","native":"グノーシア","romaji":"Gnosia","userPreferred":"Gnosia"},"trailer":{"id":"Rm4ipMdFpeA","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Rm4ipMdFpeA/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-104004},{"airingAt":1773500400,"episode":10,"id":406138,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/198374-cnzGgIW2KzHr.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#4386ff","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx198374-ROZU3qJGX4uS.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx198374-ROZU3qJGX4uS.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx198374-ROZU3qJGX4uS.jpg"},"description":"After a traumatic incident ends his teaching career, Rei Hitoma is certain he hates humans. Yet when he sees a job for “a teacher who truly cares for their students,” he’s compelled to apply. Before he knows it, he’s hired—only to find out his students are demi-humans. What begins as a job becomes a journey for healing for both a teacher who’s lost faith in humanity and students who dream of it.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":5,"month":4,"year":2026},"episodes":13,"format":"TV","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Fantasy","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":198374,"idMal":62432,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":61,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774105200,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":500796},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/198374","startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["ห้องเรียนต่างสายพันธุ์ ของอาจารย์ผู้เกลียดมนุษย์"],"title":{"english":"A Misanthrope Teaches a Class for Demi-Humans","native":"人外教室の人間嫌い教師","romaji":"Jingai Kyoushitsu no Ningengirai Kyoushi","userPreferred":"Jingai Kyoushitsu no Ningengirai Kyoushi"},"trailer":{"id":"rb0okw_1ExM","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/rb0okw_1ExM/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-104004},{"airingAt":1773500400,"episode":22,"id":405385,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"CN","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx203953-0o0WnauWOeQO.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx203953-0o0WnauWOeQO.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx203953-0o0WnauWOeQO.jpg"},"description":"The third part of \u003ci\u003eMu Shen Ji\u003c/i\u003e.","duration":20,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":26,"format":"ONA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":203953,"idMal":null,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":86,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774105200,"episode":23,"timeUntilAiring":500796},"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/203953","startDate":{"day":19,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Tales of Herding Gods 3","牧神记 叁"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"牧神记3","romaji":"Mu Shen Ji 3","userPreferred":"Mu Shen Ji 3"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-104004},{"airingAt":1773499500,"episode":19,"id":408856,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/162669-SvOE44IccAT0.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1a150","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx162669-FLYUTftoXgMh.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx162669-FLYUTftoXgMh.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx162669-FLYUTftoXgMh.jpg"},"description":"\u003cb\u003eThe story of Fushi the immortal enters the modern era.\u003c/b\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nFollowing the battles in Renril, Fushi, like a tree, spreads his roots throughout the world, fighting to eliminate the Nokkers. Hundreds of years later, having completed his mission, he awakens in the modern era. He enjoys a life of peace, free of enemy threats and surrounded by precious friends, new and old. But ominous shadows grow near yet again. Enemies that enter into the fissures of the mind. And Fushi learns of the true goals of his creator, the Beholder.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nFaced with new trials, the time approaches for Fushi to make the ultimate decision.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: NHK PR, edited)","duration":25,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":22,"format":"TV","genres":["Adventure","Drama","Fantasy","Psychological","Supernatural"],"id":162669,"idMal":54703,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":76,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774104300,"episode":20,"timeUntilAiring":499896},"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/162669","startDate":{"day":4,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"To Your Eternity Season 3","native":"不滅のあなたへ Season 3","romaji":"Fumetsu no Anata e Season 3","userPreferred":"Fumetsu no Anata e Season 3"},"trailer":{"id":"JmT51BjIJ5w","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/JmT51BjIJ5w/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-104904},{"airingAt":1773498600,"episode":11,"id":406886,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/166617-P4w3p0H4lE1O.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#1a1af1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx166617-34fpC9y47tTx.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx166617-34fpC9y47tTx.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx166617-34fpC9y47tTx.png"},"description":"In a Holy Grail War, Mages (Masters) and their Heroic Spirits (Servants) fight for the control of the Holy Grail—an omnipotent wish-granting device said to fulfill any desire. Years have passed since the end of the Fifth Holy Grail War in Japan. Now, signs portend the emergence of a new Holy Grail in the western American city of Snowfield. Sure enough, Masters and Servants begin to gather... \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nA missing Servant class...\u003cbr\u003e\nImpossible Servant summonings...\u003cbr\u003e\nA nation shrouded in secrecy...\u003cbr\u003e\nAnd a city created as a battleground.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nIn the face of such irregularities, the Holy Grail War is twisted and driven into the depth of madness. Let the curtain rise on a masquerade of humans and heroes, made to dance upon the stage of a false Holy Grail. \u003ci\u003eThis is a Holy Grail War covered in lies.\u003c/i\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Official Site, Aniplex USA, edited)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n•  \u003ci\u003eSpecial premiere of Episode 1 in its English Dub occurred in Los Angeles at the Fate 20th Anniversary Showcase event and as well through Crunchyroll’s YouTube Channel on November 23, 2024 before the Japanese television premiere.\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n•  \u003ci\u003eThe Japanese advanced premiere occurred during the \"Fate New Year's Eve TV Special 2024\" on December 31, 2024.\u003c/i\u003e","duration":25,"endDate":{"day":28,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":13,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy","Mystery","Supernatural"],"id":166617,"idMal":55830,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":83,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774103400,"episode":12,"timeUntilAiring":498996},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/166617","startDate":{"day":3,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Судьба/Странная подделка"],"title":{"english":"Fate/strange Fake","native":"Fate/strange Fake","romaji":"Fate/strange Fake","userPreferred":"Fate/strange Fake"},"trailer":{"id":"k1G8EvZg_BY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/k1G8EvZg_BY/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-105804},{"airingAt":1773498600,"episode":10,"id":405106,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/187901-03I5T8QVX1FG.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#35bbf1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx187901-T91HmZAaNwOF.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx187901-T91HmZAaNwOF.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx187901-T91HmZAaNwOF.jpg"},"description":"Always ready for a fight! Destruction for destruction’s sake! The online streamer Aoringo is a troll, making the worst of the worst of boundary-pushing flamebait content and raking in the revenue from the hate-watchers. You may think he’s nothing more than a bottom feeder and a drain on society, but in reality, he’s high school dropout Souji Enishiro, a caring older brother with a sweet tooth who loves nothing more than his little sister. His viral videos? Just a way to pay his sister’s medical bills. And even if all of humanity hates him, he doesn’t care, so long as his little sister gets better. But then, something very strange begins to happen...\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":28,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Supernatural"],"id":187901,"idMal":61196,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":62,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774103400,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":498996},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/187901","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["デドアカ","เดดแอ็กเคานต์ พิฆาตบัญชีมรณะ"],"title":{"english":"Dead Account","native":"デッドアカウント","romaji":"Dead Account","userPreferred":"Dead Account"},"trailer":{"id":"ynnk0CIyu10","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ynnk0CIyu10/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-105804},{"airingAt":1773496800,"episode":10,"id":404750,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/163144-e6vGlARSvwyE.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx163144-XdVwFRxPGY6j.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx163144-XdVwFRxPGY6j.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx163144-XdVwFRxPGY6j.jpg"},"description":"Sequel season to \u003ci\u003eTRIGUN STAMPEDE\u003c/i\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nIt’s been two and a half years since the Lost JuLai tragedy, which laid waste to an entire city and engulfed the whole planet in chaos. Meryl, now a senior journalist, continues her search for Vash with her new younger sidekick, Milly, and runs into Wolfwood along the way. As plant robberies begin taking place once again, they sense Millions Knives’s organization conspiring behind the scenes.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nMeanwhile, Vash has taken the new name Eriks and is living in hiding in a backwater town when he gets an abrupt visit from Jessica, a young girl with an SOS from the third ship they call home. He thus decides to put an end to a long-standing feud in order to protect those dear to him.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nJust as the pieces of the story begin falling back together again, the planet receives a message from the far reaches of outer space: “We are a fleet of colony ships from Earth... Those who wish may accompany us to a new frontier.” The entire population rejoices at this news. However, as if to mock their celebration, the one-winged angel returns to wreak havoc and despair. Fates collide to forge a final conclusion for the panicked planet.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":28,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Comedy","Drama","Sci-Fi"],"id":163144,"idMal":54863,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":71,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774101600,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":497196},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/163144","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["トライガン スタンピード 完結編","TRIGUN STAMPEDE: Kanketsu-hen","トライガン スターゲイズ"],"title":{"english":"TRIGUN STARGAZE","native":"TRIGUN STARGAZE","romaji":"TRIGUN STARGAZE","userPreferred":"TRIGUN STARGAZE"},"trailer":{"id":"JBYLkW--zmI","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/JBYLkW--zmI/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-107604},{"airingAt":1773493200,"episode":11,"id":405075,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#4393c9","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx199446-2jYnGrTItjyu.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx199446-2jYnGrTItjyu.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx199446-2jYnGrTItjyu.jpg"},"description":"The story of Saioshi no Gikei Mederutame, Nagaikishimasu! follows the struggle of a player to protect his favorite character, who gets reincarnated as his older brother-in-law in a simulation raising game - however, the player is reincarnated as the younger brother who was meant to die.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: ANN)","duration":4,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV_SHORT","genres":["Fantasy","Romance"],"id":199446,"idMal":61969,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":51,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774098000,"episode":12,"timeUntilAiring":493596},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/a