,"coverImage":{"color":"#f1930d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx187941-ykmc8WRedPpw.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx187941-ykmc8WRedPpw.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx187941-ykmc8WRedPpw.jpg"},"description":"Our hero needs to come out of his shell... literally! Reborn in another world inside a dragon egg, he doesn’t have the amazing magic or mighty physical strength of your typical isekai’d adventurer just yet. He’ll need to break free and grow from a weak hatchling and into a fearsome beast if he wants to escape the deep, dark forest unscathed. What battles and adventures await him in this unique take on the isekai phenomenon?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: HIDIVE)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":187941,"idMal":61207,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":62,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774096200,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":491796},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/187941","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["DoraTama"],"title":{"english":"Reincarnated as a Dragon Hatchling","native":"転生したらドラゴンの卵だった","romaji":"Tensei Shitara Dragon no Tamago Datta","userPreferred":"Tensei Shitara Dragon no Tamago Datta"},"trailer":{"id":"VPLmZd3ByAM","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/VPLmZd3ByAM/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-113004},{"airingAt":1773480300,"episode":19,"id":404837,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx186736-zYDrRDuC55s5.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx186736-zYDrRDuC55s5.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx186736-zYDrRDuC55s5.png"},"description":"The second season of \u003ci\u003eKagaku×Bouken Survival!\u003c/i\u003e","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":[],"id":186736,"idMal":60983,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":48,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774085100,"episode":20,"timeUntilAiring":480696},"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/186736","startDate":{"day":4,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"科学×冒険サバイバル！ 第2シリーズ","romaji":"Kagaku×Bouken Survival! 2nd Season","userPreferred":"Kagaku×Bouken Survival! 2nd Season"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-124104},{"airingAt":1773478800,"episode":1193,"id":409738,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/235-MTmiz0uB0fMd.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#28a1e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx235-MyYT7K3chBdO.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx235-MyYT7K3chBdO.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx235-MyYT7K3chBdO.jpg"},"description":"Kudo Shinichi is a seventeen year-old high school detective whom people call the \"Modern Sherlock Holmes.\" However, one night after a date with his childhood sweetheart, Ran, Shinichi witnessed an illegal trade and, caught off his guard, was knocked unconscious and fed a drug that was supposed to kill him... but he woke up and found himself shrunken to a seven year-old. In order to track down the men who did this to him, Shinichi hid his identity and lived with Ran, whose father happened to be a hopeless detective, and with that came a series of murders and mysteries that he must solve. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote:\u003cbr\u003e\n- Includes Keisatsu Gakkou-hen - Wild Police Story in episodes 1029, 1038, 1042, 1061\u003cbr\u003e\n- Episodes 11, 52, 76, 118, 162, 184, 208, 342, 356, 449, 452, 487, 488, 489, 490, 515, 516, 521, 522, 651, 734, 804, 805, 927, 928, 1187 aired with a runtime of ~50 minutes as opposed to the standard 25 minute long episode.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Episodes 96, 129, 174, 219, 263, 304, 383, 479 aired with a runtime of ~90 minutes as opposed to the standard 25 minute long episode.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Episode 345, 425 aired with a runtime of ~115 minutes as opposed to the standard 25 minute long episode.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c/i\u003e","duration":25,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Adventure","Comedy","Mystery","Psychological"],"id":235,"idMal":235,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":82,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774083600,"episode":1194,"timeUntilAiring":479196},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/235","startDate":{"day":8,"month":1,"year":1996},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Detective Conan","Detectiu Conan","הבלש קונאן","Detektyw Conan","المحقق كونان","名侦探柯南","Meitantei Conan: Keisaku Gakkou Hen - Wild Police Story","名探偵コナン 警察学校編 Wild Police Story","Détective Conan","ยอดนักสืบจิ๋วโคนัน","Thám Tử Lừng Danh Conan","Detektiv Conan"],"title":{"english":"Case Closed","native":"名探偵コナン","romaji":"Meitantei Conan","userPreferred":"Meitantei Conan"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-125604},{"airingAt":1773477000,"episode":12,"id":406911,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#50bbe4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx189258-qhtrra5ebBm6.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx189258-qhtrra5ebBm6.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx189258-qhtrra5ebBm6.jpg"},"description":"The second season of \u003ci\u003eAo no Miburo\u003c/i\u003e.","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Drama"],"id":189258,"idMal":61333,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":65,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/189258","startDate":{"day":20,"month":12,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Ao no Miburo Season 2"],"title":{"english":"Blue Miburo Season 2","native":"青のミブロ 芹沢暗殺編","romaji":"Ao no Miburo: Serizawa Ansatsu-hen","userPreferred":"Ao no Miburo: Serizawa Ansatsu-hen"},"trailer":{"id":"7hWWDxF0hyo","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/7hWWDxF0hyo/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-127404},{"airingAt":1773475200,"episode":906,"id":380034,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/8687-aa3QbJjGfy3B.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#fed628","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b8687-bBnJMGnih4PT.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b8687-bBnJMGnih4PT.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/b8687-bBnJMGnih4PT.jpg"},"description":"A new Doraemon series produced by the same team as the 1979 series (in association with Studio Pierrot) with new voice actors and staff and updated character designs.","duration":25,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Adventure","Comedy","Sci-Fi"],"id":8687,"idMal":8687,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":77,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774080000,"episode":907,"timeUntilAiring":475596},"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/8687","startDate":{"day":15,"month":4,"year":2005},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"ドラえもん (2005)","romaji":"Doraemon (2005)","userPreferred":"Doraemon (2005)"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-129204},{"airingAt":1773473400,"episode":1326,"id":409411,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/966-J5CwLLTBs4OO.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4e428","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b966-QUCdKAk4ls9J.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b966-QUCdKAk4ls9J.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/b966-QUCdKAk4ls9J.jpg"},"description":"Crayon Shin-chan follows the wacky antics and adventures of five-year-old Shinnosuke \"Shin\" Nohara and his parents, neighbors, and friends and is set in Kasukabe, Saitama Prefecture, Japan.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nMany of the jokes in the series stem from Shin-chan's occasionally weird, unnatural and inappropriate use of language, as well as from his inappropriate behavior. A typical gag involves Shin-chan confounding his parents by using the wrong phrase for the occasion; for example, saying \"Welcome back!\" instead of \"I am back!\" when he comes home.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nDuring the beginning of the series, the TV show was mostly based on the storyline in the original manga. As the show progressed, more and more episodes became anime-original.","duration":21,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Comedy","Ecchi","Slice of Life"],"id":966,"idMal":966,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774078200,"episode":1327,"timeUntilAiring":473796},"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/966","startDate":{"day":13,"month":4,"year":1992},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Shin Chan","native":"クレヨンしんちゃん","romaji":"Crayon Shin-chan","userPreferred":"Crayon Shin-chan"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-131004},{"airingAt":1773453600,"episode":144,"id":408244,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"CN","coverImage":{"color":"#5daee4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx137683-IMuvIECdZNBh.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx137683-IMuvIECdZNBh.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx137683-IMuvIECdZNBh.png"},"description":"The Tang Sect in a turbulent world. There is nothing but martial spirit here. Ten thousand years after the founding of the Tang Sect, it is in relative decline. An extremely talented man was born. Can the new Shrek Seven Monsters revive the Tang Sect and bring it back to glory? A soul beast of over one million years old; Electrolux who can pick stars; The new soul utensil system that led to the decline of the Tang Sect... A lot of secrets are to be revealed. Can the secret weapons of the Tang Sect be sharp again? Can the Tang Sect regain its former glory?\n\u003c/br\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\n(Source: WeTV)","duration":20,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":156,"format":"ONA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy","Romance"],"id":137683,"idMal":51836,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774058400,"episode":145,"timeUntilAiring":453996},"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/137683","startDate":{"day":24,"month":6,"year":2023},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Soul Land 2: The Unrivaled Tang Sect","斗罗大陆Ⅱ绝世唐门","Soul Land 2: Peerless Tang Sect"],"title":{"english":"Soul Land 2: The Peerless Tang Clan","native":"斗罗大陆2绝世唐门","romaji":"Douluo Dalu 2: Jueshi Tangmen","userPreferred":"Douluo Dalu 2: Jueshi Tangmen"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-150804},{"airingAt":1773442800,"episode":8,"id":409607,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#4393e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx203296-LYXWSdP4N4YF.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx203296-LYXWSdP4N4YF.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx203296-LYXWSdP4N4YF.jpg"},"description":"The fifth season of \u003ci\u003eCardfight!! Vanguard: Divinez.\u003c/i\u003e","duration":null,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":203296,"idMal":62649,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":62,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774047600,"episode":9,"timeUntilAiring":443196},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/203296","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["CARDFIGHT!! VANGUARD Divinez Parallactic Clash"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"カードファイト!! ヴァンガード Divinez 幻真星戦編","romaji":"Cardfight!! Vanguard: Divinez Genma Seisen-hen","userPreferred":"Cardfight!! Vanguard: Divinez Genma Seisen-hen"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-161604},{"airingAt":1773441000,"episode":207,"id":406438,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1bb43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx142274-qPfkeKk4caKI.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx142274-qPfkeKk4caKI.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx142274-qPfkeKk4caKI.png"},"description":"The year is 20XX. The ninja, who once forged the history of Japan, were scattered across the country during the Meiji Restoration. As these ninja mingled with the other clans, their bloodline thinned, and they gradually faded from sight. The descendants of these ninja clans, seeking to preserve their heritage, formed the WNA (World Ninja Association) in the hope of carrying on their legacy.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAnd so it was that the WNA succeeded in developing Ninja-Gum, an art which could summon forth the strength of the Shinobi. And yet creating the most powerful Ninja-Gum requires the strongest of ninja DNA. So it was that the Ninjala Tournament was held, that the mightiest of all ninjas could be found...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Official Game website)","duration":23,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Comedy","Sci-Fi"],"id":142274,"idMal":50418,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":49,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774045800,"episode":208,"timeUntilAiring":441396},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/142274","startDate":{"day":8,"month":1,"year":2022},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Ninjala the Animation","native":"ニンジャラ","romaji":"Ninjala","userPreferred":"Ninjala"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-163404},{"airingAt":1773439200,"episode":49,"id":406264,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#5da1f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx184289-v85FJN0O4S1j.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx184289-v85FJN0O4S1j.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx184289-v85FJN0O4S1j.jpg"},"description":"Following the chaotic and heartwarming daily lives of Kaijuu who have come to Earth to conquer the world and live with their human masters.","duration":3,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV_SHORT","genres":["Slice of Life"],"id":184289,"idMal":60070,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":51,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774044000,"episode":50,"timeUntilAiring":439596},"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/184289","startDate":{"day":5,"month":4,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Tiny Dragons Rule the World"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"かいじゅうせかいせいふく","romaji":"Kaijuu Sekai Seifuku","userPreferred":"Kaijuu Sekai Seifuku"},"trailer":{"id":"f8VXXMz6StQ","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/f8VXXMz6StQ/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-165204},{"airingAt":1773435600,"episode":24,"id":401293,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","c